prod2, canal, subcanal, i_canal, i_segmento, i_agrupado, i_apetito, i_plazared, i_prodinfo,

from bddldes.dauniverso

SELECT
	*
FROM
	(
	SELECT
		KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL	AS	NUM_POLIZA,
		KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL	AS	NUM_VERSION,
		KCIM06T.CDNUMCON	AS	NUM_CONTRATO,
		KCIM06T.INULTSIT	AS	ULT_SITUACION,
		KCIM06T.CDPRODTE	AS	CVE_PRODUCTO_TECNICO,
		KCIM06T.CDPRODCO	AS	CVE_PRODUCTO_COMERCIAL,
		KCIM06T.CDCANALD	AS	CVE_CANAL_DISTRIBUCION_INFO,
		KCIM06T.CDNIVDIV	AS	CVE_NIVEL_DIVISION,
		KCIM06T.CDNIVSUB	AS	CVE_NIVEL_SUBDIVISION,
		KCIM06T.CLGESUN		AS	CVE_OFICINA_GESTORA,
		KCIM06T.CLPROUN		AS	CVE_OFICINA_PRODUCTORA,
		KCIM06T.CLOPEUN		AS	CVE_OFICINA_OPERATIVA,
		KCIM06T.TCTIMOVP	AS  CVE_TIPO_MOVIMIENTO,
		KCIM06T.TCMOMOVP	AS	CVE_MOTIVO_MOVIMIENTO,
		KCIM06T.DUCONTRA	AS	DURACION_CONTRATO,
		KCIM06T.ESPOLIZA	AS	EST_POLIZA,
		KCIM06T.INANULFP	AS	BAN_FALTA_PAGO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FECAMEST as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FECAMEST as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FECAMEST IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FECAMEST as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') -- TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FECAMEST),'YYYYMMDD')
		END 		AS	FCH_CAMB_EST,
		TCFORPAG	AS	CVE_FORMA_PAGO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEANULFP IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') -- TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEANULFP),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_FALTA_PAGO_ANT,
		TCFOPASU	AS	CVE_FORMA_PAGO,
		HOEFTINI	AS	TS_INICIO_POLIZA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEINIPOL as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEINIPOL as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEINIPOL IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEINIPOL as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEINIPOL),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_INICIO_POLIZA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTONA as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTONA as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEEFTONA IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTONA as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEEFTONA),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_INICIO_VIGENCIA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEVENCIM IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_FIN_VIGENCIA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEFINEFE IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_FIN_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEMISION IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEMISION),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_EMISION,
		KCIM06T.INANCACO	AS 	NUM_RENOVACION,
		KCIM06T.POCESCOM	AS 	PCT_CESION_COMISION,
		KCIM06T.INTICOAS	AS 	TIPO_COASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.POCOASEG	AS	PCT_COASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.INREAACE	AS	BAN_REASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.CLFILTOM	AS	CVE_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMPOL	AS	TOMADOR_NOMBRE,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMP01	AS	TOMADOR_PRIMER_APELLIDO,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMP02	AS	TOMADOR_SEGUNDO_APELLIDO,
		KCIM06T.NODIRTOM	AS	CALLE_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NUDIRTOM	AS	NUMERO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.CLACCADT	AS	REFERENCIA_DOMICILIO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NOPOBTOM	AS	MUNICIPIO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.TCCOPTOM	AS	CP_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.CLFILPAG	AS	CVE_PAGADOR,
		KCIM06T.TCCANCO1	AS	CVE_CANAL_COBRO,
		KCIM06T.TCCANCOS	AS	CVE_CANAL_COBRO_SUCESIVO,
		KCIM06T.TCCDMONE	AS	CVE_MONEDA_INFO,
		KCIM06T.CDTIPCAM	AS	CVE_TIPO_CAMBIO,
		KCIM06T.INIDIOMA	AS	IDIOMA_POLIZA,
		KCIM06T.CDCIAGRU	AS	CVE_RAMO,
		KCIM06T.TCSEGMEN	AS	SEGMENTO,
		KCIM06T.INPOLPAD	AS	BAN_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CDPOLPAD	AS	NUM_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CTVRSPAD	AS	NUM_VERSION_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CLREFERE	AS	REFERENCIA1,
		KCIM06T.CLREFLIB	AS	REFERENCIA2,
		KCIM06T.INDIVIDE	AS	BAN_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.TCFORPAD	AS	CVE_FORMA_PAGO_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.POFACDIV	AS	PCT_FAC_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.POFACPRI	AS	PCT_FAC_PRIMA,
		KCIM06T.POFACCOM	AS	PCT_FAC_COMISIONES,
		KCIM06T.POFACSIN	AS	PCT_FAC_SINIESTROS,
		KCIM06T.POFACGIA	AS	PCT_FAC_GIA,
		KCIM06T.TSCDC	AS	TS_ULTIMA_MODIFICACION,
		--SYSDATE				AS	FEC_CORTE,
		TABLA_ENDOSOS.CONT_ENDOSO AS NUM_ENDOSOS,
		E.CTVRSPOL			AS	A_CTVRSPOL,
		CASE
			WHEN E.CTVRSPOL IS NULL THEN KCIM06T.INULTSIT
			WHEN E.CTVRSPOL=KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL THEN 'U'
			ELSE 'H'
		END AS ULT_EST_CORREGIDO,
		I.NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_INICIO_VIGENCIA_X_RENOVA,
		I.NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_INICIO_VIG_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_FIN_VIG_X_RENOVA,
		KRBM10T.CDNUMPOL	AS	KRBM10T_CDNUMPOL,
		KRBM10T.CTVRSPOL	AS	KRBM10T_CTVRSPOL,
		KRBM10T.TCESREC		AS	KRBM10T_TCESREC,
		KRBM10T.TCSBEREC	AS	KRBM10T_TCSBEREC,
		KRBM10T.FECREBRE	AS	KRBM10T_FECREBRE,
		CASE
			WHEN KRBM10T.FECREBRE IS NULL 
					AND cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING)<>'0'
					AND SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING),5,2)<=12
					AND KCIM06T.FEANULFP IS NOT NULL
				THEN from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEANULFP),'YYYYMMDD')
			WHEN KRBM10T.FECREBRE IS NOT NULL 
					AND cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as STRING)<>'0'
					AND SUBSTR(cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as STRING),5,2)<=12
				THEN from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KRBM10T.FECREBRE),'YYYYMMDD')
			ELSE NULL
		END AS FCH_FALTA_PAGO,
		ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL, KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL ORDER BY KCIM06T.INULTSIT DESC) AS RN 
	FROM
	    bddlcru.KCIM06T AS KCIM06T
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				A.CDNUMPOL,
				A.INANCACO,
				COUNT(A.CDNUMPOL) AS CONT_ENDOSO
			FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T A
			WHERE
	    	A.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -1) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    	AND	A.TSCDC	<	current_date --SYSDATE
			AND SUBSTR(TRIM(A.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
			AND A.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
			GROUP BY A.CDNUMPOL, A.INANCACO) TABLA_ENDOSOS
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=TABLA_ENDOSOS.CDNUMPOL
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				B.CDNUMPOL,
				B.CTVRSPOL
			FROM
				bddlcru.KCIM06T B
			INNER JOIN
				(SELECT
					D.CDNUMPOL,
					max(cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(D.tscdc),'YYYYMMdd') as string)) AS ULTMODMAX -- MAX(TO_CHAR(D.TSCDC,'YYYYMMDD')) AS ULTMODMAX
				FROM
					bddlcru.KCIM06T D
				WHERE
	    			D.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3)-- SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    			AND	D.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    			AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(D.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    			AND	D.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	    			AND D.INULTSIT='U'
	    		GROUP BY D.CDNUMPOL
				)C
			ON B.CDNUMPOL=C.CDNUMPOL AND cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(B.TSCDC),'YYYYMMdd') as string)=C.ULTMODMAX
			WHERE
	    		B.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    		AND	B.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    		AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(B.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    		AND	B.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	    		AND B.INULTSIT='U'
			)E
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=E.CDNUMPOL
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				H.CDNUMPOL	AS	NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA,
				H.FEEFTONA	AS	FCH_INICIO_VIGENCIA_X_RENOVA,
				H.INANCACO	AS	NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA,
				CASE
					WHEN cast(H.FEEFTONA as STRING)='0' OR -- TO_CHAR(H.FEEFTONA)='0' OR
					SUBSTR(cast(H.FEEFTONA as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
					H.FEEFTONA IS NULL THEN NULL
					ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(H.FEEFTONA as string), 'YYYYMMdd'), 'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(H.FEEFTONA),'YYYYMMDD')
				END 		AS	FCH_INICIO_VIG_X_RENOVA,
				CASE
					WHEN cast(H.FEVENCIM as STRING)='0' OR
					SUBSTR(cast(H.FEVENCIM as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
					H.FEVENCIM IS NULL THEN NULL
					ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(H.FEVENCIM as string), 'YYYYMMdd'), 'YYYYMMdd') -- TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(H.FEVENCIM),'YYYYMMDD')
				END 		AS	FCH_FIN_VIG_X_RENOVA
			FROM
				bddlcru.KCIM06T H
			INNER JOIN
				(SELECT
					F.CDNUMPOL,
					MIN(F.CTVRSPOL) AS MN_CTVRSPOL,
					F.INANCACO
				FROM
					bddlcru.KCIM06T F
				GROUP BY F.CDNUMPOL, F.INANCACO
				)G
			ON H.CDNUMPOL=G.CDNUMPOL AND H.CTVRSPOL=G.MN_CTVRSPOL AND H.INANCACO=G.INANCACO
			)I
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=I.NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA AND KCIM06T.INANCACO=I.NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				CDNUMPOL,
				CTVRSPOL,
				TCESREC,
				TCSBEREC,
				MAX(FECREBRE) AS FECREBRE
			FROM
				bddlcru.KRBM10T
			WHERE
				TCSBEREC='FP'
			GROUP BY 	CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,	TCESREC, TCSBEREC
			) KRBM10T
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=KRBM10T.CDNUMPOL AND KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL=KRBM10T.CTVRSPOL
	WHERE
	    KCIM06T.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    AND	KCIM06T.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(KCIM06T.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    AND	KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	) PRO_TGT

SELECT
	*
FROM
	(
	SELECT
		KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL	AS	NUM_POLIZA,
		KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL	AS	NUM_VERSION,
		KCIM06T.CDNUMCON	AS	NUM_CONTRATO,
		KCIM06T.INULTSIT	AS	ULT_SITUACION,
		KCIM06T.CDPRODTE	AS	CVE_PRODUCTO_TECNICO,
		KCIM06T.CDPRODCO	AS	CVE_PRODUCTO_COMERCIAL,
		KCIM06T.CDCANALD	AS	CVE_CANAL_DISTRIBUCION_INFO,
		KCIM06T.CDNIVDIV	AS	CVE_NIVEL_DIVISION,
		KCIM06T.CDNIVSUB	AS	CVE_NIVEL_SUBDIVISION,
		KCIM06T.CLGESUN		AS	CVE_OFICINA_GESTORA,
		KCIM06T.CLPROUN		AS	CVE_OFICINA_PRODUCTORA,
		KCIM06T.CLOPEUN		AS	CVE_OFICINA_OPERATIVA,
		KCIM06T.TCTIMOVP	AS  CVE_TIPO_MOVIMIENTO,
		KCIM06T.TCMOMOVP	AS	CVE_MOTIVO_MOVIMIENTO,
		KCIM06T.DUCONTRA	AS	DURACION_CONTRATO,
		KCIM06T.ESPOLIZA	AS	EST_POLIZA,
		KCIM06T.INANULFP	AS	BAN_FALTA_PAGO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FECAMEST as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FECAMEST as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FECAMEST IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FECAMEST as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') -- TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FECAMEST),'YYYYMMDD')
		END 		AS	FCH_CAMB_EST,
		TCFORPAG	AS	CVE_FORMA_PAGO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEANULFP IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') -- TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEANULFP),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_FALTA_PAGO_ANT,
		TCFOPASU	AS	CVE_FORMA_PAGO,
		HOEFTINI	AS	TS_INICIO_POLIZA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEINIPOL as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEINIPOL as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEINIPOL IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEINIPOL as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEINIPOL),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_INICIO_POLIZA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTONA as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTONA as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEEFTONA IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTONA as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEEFTONA),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_INICIO_VIGENCIA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEVENCIM IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_FIN_VIGENCIA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEFINEFE IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_FIN_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEMISION IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEMISION),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_EMISION,
		KCIM06T.INANCACO	AS 	NUM_RENOVACION,
		KCIM06T.POCESCOM	AS 	PCT_CESION_COMISION,
		KCIM06T.INTICOAS	AS 	TIPO_COASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.POCOASEG	AS	PCT_COASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.INREAACE	AS	BAN_REASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.CLFILTOM	AS	CVE_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMPOL	AS	TOMADOR_NOMBRE,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMP01	AS	TOMADOR_PRIMER_APELLIDO,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMP02	AS	TOMADOR_SEGUNDO_APELLIDO,
		KCIM06T.NODIRTOM	AS	CALLE_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NUDIRTOM	AS	NUMERO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.CLACCADT	AS	REFERENCIA_DOMICILIO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NOPOBTOM	AS	MUNICIPIO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.TCCOPTOM	AS	CP_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.CLFILPAG	AS	CVE_PAGADOR,
		KCIM06T.TCCANCO1	AS	CVE_CANAL_COBRO,
		KCIM06T.TCCANCOS	AS	CVE_CANAL_COBRO_SUCESIVO,
		KCIM06T.TCCDMONE	AS	CVE_MONEDA_INFO,
		KCIM06T.CDTIPCAM	AS	CVE_TIPO_CAMBIO,
		KCIM06T.INIDIOMA	AS	IDIOMA_POLIZA,
		KCIM06T.CDCIAGRU	AS	CVE_RAMO,
		KCIM06T.TCSEGMEN	AS	SEGMENTO,
		KCIM06T.INPOLPAD	AS	BAN_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CDPOLPAD	AS	NUM_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CTVRSPAD	AS	NUM_VERSION_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CLREFERE	AS	REFERENCIA1,
		KCIM06T.CLREFLIB	AS	REFERENCIA2,
		KCIM06T.INDIVIDE	AS	BAN_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.TCFORPAD	AS	CVE_FORMA_PAGO_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.POFACDIV	AS	PCT_FAC_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.POFACPRI	AS	PCT_FAC_PRIMA,
		KCIM06T.POFACCOM	AS	PCT_FAC_COMISIONES,
		KCIM06T.POFACSIN	AS	PCT_FAC_SINIESTROS,
		KCIM06T.POFACGIA	AS	PCT_FAC_GIA,
		KCIM06T.TSCDC	AS	TS_ULTIMA_MODIFICACION,
		--SYSDATE				AS	FEC_CORTE,
		TABLA_ENDOSOS.CONT_ENDOSO AS NUM_ENDOSOS,
		E.CTVRSPOL			AS	A_CTVRSPOL,
		CASE
			WHEN E.CTVRSPOL IS NULL THEN KCIM06T.INULTSIT
			WHEN E.CTVRSPOL=KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL THEN 'U'
			ELSE 'H'
		END AS ULT_EST_CORREGIDO,
		I.NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_INICIO_VIGENCIA_X_RENOVA,
		I.NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_INICIO_VIG_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_FIN_VIG_X_RENOVA,
		KRBM10T.CDNUMPOL	AS	KRBM10T_CDNUMPOL,
		KRBM10T.CTVRSPOL	AS	KRBM10T_CTVRSPOL,
		KRBM10T.TCESREC		AS	KRBM10T_TCESREC,
		KRBM10T.TCSBEREC	AS	KRBM10T_TCSBEREC,
		KRBM10T.FECREBRE	AS	KRBM10T_FECREBRE,
		CASE
			WHEN KRBM10T.FECREBRE IS NULL 
					AND cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING)<>'0'
					AND SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING),5,2)<=12
					AND KCIM06T.FEANULFP IS NOT NULL
				THEN from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEANULFP),'YYYYMMDD')
			WHEN KRBM10T.FECREBRE IS NOT NULL 
					AND cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as STRING)<>'0'
					AND SUBSTR(cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as STRING),5,2)<=12
				THEN from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KRBM10T.FECREBRE),'YYYYMMDD')
			ELSE NULL
		END AS FCH_FALTA_PAGO,
		ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL, KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL ORDER BY KCIM06T.INULTSIT DESC) AS RN 
	FROM
	    bddlcru.KCIM06T AS KCIM06T
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				A.CDNUMPOL,
				A.INANCACO,
				COUNT(A.CDNUMPOL) AS CONT_ENDOSO
			FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T A
			WHERE
	    	A.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -1) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    	AND	A.TSCDC	<	current_date --SYSDATE
			AND SUBSTR(TRIM(A.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
			AND A.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
			GROUP BY A.CDNUMPOL, A.INANCACO) TABLA_ENDOSOS
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=TABLA_ENDOSOS.CDNUMPOL
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				B.CDNUMPOL,
				B.CTVRSPOL
			FROM
				bddlcru.KCIM06T B
			INNER JOIN
				(SELECT
					D.CDNUMPOL,
					max(cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(D.tscdc),'YYYYMMdd') as string)) AS ULTMODMAX -- MAX(TO_CHAR(D.TSCDC,'YYYYMMDD')) AS ULTMODMAX
				FROM
					bddlcru.KCIM06T D
				WHERE
	    			D.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3)-- SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    			AND	D.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    			AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(D.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    			AND	D.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	    			AND D.INULTSIT='U'
	    		GROUP BY D.CDNUMPOL
				)C
			ON B.CDNUMPOL=C.CDNUMPOL AND cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(B.TSCDC),'YYYYMMdd') as string)=C.ULTMODMAX
			WHERE
	    		B.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    		AND	B.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    		AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(B.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    		AND	B.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	    		AND B.INULTSIT='U'
			)E
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=E.CDNUMPOL
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				H.CDNUMPOL	AS	NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA,
				H.FEEFTONA	AS	FCH_INICIO_VIGENCIA_X_RENOVA,
				H.INANCACO	AS	NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA,
				CASE
					WHEN cast(H.FEEFTONA as STRING)='0' OR -- TO_CHAR(H.FEEFTONA)='0' OR
					SUBSTR(cast(H.FEEFTONA as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
					H.FEEFTONA IS NULL THEN NULL
					ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(H.FEEFTONA as string), 'YYYYMMdd'), 'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(H.FEEFTONA),'YYYYMMDD')
				END 		AS	FCH_INICIO_VIG_X_RENOVA,
				CASE
					WHEN cast(H.FEVENCIM as STRING)='0' OR
					SUBSTR(cast(H.FEVENCIM as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
					H.FEVENCIM IS NULL THEN NULL
					ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(H.FEVENCIM as string), 'YYYYMMdd'), 'YYYYMMdd') -- TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(H.FEVENCIM),'YYYYMMDD')
				END 		AS	FCH_FIN_VIG_X_RENOVA
			FROM
				bddlcru.KCIM06T H
			INNER JOIN
				(SELECT
					F.CDNUMPOL,
					MIN(F.CTVRSPOL) AS MN_CTVRSPOL,
					F.INANCACO
				FROM
					bddlcru.KCIM06T F
				GROUP BY F.CDNUMPOL, F.INANCACO
				)G
			ON H.CDNUMPOL=G.CDNUMPOL AND H.CTVRSPOL=G.MN_CTVRSPOL AND H.INANCACO=G.INANCACO
			)I
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=I.NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA AND KCIM06T.INANCACO=I.NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				CDNUMPOL,
				CTVRSPOL,
				TCESREC,
				TCSBEREC,
				MAX(FECREBRE) AS FECREBRE
			FROM
				bddlcru.KRBM10T
			WHERE
				TCSBEREC='FP'
			GROUP BY 	CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,	TCESREC, TCSBEREC
			) KRBM10T
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=KRBM10T.CDNUMPOL AND KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL=KRBM10T.CTVRSPOL
	WHERE
	    KCIM06T.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    AND	KCIM06T.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(KCIM06T.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    AND	KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	) PRO_TGT

			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEEFTOMO),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEVENCIM IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEVENCIM),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_FIN_VIGENCIA,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEFINEFE IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEFINEFE),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_FIN_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
		CASE
			WHEN cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as STRING)='0' OR
			SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
			KCIM06T.FEMISION IS NULL THEN NULL
			ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEMISION as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEMISION),'YYYYMMDD')
		END			AS	FCH_EMISION,
		KCIM06T.INANCACO	AS 	NUM_RENOVACION,
		KCIM06T.POCESCOM	AS 	PCT_CESION_COMISION,
		KCIM06T.INTICOAS	AS 	TIPO_COASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.POCOASEG	AS	PCT_COASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.INREAACE	AS	BAN_REASEGURO,
		KCIM06T.CLFILTOM	AS	CVE_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMPOL	AS	TOMADOR_NOMBRE,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMP01	AS	TOMADOR_PRIMER_APELLIDO,
		KCIM06T.NOTOMP02	AS	TOMADOR_SEGUNDO_APELLIDO,
		KCIM06T.NODIRTOM	AS	CALLE_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NUDIRTOM	AS	NUMERO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.CLACCADT	AS	REFERENCIA_DOMICILIO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.NOPOBTOM	AS	MUNICIPIO_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.TCCOPTOM	AS	CP_CONTRATANTE,
		KCIM06T.CLFILPAG	AS	CVE_PAGADOR,
		KCIM06T.TCCANCO1	AS	CVE_CANAL_COBRO,
		KCIM06T.TCCANCOS	AS	CVE_CANAL_COBRO_SUCESIVO,
		KCIM06T.TCCDMONE	AS	CVE_MONEDA_INFO,
		KCIM06T.CDTIPCAM	AS	CVE_TIPO_CAMBIO,
		KCIM06T.INIDIOMA	AS	IDIOMA_POLIZA,
		KCIM06T.CDCIAGRU	AS	CVE_RAMO,
		KCIM06T.TCSEGMEN	AS	SEGMENTO,
		KCIM06T.INPOLPAD	AS	BAN_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CDPOLPAD	AS	NUM_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CTVRSPAD	AS	NUM_VERSION_POLIZA_PADRE,
		KCIM06T.CLREFERE	AS	REFERENCIA1,
		KCIM06T.CLREFLIB	AS	REFERENCIA2,
		KCIM06T.INDIVIDE	AS	BAN_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.TCFORPAD	AS	CVE_FORMA_PAGO_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.POFACDIV	AS	PCT_FAC_DIVIDENDO,
		KCIM06T.POFACPRI	AS	PCT_FAC_PRIMA,
		KCIM06T.POFACCOM	AS	PCT_FAC_COMISIONES,
		KCIM06T.POFACSIN	AS	PCT_FAC_SINIESTROS,
		KCIM06T.POFACGIA	AS	PCT_FAC_GIA,
		KCIM06T.TSCDC	AS	TS_ULTIMA_MODIFICACION,
		--SYSDATE				AS	FEC_CORTE,
		TABLA_ENDOSOS.CONT_ENDOSO AS NUM_ENDOSOS,
		E.CTVRSPOL			AS	A_CTVRSPOL,
		CASE
			WHEN E.CTVRSPOL IS NULL THEN KCIM06T.INULTSIT
			WHEN E.CTVRSPOL=KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL THEN 'U'
			ELSE 'H'
		END AS ULT_EST_CORREGIDO,
		I.NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_INICIO_VIGENCIA_X_RENOVA,
		I.NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_INICIO_VIG_X_RENOVA,
		I.FCH_FIN_VIG_X_RENOVA,
		KRBM10T.CDNUMPOL	AS	KRBM10T_CDNUMPOL,
		KRBM10T.CTVRSPOL	AS	KRBM10T_CTVRSPOL,
		KRBM10T.TCESREC		AS	KRBM10T_TCESREC,
		KRBM10T.TCSBEREC	AS	KRBM10T_TCSBEREC,
		KRBM10T.FECREBRE	AS	KRBM10T_FECREBRE,
		CASE
			WHEN KRBM10T.FECREBRE IS NULL 
					AND cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING)<>'0'
					AND SUBSTR(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as STRING),5,2)<=12
					AND KCIM06T.FEANULFP IS NOT NULL
				THEN from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KCIM06T.FEANULFP as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KCIM06T.FEANULFP),'YYYYMMDD')
			WHEN KRBM10T.FECREBRE IS NOT NULL 
					AND cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as STRING)<>'0'
					AND SUBSTR(cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as STRING),5,2)<=12
				THEN from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(KRBM10T.FECREBRE as string), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.S'),'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(KRBM10T.FECREBRE),'YYYYMMDD')
			ELSE NULL
		END AS FCH_FALTA_PAGO,
		ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL, KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL ORDER BY KCIM06T.INULTSIT DESC) AS RN 
	FROM
	    bddlcru.KCIM06T AS KCIM06T
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				A.CDNUMPOL,
				A.INANCACO,
				COUNT(A.CDNUMPOL) AS CONT_ENDOSO
			FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T A
			WHERE
	    	A.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -1) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    	AND	A.TSCDC	<	current_date --SYSDATE
			AND SUBSTR(TRIM(A.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
			AND A.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
			GROUP BY A.CDNUMPOL, A.INANCACO) TABLA_ENDOSOS
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=TABLA_ENDOSOS.CDNUMPOL
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				B.CDNUMPOL,
				B.CTVRSPOL
			FROM
				bddlcru.KCIM06T B
			INNER JOIN
				(SELECT
					D.CDNUMPOL,
					max(cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(D.tscdc),'YYYYMMdd') as string)) AS ULTMODMAX -- MAX(TO_CHAR(D.TSCDC,'YYYYMMDD')) AS ULTMODMAX
				FROM
					bddlcru.KCIM06T D
				WHERE
	    			D.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3)-- SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    			AND	D.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    			AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(D.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    			AND	D.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	    			AND D.INULTSIT='U'
	    		GROUP BY D.CDNUMPOL
				)C
			ON B.CDNUMPOL=C.CDNUMPOL AND cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(B.TSCDC),'YYYYMMdd') as string)=C.ULTMODMAX
			WHERE
	    		B.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    		AND	B.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    		AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(B.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    		AND	B.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	    		AND B.INULTSIT='U'
			)E
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=E.CDNUMPOL
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				H.CDNUMPOL	AS	NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA,
				H.FEEFTONA	AS	FCH_INICIO_VIGENCIA_X_RENOVA,
				H.INANCACO	AS	NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA,
				CASE
					WHEN cast(H.FEEFTONA as STRING)='0' OR -- TO_CHAR(H.FEEFTONA)='0' OR
					SUBSTR(cast(H.FEEFTONA as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
					H.FEEFTONA IS NULL THEN NULL
					ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(H.FEEFTONA as string), 'YYYYMMdd'), 'YYYYMMdd') --TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(H.FEEFTONA),'YYYYMMDD')
				END 		AS	FCH_INICIO_VIG_X_RENOVA,
				CASE
					WHEN cast(H.FEVENCIM as STRING)='0' OR
					SUBSTR(cast(H.FEVENCIM as STRING),5,2)>12 OR
					H.FEVENCIM IS NULL THEN NULL
					ELSE from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(H.FEVENCIM as string), 'YYYYMMdd'), 'YYYYMMdd') -- TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(H.FEVENCIM),'YYYYMMDD')
				END 		AS	FCH_FIN_VIG_X_RENOVA
			FROM
				bddlcru.KCIM06T H
			INNER JOIN
				(SELECT
					F.CDNUMPOL,
					MIN(F.CTVRSPOL) AS MN_CTVRSPOL,
					F.INANCACO
				FROM
					bddlcru.KCIM06T F
				GROUP BY F.CDNUMPOL, F.INANCACO
				)G
			ON H.CDNUMPOL=G.CDNUMPOL AND H.CTVRSPOL=G.MN_CTVRSPOL AND H.INANCACO=G.INANCACO
			)I
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=I.NUM_POLIZA_X_RENOVA AND KCIM06T.INANCACO=I.NUM_RENOVACION_X_RENOVA
		LEFT OUTER JOIN
			(SELECT
				CDNUMPOL,
				CTVRSPOL,
				TCESREC,
				TCSBEREC,
				MAX(FECREBRE) AS FECREBRE
			FROM
				bddlcru.KRBM10T
			WHERE
				TCSBEREC='FP'
			GROUP BY 	CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,	TCESREC, TCSBEREC
			) KRBM10T
		ON KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL=KRBM10T.CDNUMPOL AND KCIM06T.CTVRSPOL=KRBM10T.CTVRSPOL
	WHERE
	    KCIM06T.TSCDC	>=	date_add(current_date(), -3) --SYSDATE	- 1 DAYS
	    AND	KCIM06T.TSCDC	<	current_date() --SYSDATE
	    AND	SUBSTR(TRIM(KCIM06T.CDPRODTE),1,1)	=	'A'
	    AND	KCIM06T.CDNUMPOL	IS NOT NULL
	) PRO_TGT

CREATE TABLE MES_ANT AS
SELECT anio_mes_contable, num_reclamacion, num_solicitud_tramite, id_solicitud, 
CASE WHEN num_solicitud_tramite = -999 THEN id_solicitud ELSE CAST(num_solicitud_tramite AS string) END AS tramite_siniestro,
ind_tramite_fondo_cashflow, 
CASE WHEN cve_unidad_pago IN ('U002', 'U099', 'U007') THEN 'MXP' ELSE cve_unidad_pago END AS cve_unidad_pago,
cve_modalidad, ramo, ramo_conjunto, cve_subconcepto_reserva, mto_importe_siniestral, mto_neto, 
num_poliza, num_poliza_cobranza, num_version_poliza, hosp_nom, hosp_gpo,
CASE 
WHEN hosp_nom = 'SOHIN' THEN 'Farm'
WHEN hosp_nom = 'ADM SALUD' THEN 'SAUX'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' AND hosp_gpo = 'Grupo Star Medica' THEN 'HM' 
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp' THEN 'Hosp'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp Extr' THEN 'Etranjero'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Farmacias' THEN 'Etranjero'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva IN ('RE','DH') AND cve_modalidad = 'RE' THEN 'RE'
WHEN id_proveedor = 0 OR hosp_tpo IN ('ND','Otro') OR hosp_tpo IS NULL AND cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' THEN 'HM'
ELSE 'SAUX'
END AS TIPO_GASTO
FROM bddldes.tmp_gmm_siniestros_5
WHERE id_solicitud <> '0092051333' AND anio_mes_contable >= 201811 AND anio_mes_contable <= 201910

SELECT count(*) FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT * FROM ( SELECT    DISTINCT    PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado,    PERFIL.num_poliza,    PERFIL.fch_vigencia_inicial,    PERFIL.fch_vigencia_final,      SEG.segmento,        INTEGRALIDAD.pol_autos,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_danos,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_salud,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_vida,        INTEGRALIDAD.poliza_total,        INTEGRALIDAD.prima_autos,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_danos,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_salud,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_vida,        INTEGRALIDAD.ramos        FROM       (SELECT        DISTINCT        num_poliza,        id_participante_consolidado,        fch_vigencia_inicial,        fch_vigencia_final                FROM bddldes.crm_01_tablero_perfil_sep19        WHERE cve_ramo = "AU"        AND cve_rol in ("TOM") ) AS PERFIL    LEFT JOIN    (SELECT        DISTINCT        id_participante_consolidado,        segmento                            FROM bddldes.crm_segmento_tom_sep19) AS SEG    ON SEG.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado        LEFT JOIN    (SELECT        DISTINCT        id_participante_consolidado,        pol_vida,        pol_danos,        pol_salud,        pol_autos,        poliza_total,        prima_vida,        prima_danos,        prima_salud,        prima_autos,        ramos                FROM bddldes.crm_02_tablero_integralidad_sep19        --WHERE tipo_integralidad = "RAMOS" --AND    ) AS INTEGRALIDAD    ON INTEGRALIDAD.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado     ORDER BY PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado )OJPO ORDER BY 1,2 ) AS JO

CREATE TABLE MES_ANT AS
SELECT anio_mes_contable, num_reclamacion, num_solicitud_tramite, id_solicitud, 
CASE WHEN num_solicitud_tramite = -999 THEN id_solicitud ELSE CAST(num_solicitud_tramite AS string) END AS tramite_siniestro,
ind_tramite_fondo_cashflow, 
CASE WHEN cve_unidad_pago IN ('U002', 'U099', 'U007') THEN 'MXP' ELSE cve_unidad_pago END AS cve_unidad_pago,
cve_modalidad, ramo, ramo_conjunto, cve_subconcepto_reserva, mto_importe_siniestral, mto_neto, 
num_poliza, num_poliza_cobranza, num_version_poliza, hosp_nom, hosp_gpo,
CASE 
WHEN hosp_nom = 'SOHIN' THEN 'Farm'
WHEN hosp_nom = 'ADM SALUD' THEN 'SAUX'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' AND hosp_gpo = 'Grupo Star Medica' THEN 'HM' 
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp' THEN 'Hosp'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp Extr' THEN 'Etranjero'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Farmacias' THEN 'Etranjero'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva IN ('RE','DH') AND cve_modalidad = 'RE' THEN 'RE'
WHEN id_proveedor = 0 OR hosp_tpo IN ('ND','Otro') OR hosp_tpo IS NULL AND cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' THEN 'HM'
ELSE 'SAUX'
END AS TIPO_GASTO

create table bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_salida as
SELECT
INANCACO                                				as vigencia_poliza
,pe.CDNUMPOL                            				as num_poliza
,''                                     				as num_endoso
,'' 													as num_poliza_cobranza
,pe.CTVRSPOL 											as num_version_poliza
,CTSECOBJ 												as contador_secuencia_objeto
,CDMCT 													as cve_cobertura_contratada
,descripcion 											as desc_cobertura_contratada
,CASE WHEN
(FEMISION=0 OR FEMISION IS NULL )
THEN
cast(14000101 as timestamp)
ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FEMISION as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'),
'yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss') as timestamp)
END												AS FCH_EMISION
,DSFORPAG  												as forma_pago
,CAST((IMPRNETA_SN - PRTECNIC_SN) AS DECIMAL(20,6))  	AS MTO_RECARGO_DESCUENTO
,IMPRNETA_SN											as mto_prima_neta
,IMCAAP15												as pct_pago_prima
,CASE WHEN
K16T.IMCAAP15 > 0
THEN
CAST(((IMPRNETA_SN * K16T.IMCAAP15) / 100) AS DECIMAL(20,6))
ELSE
CAST(IMPRNETA_SN AS DECIMAL(20,6))
END                                				AS MTO_PRIMA_NETA_SIN_PAGO_FRACC
,CAST((IMPRNETA_SN -
CASE WHEN
K16T.IMCAAP15 > 0
THEN
CAST(((IMPRNETA_SN * K16T.IMCAAP15) / 100) AS DECIMAL(20,6))
ELSE
CAST(IMPRNETA_SN AS DECIMAL(20,6))
END ) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) 					AS MTO_RECARGO_NVO_MET_PAGO
,PRTECNIC_SN as mto_prima_tecnica
,IMPREFRA_SN as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,IMPCESCOM   as mto_cesion_comision
,IMPGASTOS_SN as mto_derecho_poliza
,IMPIVA_SN as mto_iva_poliza
,(IMPRNETA_SN+IMPREFRA_SN+IMPGASTOS_SN+IMPIVA_SN+IMPCESCOM) as mto_prima_total
,cast(substring(CDRAMDGS,1,3) as varchar(3))  as cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(CAST(FECMVTO AS CHAR(8)),'yyyyMMdd'),'yyyy-MM-dd 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS FCH_CONTABLE
,CAST(SUBSTR(CAST(FECMVTO AS STRING),1,6) AS INT)	AS anio_mes_contable
,NVL(pe.segmento, '') as segmento,
NVL(pe.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento,
NVL(pe.negocio, '') as negocio,
NVL(pe.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio,
NVL(pe.bonos, '') as bonos,
NVL(pe.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos,
NVL(pe.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos,
NVL(pe.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr,
NVL(pe.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr,
NVL(pe.contrb, 0) as contrb,
NVL(pe.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest,
NVL(pe.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest,
NVL(pe.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc,
NVL(pe.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
from
bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base as pe
left join (
SELECT
cve_info,descripcion
from
bddlcru.cat_hom_515_286_287_clave_cob_contratada_afectada
where
trim(cve_info)!='' ) cats
on
trim(cats.cve_info) = trim(pe.CDMCT)
left join (
SELECT
trim(CDELEMEN) AS CDFORPAG,
TRIM(SUBSTR(DSELEMEN,1,30)) AS DSFORPAG
FROM
bddlcru.KTCTGET
WHERE
trim(CDTABLA)='KCIT27S' AND
trim(CDIDIOMA)='ES'
)  as cat
on  cat.CDFORPAG =  pe.TCFORPAG
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT distinct
CDNUMPOL,
CTVRSPOL,
IMCAAP15
FROM
bddlcru.kcim16t
WHERE
NURELREP = 1 AND
CDPRODTE LIKE 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct
CDNUMPOL,
CTVRSPOL,
IMCAAP15
FROM
bddlcru.kcim16h
WHERE
NURELREP = 1 AND
CDPRODTE LIKE 'G%'
) AS K16T
ON
pe.CDNUMPOL = K16T.CDNUMPOL	AND
pe.CTVRSPOL = K16T.CTVRSPOL

create table bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_42t
as
select
K42T.CDNUMPOL
,K42T.CTVRSPOL
,K42T.FECMVTO
,K42T.NUSECMVO
,K42T.CDNUMINT
,K42T.INGRPMVT
,K42T.TCCDMVTO
,KCIM06T.cdciagru
,KCIM06T.INANCACO
,KCIM06T.TCFORPAG
,KCIM06T.FEMISION,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDETISEG AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS SEGMENTO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETSEG.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_segmento,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDNEGMUL AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS NEGOCIO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMUL.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_negocio,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDTIPBON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS BONOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETBON.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_bonos,
CASE WHEN (KCIM06T.INPOLPAI = 'N') THEN 'True' ELSE 'False' END AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLCON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_CONTR,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPCO.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_contr,
CAST(gmmep.PORCONTR AS INT) AS CONTRB,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLPRE AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_PREST,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPPR.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_prest,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI AS STRING), '')AS STRING)  AS MOT_EXC,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMOT.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_mot_exc
from (SELECT *
FROM    bddlcru.kcin42t as K42T
where  K42T.INPROCES = 'S'
and K42T.FECMVTO between  20191001  and 20191031
)as K42T
inner join
(   SELECT distinct  cast(CDNUMPOL as 	char(14)) as CDNUMPOL,cast(CTVRSPOL as 	decimal(5,0)) as CTVRSPOL ,cast(INANCACO as decimal(2,0)) as INANCACO,cast(TCFORPAG as char(1)) as TCFORPAG
,cast(FEMISION as decimal(8,0)) as FEMISION,cast(feeftona as decimal(8,0)) as feeftona,cast(cdciagru as char(2)) as cdciagru, INPOLPAI as INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06T WHERE trim(cdciagru)='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT  distinct  cast(CDNUMPOL as 	char(14)) as CDNUMPOL,cast(CTVRSPOL as 	decimal(5,0)) as CTVRSPOL ,cast(INANCACO as decimal(2,0)) as INANCACO,cast(TCFORPAG as char(1)) as TCFORPAG
,cast(FEMISION as decimal(8,0)) as FEMISION,cast(feeftona as decimal(8,0)) as feeftona,cast(cdciagru as char(2)) as cdciagru, INPOLPAI as INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06H WHERE trim(cdciagru)='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
) AS KCIM06T
ON K42T.cdnumpol=KCIM06T.cdnumpol AND K42T.ctvrspol=KCIM06T.ctvrspol
left join bddlalm.gmm_elemento_poliza gmmep
on K42T.cdnumpol = TRIM(gmmep.num_poliza) and K42T.CTVRSPOL = gmmep.num_version
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGXG') as KTCTGETSEG on  CAST(trim(gmmep.CDETISEG) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETSEG.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KCDTECG') as KTCTGETMOT on  CAST(trim(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI) AS STRING)= trim(KTCTGETMOT.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGYG') as KTCTGETMUL on  CAST(trim(gmmep.CDNEGMUL) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETMUL.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGZG') as KTCTGETBON on  CAST(trim(gmmep.CDTIPBON) AS STRING)= trim(KTCTGETBON.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPCO on  CAST(trim(gmmep.INPOLCON) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETPCO.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPPR on  CAST(trim(gmmep.INPOLPRE) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETPPR.cdelemen)

sum(b.mto_total) as mto_total,

b.anio_mes_contable,

LEFT JOIN bddlapr.cnm_solicitud_pago AS B ON A.id_solicitud = B.id_solicitud

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU

ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

SELECT DISTINCT num_poliza,num_version,cve_sistema,cve_estatus_poliza,
fch_emision,fch_inicio_poliza,fch_vigencia_inicial,fch_vigencia_final,cve_forma_pago,cve_plan_comercial,mto_prima_neta,mto_prima_total,
cve_prod_tecnico,cve_prod_comercial,cve_moneda,cve_motivo_movimiento,cve_conducto_pago,mto_prima_pendiente_pago,mto_prima_total_deudor,
tipo_participante,id_participante_consolidado,ban_consolidado,nombres,apellido_paterno,apellido_materno,fch_nacimiento,cve_profesion,curp,
rfc,cve_nacionalidad,cve_actividad_economica,id_da,cve_da,cve_funcion_agente,tipo_participante_ag,rfc_ag,cve_nacionalidad_ag,nombres_ag,
apellido_paterno_ag,apellido_materno_ag,fch_nacimiento_ag,cve_profesion_ag,curp_ag,valor_medio_contacto_m,valor_medio_contacto_t,lada_int,
lada,calle,num_exterior,num_interior,punto_referencia,apartado_postal,id_direccion,est_direccion,ban_dir_principal,cve_tipo_direccion,cve_pais,
cve_estado,cve_municipio,cve_colonia,codigo_postal,est_direccion_participante,fecha_proceso FROM (
SELECT par_pol_medio_e_t.*,dir.rfc, dir.cve_nacionalidad, dir.calle, dir.num_exterior, dir.num_interior, dir.punto_referencia,
dir.apartado_postal, dir.id_direccion, dir.est_direccion, dir.ban_dir_principal, dir.cve_tipo_direccion, dir.cve_pais,
dir.cve_estado, dir.cve_municipio, dir.cve_colonia, dir.codigo_postal, dir.est_direccion_participante, 20191127 AS fecha_proceso
FROM (
SELECT par_pol_medio_e.*,mediot.valor_medio_contacto AS valor_medio_contacto_t, mediot.lada_int, mediot.lada
FROM (
SELECT parpolcontra_agen.*,medio.valor_medio_contacto AS valor_medio_contacto_m FROM  (
SELECT parpolcontra.*, agen.id_da,agen.cve_da, agen.cve_funcion_agente, agen.tipo_participante AS tipo_participante_ag,
agen.rfc AS rfc_ag, agen.cve_nacionalidad AS cve_nacionalidad_ag, agen.nombres AS nombres_ag, agen.apellido_paterno AS apellido_paterno_ag,
agen.apellido_materno AS apellido_materno_ag, agen.fch_nacimiento AS fch_nacimiento_ag, agen.cve_profesion AS cve_profesion_ag, agen.curp AS curp_ag
FROM (
SELECT parpol.*, contra.nombres, contra.apellido_paterno, contra.apellido_materno, contra.fch_nacimiento, contra.cve_profesion,
contra.curp, contra.cve_profesion AS cve_actividad_economica FROM (
SELECT par.tipo_participante, TRIM(par.id_participante_consolidado) AS id_participante_consolidado, par.id_participante,
par.ban_consolidado, crmpol.num_poliza, crmpol.num_version_ult_situacion AS num_version, crmpol.cve_sistema,
crmpol.cve_estatus_poliza, crmpol.fch_emision, crmpol.fch_inicio_poliza, crmpol.fch_vigencia_inicial,
crmpol.fch_vigencia_final, crmpol.cve_forma_pago, crmpol.cve_plan_comercial, crmpol.mto_prima_neta,
crmpol.mto_prima_total, crmpol.cve_prod_tecnico, crmpol.cve_prod_comercial, crmpol.cve_moneda, crmpol.cve_motivo_movimiento,
crmpol.cve_conducto_pago, crmpol.mto_prima_pendiente_pago, crmpol.mto_prima_total_deudor
FROM bddltrn.adc_t_crm_participante par
LEFT JOIN bddltrn.adc_t_crm_polizas crmpol
ON par.num_poliza = crmpol.num_poliza
) AS parpol
LEFT JOIN bddltrn.adc_t_crm_contratante contra
ON parpol.id_participante = contra.id_participante
) AS parpolcontra
LEFT JOIN bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_AGENTE agen
ON parpolcontra.num_poliza = agen.num_poliza
) AS parpolcontra_agen
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT valor_medio_contacto,id_participante,COUNT(id_participante) AS total
FROM bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_MEDIO_CONTACTO
WHERE cve_tipo_contacto = "MAIL"
GROUP BY valor_medio_contacto, id_participante
) AS medio
ON parpolcontra_agen.id_participante=medio.id_participante
) AS par_pol_medio_e
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT valor_medio_contacto, lada_int, lada, id_participante, COUNT(id_participante) AS total
FROM bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_MEDIO_CONTACTO
WHERE cve_tipo_contacto = "TLPT"
GROUP BY valor_medio_contacto, lada_int, lada, id_participante
) AS mediot
ON par_pol_medio_e.id_participante=mediot.id_participante
) AS par_pol_medio_e_t
LEFT JOIN bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_DIRECCION dir
ON par_pol_medio_e_t.id_participante=dir.id_participante AND par_pol_medio_e_t.num_poliza=dir.num_poliza
) AS glob

agen.apellido_materno AS apellido_materno_ag, agen.fch_nacimiento AS fch_nacimiento_ag, agen.cve_profesion AS cve_profesion_ag, agen.curp AS curp_ag
FROM (
SELECT parpol.*, contra.nombres, contra.apellido_paterno, contra.apellido_materno, contra.fch_nacimiento, contra.cve_profesion,
contra.curp, contra.cve_profesion AS cve_actividad_economica FROM (
SELECT par.tipo_participante, TRIM(par.id_participante_consolidado) AS id_participante_consolidado, par.id_participante,
par.ban_consolidado, crmpol.num_poliza, crmpol.num_version_ult_situacion AS num_version, crmpol.cve_sistema,
crmpol.cve_estatus_poliza, crmpol.fch_emision, crmpol.fch_inicio_poliza, crmpol.fch_vigencia_inicial,
crmpol.fch_vigencia_final, crmpol.cve_forma_pago, crmpol.cve_plan_comercial, crmpol.mto_prima_neta,
crmpol.mto_prima_total, crmpol.cve_prod_tecnico, crmpol.cve_prod_comercial, crmpol.cve_moneda, crmpol.cve_motivo_movimiento,
crmpol.cve_conducto_pago, crmpol.mto_prima_pendiente_pago, crmpol.mto_prima_total_deudor
FROM bddltrn.adc_t_crm_participante par
LEFT JOIN bddltrn.adc_t_crm_polizas crmpol
ON par.num_poliza = crmpol.num_poliza
) AS parpol
LEFT JOIN bddltrn.adc_t_crm_contratante contra
ON parpol.id_participante = contra.id_participante
) AS parpolcontra
LEFT JOIN bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_AGENTE agen
ON parpolcontra.num_poliza = agen.num_poliza
) AS parpolcontra_agen
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT valor_medio_contacto,id_participante,COUNT(id_participante) AS total
FROM bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_MEDIO_CONTACTO
WHERE cve_tipo_contacto = "MAIL"
GROUP BY valor_medio_contacto, id_participante
) AS medio
ON parpolcontra_agen.id_participante=medio.id_participante
) AS par_pol_medio_e
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT valor_medio_contacto, lada_int, lada, id_participante, COUNT(id_participante) AS total
FROM bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_MEDIO_CONTACTO
WHERE cve_tipo_contacto = "TLPT"
GROUP BY valor_medio_contacto, lada_int, lada, id_participante
) AS mediot
ON par_pol_medio_e.id_participante=mediot.id_participante
) AS par_pol_medio_e_t
LEFT JOIN bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_DIRECCION dir
ON par_pol_medio_e_t.id_participante=dir.id_participante AND par_pol_medio_e_t.num_poliza=dir.num_poliza
) AS glob

SELECT count(*) FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT * FROM ( SELECT    DISTINCT    PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado,    PERFIL.num_poliza,    PERFIL.fch_vigencia_inicial,    PERFIL.fch_vigencia_final,      SEG.segmento,        INTEGRALIDAD.pol_autos,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_danos,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_salud,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_vida,        INTEGRALIDAD.pol_total,        INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_autos,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_danos,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_salud,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_vida,        INTEGRALIDAD.ramos_comb        FROM       (SELECT        DISTINCT        num_poliza,        id_participante_consolidado,        fch_vigencia_inicial,        fch_vigencia_final                FROM bddldes.crm_01_tablero_perfil_jul19        WHERE cve_ramo = "AU"        AND cve_rol in ("TOM") ) AS PERFIL    LEFT JOIN    (SELECT        DISTINCT        id_participante_consolidado,        segmento                            FROM bddldes.crm_segmento_tom_jul19) AS SEG    ON SEG.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado        LEFT JOIN    (SELECT        DISTINCT        id_participante_consolidado,        pol_vida,        pol_danos,        pol_salud,        pol_autos,        pol_total,        prima_total_vida,        prima_total_danos,        prima_total_salud,        prima_total_autos,        ramos_comb                FROM bddldes.crm_tablero_integralidad_jul19        --WHERE tipo_integralidad = "RAMOS" --AND    ) AS INTEGRALIDAD    ON INTEGRALIDAD.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado     ORDER BY PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado )OJPO ORDER BY 1,2) AS JI

SELECT max (id) from bddladm.adm_monitor_blocks
SELECT max (id) from bddladm.adm_monitor_blocks

SELECT 
a.id_solicitud,
a.num_poliza,
a.num_version_poliza,
a.cve_cliente_origen,
a.nombre_asegurado,
a.apellido_paterno_asegurado,
a.apellido_materno_asegurado,
a.cve_sistema,
a.nombre_med_tratante,
a.apellido_paterno_med_tratante,
a.apellido_materno_med_tratante,
a.rfc_medico_tratante,
a.cve_pad_icd9_solicitud,
a.des_pad_icd9_solicitud,
a.cve_modalidad,
a.fch_ocurrencia_siniestro,
a.razon_social_proveedor,
b.num_orden_pago,
b.num_consecutivo_orden_pago,
b.num_reclamacion,
b.cve_tipo_gasto,
b.descr_tipo_gasto,
b.cve_estatus_pago,
b.descr_estatus_pago,
b.cve_cliente_origen_beneficiario,
sum(b.mto_total) as mto_total,
b.fch_contable,
b.anio_mes_contable,
b.num_factura_pago,
b.cve_medio_pago,
b.id_proveedor,
b.cve_subconcepto_reserva,
c.folio_comprobante,
d.cve_procedimiento,
d.des_procedimiento,
d.num_cons_procedimiento_aut
FROM cnm_solicitud A
LEFT JOIN bddlapr.cnm_solicitud_pago AS B ON A.id_solicitud = B.id_solicitud
LEFT JOIN cnm_comprobante AS C ON B.id_solicitud = C.id_solicitud 
                               AND B.num_orden_pago = C.num_orden_pago
                               AND B.num_consecutivo_orden_pago = C.num_consecutivo_orden_pago
LEFT JOIN cnm_procedimiento AS D ON A.id_solicitud = D.id_solicitud
--WHERE A.id_solicitud = '0077449692'
WHERE cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM'
AND  b.fch_contable between '2019-01-01 00:00:00' and '2019-10-31 00:00:00'
--and d.num_cons_procedimiento_aut = 1
GROUP BY 
a.id_solicitud,
a.num_poliza,
a.num_version_poliza,
a.cve_cliente_origen,
a.nombre_asegurado,
a.apellido_paterno_asegurado,
a.apellido_materno_asegurado,
a.cve_sistema,
a.nombre_med_tratante,
a.apellido_paterno_med_tratante,
a.apellido_materno_med_tratante,
a.rfc_medico_tratante,
a.cve_pad_icd9_solicitud,
a.des_pad_icd9_solicitud,
a.cve_modalidad,
a.fch_ocurrencia_siniestro,
a.razon_social_proveedor,
b.num_orden_pago,
b.num_consecutivo_orden_pago,
b.num_reclamacion,
b.cve_tipo_gasto,

Operation Text:
create table bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_salida as
SELECT
INANCACO                                				as vigencia_poliza
,pe.CDNUMPOL                            				as num_poliza
,''                                     				as num_endoso
,'' 													as num_poliza_cobranza
,pe.CTVRSPOL 											as num_version_poliza
,CTSECOBJ 												as contador_secuencia_objeto
,CDMCT 													as cve_cobertura_contratada
,descripcion 											as desc_cobertura_contratada
,CASE WHEN
(FEMISION=0 OR FEMISION IS NULL )
THEN
cast(14000101 as timestamp)
ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FEMISION as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'),
'yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss') as timestamp)
END												AS FCH_EMISION
,DSFORPAG  												as forma_pago
,CAST((IMPRNETA_SN - PRTECNIC_SN) AS DECIMAL(20,6))  	AS MTO_RECARGO_DESCUENTO
,IMPRNETA_SN											as mto_prima_neta
,IMCAAP15												as pct_pago_prima
,CASE WHEN
K16T.IMCAAP15 > 0
THEN
CAST(((IMPRNETA_SN * K16T.IMCAAP15) / 100) AS DECIMAL(20,6))
ELSE
CAST(IMPRNETA_SN AS DECIMAL(20,6))
END                                				AS MTO_PRIMA_NETA_SIN_PAGO_FRACC
,CAST((IMPRNETA_SN -
CASE WHEN
K16T.IMCAAP15 > 0
THEN
CAST(((IMPRNETA_SN * K16T.IMCAAP15) / 100) AS DECIMAL(20,6))
ELSE
CAST(IMPRNETA_SN AS DECIMAL(20,6))
END ) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) 					AS MTO_RECARGO_NVO_MET_PAGO
,PRTECNIC_SN as mto_prima_tecnica
,IMPREFRA_SN as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,IMPCESCOM   as mto_cesion_comision
,IMPGASTOS_SN as mto_derecho_poliza
,IMPIVA_SN as mto_iva_poliza
,(IMPRNETA_SN+IMPREFRA_SN+IMPGASTOS_SN+IMPIVA_SN+IMPCESCOM) as mto_prima_total
,cast(substring(CDRAMDGS,1,3) as varchar(3))  as cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(CAST(FECMVTO AS CHAR(8)),'yyyyMMdd'),'yyyy-MM-dd 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS FCH_CONTABLE
,CAST(SUBSTR(CAST(FECMVTO AS STRING),1,6) AS INT)	AS anio_mes_contable
,NVL(pe.segmento, '') as segmento,
NVL(pe.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento,
NVL(pe.negocio, '') as negocio,
NVL(pe.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio,
NVL(pe.bonos, '') as bonos,
NVL(pe.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos,
NVL(pe.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos,
NVL(pe.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr,
NVL(pe.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr,
NVL(pe.contrb, 0) as contrb,
NVL(pe.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest,
NVL(pe.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest,
NVL(pe.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc,
NVL(pe.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
from
bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base as pe
left join (
SELECT
cve_info,descripcion
from
bddlcru.cat_hom_515_286_287_clave_cob_contratada_afectada
where
trim(cve_info)!='' ) cats
on
trim(cats.cve_info) = trim(pe.CDMCT)
left join (
SELECT
trim(CDELEMEN) AS CDFORPAG,
TRIM(SUBSTR(DSELEMEN,1,30)) AS DSFORPAG
FROM
bddlcru.KTCTGET
WHERE
trim(CDTABLA)='KCIT27S' AND
trim(CDIDIOMA)='ES'
)  as cat
on  cat.CDFORPAG =  pe.TCFORPAG
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT distinct
CDNUMPOL,
CTVRSPOL,
IMCAAP15
FROM
bddlcru.kcim16t
WHERE
NURELREP = 1 AND
CDPRODTE LIKE 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct
CDNUMPOL,
CTVRSPOL,
IMCAAP15
FROM
bddlcru.kcim16h
WHERE
NURELREP = 1 AND
CDPRODTE LIKE 'G%'
) AS K16T
ON
pe.CDNUMPOL = K16T.CDNUMPOL	AND
pe.CTVRSPOL = K16T.CTVRSPOL

,(IMPRNETA_SN+IMPREFRA_SN+IMPGASTOS_SN+IMPIVA_SN+IMPCESCOM) as mto_prima_total
,cast(substring(CDRAMDGS,1,3) as varchar(3))  as cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(CAST(FECMVTO AS CHAR(8)),'yyyyMMdd'),'yyyy-MM-dd 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS FCH_CONTABLE
,CAST(SUBSTR(CAST(FECMVTO AS STRING),1,6) AS INT)	AS anio_mes_contable
,NVL(pe.segmento, '') as segmento,
NVL(pe.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento,
NVL(pe.negocio, '') as negocio,
NVL(pe.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio,
NVL(pe.bonos, '') as bonos,
NVL(pe.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos,
NVL(pe.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos,
NVL(pe.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr,
NVL(pe.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr,
NVL(pe.contrb, 0) as contrb,
NVL(pe.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest,
NVL(pe.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest,
NVL(pe.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc,
NVL(pe.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
from
bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base as pe
left join (
SELECT
cve_info,descripcion
from
bddlcru.cat_hom_515_286_287_clave_cob_contratada_afectada
where
trim(cve_info)!='' ) cats
on
trim(cats.cve_info) = trim(pe.CDMCT)
left join (
SELECT
trim(CDELEMEN) AS CDFORPAG,
TRIM(SUBSTR(DSELEMEN,1,30)) AS DSFORPAG
FROM
bddlcru.KTCTGET
WHERE
trim(CDTABLA)='KCIT27S' AND
trim(CDIDIOMA)='ES'
)  as cat
on  cat.CDFORPAG =  pe.TCFORPAG
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT distinct
CDNUMPOL,
CTVRSPOL,
IMCAAP15
FROM
bddlcru.kcim16t
WHERE
NURELREP = 1 AND
CDPRODTE LIKE 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct
CDNUMPOL,
CTVRSPOL,
IMCAAP15
FROM
bddlcru.kcim16h
WHERE
NURELREP = 1 AND
CDPRODTE LIKE 'G%'
) AS K16T
ON
pe.CDNUMPOL = K16T.CDNUMPOL	AND
pe.CTVRSPOL = K16T.CTVRSPOL

K300.*
,(K300.GASTOS1 + K300.GASTOS2 + K300.GASTOS3 +

K300.IMPIVA5 + K300.IMPIVA6 +
K300.GAIVA2  + K300.GAIVA3  +
K300.GAIVA4  + K300.GAIVA5  +

create table  bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_42t_45t_montos as
SELECT
K200.*
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE1) = 'GASTOS'   THEN K200.IMPDET1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GASTOS1
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE1) = 'IMREFRAC' THEN K200.IMPDET1 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMREFRAC1
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE1) = 'PRTECNIC' THEN K200.IMPDET1 ELSE 0 END ) AS PRTECNIC1
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE2) = 'GASTOS'   THEN K200.IMPDET2 ELSE 0 END ) AS GASTOS2
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE2) = 'IMREFRAC' THEN K200.IMPDET2 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMREFRAC2
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE2) = 'IPIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET2 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMPIVA2
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE2) = 'PRTECNIC' THEN K200.IMPDET2 ELSE 0 END ) AS PRTECNIC2
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE3) = 'GASTOS'   THEN K200.IMPDET3 ELSE 0 END ) AS GASTOS3
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE3) = 'IMREFRAC' THEN K200.IMPDET3 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMREFRAC3
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE3) = 'IPIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET3 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMPIVA3
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE4) = 'GASTOS'   THEN K200.IMPDET4 ELSE 0 END ) AS GASTOS4
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE4) = 'IMREFRAC' THEN K200.IMPDET4 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMREFRAC4
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE4) = 'IPIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET4 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMPIVA4
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE5) = 'GASTOS'   THEN K200.IMPDET5 ELSE 0 END ) AS GASTOS5
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE5) = 'IMREFRAC' THEN K200.IMPDET5 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMREFRAC5
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE5) = 'IPIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET5 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMPIVA5
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE6) = 'IPIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET6 ELSE 0 END ) AS IMPIVA6
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE2) = 'GARECFRA' THEN K200.IMPDET2 ELSE 0 END ) AS GARECFRA2
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE4) = 'GARECFRA' THEN K200.IMPDET4 ELSE 0 END ) AS GARECFRA4
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE5) = 'GARECFRA' THEN K200.IMPDET5 ELSE 0 END ) AS GARECFRA5
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE6) = 'GARECFRA' THEN K200.IMPDET6 ELSE 0 END ) AS GARECFRA6
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE2) = 'GAIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET2 ELSE 0 END ) AS GAIVA2
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE3) = 'GAIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET3 ELSE 0 END ) AS GAIVA3
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE4) = 'GAIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET4 ELSE 0 END ) AS GAIVA4
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE5) = 'GAIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET5 ELSE 0 END ) AS GAIVA5
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE6) = 'GAIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET6 ELSE 0 END ) AS GAIVA6
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE7) = 'GAIVA'    THEN K200.IMPDET7 ELSE 0 END ) AS GAIVA7
,(CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE1) = 'PRCEDIDA' THEN K200.IMPDET1
ELSE CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE2) = 'PRCEDIDA' THEN K200.IMPDET2
ELSE CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE3) = 'PRCEDIDA' THEN K200.IMPDET3
ELSE CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE4) = 'PRCEDIDA' THEN K200.IMPDET4
ELSE CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE5) = 'PRCEDIDA' THEN K200.IMPDET5
ELSE CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE6) = 'PRCEDIDA' THEN K200.IMPDET6
ELSE CASE WHEN TRIM(K200.TCCONDE7) = 'PRCEDIDA' THEN K200.IMPDET7
ELSE 0
END
END
END
END
END
END
END ) AS IMPCESCOM
from bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_42t_45t AS K200

create table  bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_42t_45t as
select
K42T.*,
k41t.CDRAMDGS AS CDRAMDGS_ANT,
POL.CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE AS CDRAMDGS
from
bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_42t_45t_int as K42T
left join
(select
num_poliza,
NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE
FROM
bddlapr.CNM_POLIZA
) POL
ON
K42T.cdnumpol=POL.NUM_POLIZA AND
K42T.ctvrspol=POL.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA
left join (
SELECT distinct
k41t.cdnumpol,
k41t.ctvrspol,
k41t.CDRAMDGS ,
k41t.CDMCT
from bddlcru.ktom41t k41t
inner join(
SELECT distinct
cast(CDNUMPOL as 	char(14)) as CDNUMPOL,
cast(CTVRSPOL as 	decimal(5,0)) as CTVRSPOL ,
cast(INANCACO as decimal(2,0)) as INANCACO,
cast(TCFORPAG as char(1)) as TCFORPAG,
cast(FEMISION as decimal(8,0)) as FEMISION,
cast(feeftona as decimal(8,0)) as feeftona,
cast(cdciagru as char(2)) as cdciagru
FROM
bddlcru.kcim06T
WHERE
trim(cdciagru)='SA'
and cdprodte like 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct
cast(CDNUMPOL as 	char(14)) as CDNUMPOL,
cast(CTVRSPOL as 	decimal(5,0)) as CTVRSPOL ,
cast(INANCACO as decimal(2,0)) as INANCACO,
cast(TCFORPAG as char(1)) as TCFORPAG,
cast(FEMISION as decimal(8,0)) as FEMISION,
cast(feeftona as decimal(8,0)) as feeftona,
cast(cdciagru as char(2)) as cdciagru
FROM
bddlcru.kcim06H
WHERE
trim(cdciagru)='SA'
and cdprodte like 'G%'
)
AS KCIM06T
ON
k41t.cdnumpol=KCIM06T.cdnumpol
AND k41t.ctvrspol=KCIM06T.ctvrspol
where
FECONTAB  between  20150601  and 20150630
and trim(CDRAMDGS) !=''
)
as k41t
ON K42T.cdnumpol=k41t.cdnumpol AND
K42T.ctvrspol=k41t.ctvrspol and
K42T.CDMCT=k41t.CDMCT

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM  ( SELECT      DISTINCT     PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado,     PERFIL.num_poliza,     PERFIL.fch_vigencia_inicial,     PERFIL.fch_vigencia_final,        SEG.segmento,          INTEGRALIDAD.pol_autos,     INTEGRALIDAD.pol_danos,     INTEGRALIDAD.pol_salud,     INTEGRALIDAD.pol_vida,          INTEGRALIDAD.pol_total,          INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_autos,     INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_danos,     INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_salud,     INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_vida,          INTEGRALIDAD.ramos_comb          FROM         (SELECT          DISTINCT         num_poliza,         id_participante_consolidado,         fch_vigencia_inicial,         fch_vigencia_final                  FROM bddldes.crm_01_tablero_perfil_jul19         WHERE cve_ramo = "AU"          AND cve_rol in ("TOM") ) AS PERFIL     LEFT JOIN     (SELECT          DISTINCT         id_participante_consolidado,         segmento                              FROM bddldes.crm_segmento_tom_jul19) AS SEG     ON SEG.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado          LEFT JOIN      (SELECT          DISTINCT         id_participante_consolidado,         pol_vida,         pol_danos,         pol_salud,         pol_autos,         pol_total,         prima_total_vida,         prima_total_danos,         prima_total_salud,         prima_total_autos,         ramos_comb                  FROM bddldes.crm_tablero_integralidad_jul19         --WHERE tipo_integralidad = "RAMOS" 		--AND      ) AS INTEGRALIDAD     ON INTEGRALIDAD.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado      ORDER BY PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado )OJPO --ORDER BY 1,2

create table bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_42t
as
select
K42T.CDNUMPOL
,K42T.CTVRSPOL
,K42T.FECMVTO
,K42T.NUSECMVO
,K42T.CDNUMINT
,K42T.INGRPMVT
,K42T.TCCDMVTO
,KCIM06T.cdciagru
,KCIM06T.INANCACO
,KCIM06T.TCFORPAG
,KCIM06T.FEMISION,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDETISEG AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS SEGMENTO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETSEG.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_segmento,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDNEGMUL AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS NEGOCIO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMUL.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_negocio,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDTIPBON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS BONOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETBON.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_bonos,
CASE WHEN (KCIM06T.INPOLPAI = 'N') THEN 'True' ELSE 'False' END AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLCON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_CONTR,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPCO.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_contr,
CAST(gmmep.PORCONTR AS INT) AS CONTRB,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLPRE AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_PREST,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPPR.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_prest,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI AS STRING), '')AS STRING)  AS MOT_EXC,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMOT.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_mot_exc
from (SELECT *
FROM    bddlcru.kcin42t as K42T
where  K42T.INPROCES = 'S'
and K42T.FECMVTO between  20191001  and 20191031
)as K42T
inner join
(   SELECT distinct  cast(CDNUMPOL as 	char(14)) as CDNUMPOL,cast(CTVRSPOL as 	decimal(5,0)) as CTVRSPOL ,cast(INANCACO as decimal(2,0)) as INANCACO,cast(TCFORPAG as char(1)) as TCFORPAG
,cast(FEMISION as decimal(8,0)) as FEMISION,cast(feeftona as decimal(8,0)) as feeftona,cast(cdciagru as char(2)) as cdciagru, INPOLPAI as INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06T WHERE trim(cdciagru)='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT  distinct  cast(CDNUMPOL as 	char(14)) as CDNUMPOL,cast(CTVRSPOL as 	decimal(5,0)) as CTVRSPOL ,cast(INANCACO as decimal(2,0)) as INANCACO,cast(TCFORPAG as char(1)) as TCFORPAG
,cast(FEMISION as decimal(8,0)) as FEMISION,cast(feeftona as decimal(8,0)) as feeftona,cast(cdciagru as char(2)) as cdciagru, INPOLPAI as INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06H WHERE trim(cdciagru)='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
) AS KCIM06T
ON K42T.cdnumpol=KCIM06T.cdnumpol AND K42T.ctvrspol=KCIM06T.ctvrspol
left join bddlalm.gmm_elemento_poliza gmmep
on K42T.cdnumpol = TRIM(gmmep.num_poliza) and K42T.CTVRSPOL = gmmep.num_version
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGXG') as KTCTGETSEG on  CAST(trim(gmmep.CDETISEG) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETSEG.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KCDTECG') as KTCTGETMOT on  CAST(trim(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI) AS STRING)= trim(KTCTGETMOT.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGYG') as KTCTGETMUL on  CAST(trim(gmmep.CDNEGMUL) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETMUL.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGZG') as KTCTGETBON on  CAST(trim(gmmep.CDTIPBON) AS STRING)= trim(KTCTGETBON.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPCO on  CAST(trim(gmmep.INPOLCON) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETPCO.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPPR on  CAST(trim(gmmep.INPOLPRE) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETPPR.cdelemen)

create table bddltrn.prima_emitida_asegurado_cobertura_base_42t
as
select
K42T.CDNUMPOL
,K42T.CTVRSPOL
,K42T.FECMVTO
,K42T.NUSECMVO
,K42T.CDNUMINT
,K42T.INGRPMVT
,K42T.TCCDMVTO
,KCIM06T.cdciagru
,KCIM06T.INANCACO
,KCIM06T.TCFORPAG
,KCIM06T.FEMISION,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDETISEG AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS SEGMENTO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETSEG.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_segmento,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDNEGMUL AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS NEGOCIO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMUL.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_negocio,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDTIPBON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS BONOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETBON.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_bonos,
CASE WHEN (KCIM06T.INPOLPAI = 'N') THEN 'True' ELSE 'False' END AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLCON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_CONTR,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPCO.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_contr,
CAST(gmmep.PORCONTR AS INT) AS CONTRB,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLPRE AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_PREST,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPPR.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_prest,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI AS STRING), '')AS STRING)  AS MOT_EXC,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMOT.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_mot_exc
from (SELECT *
FROM    bddlcru.kcin42t as K42T
where  K42T.INPROCES = 'S'
and K42T.FECMVTO between  20191001  and 20191031
)as K42T
inner join
(   SELECT distinct  cast(CDNUMPOL as 	char(14)) as CDNUMPOL,cast(CTVRSPOL as 	decimal(5,0)) as CTVRSPOL ,cast(INANCACO as decimal(2,0)) as INANCACO,cast(TCFORPAG as char(1)) as TCFORPAG
,cast(FEMISION as decimal(8,0)) as FEMISION,cast(feeftona as decimal(8,0)) as feeftona,cast(cdciagru as char(2)) as cdciagru, INPOLPAI as INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06T WHERE trim(cdciagru)='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT  distinct  cast(CDNUMPOL as 	char(14)) as CDNUMPOL,cast(CTVRSPOL as 	decimal(5,0)) as CTVRSPOL ,cast(INANCACO as decimal(2,0)) as INANCACO,cast(TCFORPAG as char(1)) as TCFORPAG
,cast(FEMISION as decimal(8,0)) as FEMISION,cast(feeftona as decimal(8,0)) as feeftona,cast(cdciagru as char(2)) as cdciagru, INPOLPAI as INPOLPAI

left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGYG') as KTCTGETMUL on  CAST(trim(gmmep.CDNEGMUL) AS STRING) = trim(KTCTGETMUL.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGZG') as KTCTGETBON on  CAST(trim(gmmep.CDTIPBON) AS STRING)= trim(KTCTGETBON.cdelemen)

SELECT DISTINCT * FROM  ( SELECT      DISTINCT     PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado,     PERFIL.num_poliza,     PERFIL.fch_vigencia_inicial,     PERFIL.fch_vigencia_final,        SEG.segmento,          INTEGRALIDAD.pol_autos,     INTEGRALIDAD.pol_danos,     INTEGRALIDAD.pol_salud,     INTEGRALIDAD.pol_vida,          INTEGRALIDAD.pol_total,          INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_autos,     INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_danos,     INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_salud,     INTEGRALIDAD.prima_total_vida,          INTEGRALIDAD.ramos_comb          FROM         (SELECT          DISTINCT         num_poliza,         id_participante_consolidado,         fch_vigencia_inicial,         fch_vigencia_final                  FROM bddldes.crm_01_tablero_perfil_jul19         WHERE cve_ramo = "AU"          AND cve_rol in ("TOM") ) AS PERFIL     LEFT JOIN     (SELECT          DISTINCT         id_participante_consolidado,         segmento                              FROM bddldes.crm_segmento_tom_jul19) AS SEG     ON SEG.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado          LEFT JOIN      (SELECT          DISTINCT         id_participante_consolidado,         pol_vida,         pol_danos,         pol_salud,         pol_autos,         pol_total,         prima_total_vida,         prima_total_danos,         prima_total_salud,         prima_total_autos,         ramos_comb                  FROM bddldes.crm_tablero_integralidad_jul19         --WHERE tipo_integralidad = "RAMOS" 		--AND      ) AS INTEGRALIDAD     ON INTEGRALIDAD.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado      ORDER BY PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado )OJPO ORDER BY 1,2

select count(*) from  bddldes.crm_cat_ingreso_codpost

select a.num_poliza,a.num_version,a.cve_negocio_operable,a.cve_codigo_promocion ,a.ID_NEGOCIO, a.VERSION_NEGOCIO,b.ID_NODO,c.ID_DETALLE_DOMINIO,c.VERSION_DETALLE_DOMINIO,a.cve_producto_personalizado, d.producto_personalizado_nombre from ( select a.num_poliza,a.num_version,a.cve_negocio_operable,a.cve_codigo_promocion,a.cve_producto_personalizado ,b.ID_NEGOCIO, b.VERSION_NEGOCIO from  bddldes.insumos_autos_p7 a  inner join  bddlorg.SCA_TESTRUCTURA_NEGOCIO_sqp AS b  on trim(a.cve_negocio_operable)=trim(b.ID_NEGOCIO_OPERABLE)  inner join  bddlorg.SCA_TNEGOCIO_sqp as c  on    b.ID_NEGOCIO = c.ID_NEGOCIO and b.VERSION_NEGOCIO =c.VERSION_NEGOCIO  and  a.fch_inicio_vigencia>= Cast(unix_timestamp(concat(substring(c.FECHA_INICIO,1,4),substring(c.FECHA_INICIO,6,2),substring(c.FECHA_INICIO,9,2),'000000'),'yyyyMMddHHmmss')  as timestamp)  and   a.fch_inicio_vigencia <=Cast(unix_timestamp(concat(substring(c.FECHA_FIN,1,4),substring(c.FECHA_FIN,6,2),substring(c.FECHA_FIN,9,2),'000000'),'yyyyMMddHHmmss')  as timestamp)  where a.num_poliza='00000271692360' ) a inner join   bddlorg.sca_tnodo_sqp  b on trim(a.cve_codigo_promocion)=trim(b.CODIGO_PROMOCION)    and a.ID_NEGOCIO = b.ID_NEGOCIO and a.VERSION_NEGOCIO =b.VERSION_NEGOCIO inner join bddlorg.sca_tdetalle_dominio_nodo_sqp c on       a.ID_NEGOCIO = c.ID_NEGOCIO and a.VERSION_NEGOCIO = c.VERSION_NEGOCIO and b.ID_NODO = c.ID_NODO and c.ID_DOMINIO=1 inner join bddlorg.SCA_TDOMINIO_COMBINACION_PAQUETE_sqp d on        c.ID_DETALLE_DOMINIO = d.ID_DETALLE_DOMINIO and  c.VERSION_DETALLE_DOMINIO =d.VERSION_DETALLE_DOMINIO and  TRIM(a.cve_producto_personalizado)=TRIM(d.PRODUCTO_PERSONALIZADO)

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

select "", CVE_SISTEMA, "", "", FCH_CONTABLE, "", "", TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM, "", "", MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL, "" FROM ( SELECT CVE_SISTEMA ,CAST(FCH_CONTABLE AS CHAR(10)) AS FCH_CONTABLE ,CAST(TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM AS DECIMAL(34,4)) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ,CAST(SUM(MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL) AS DECIMAL(34,3)) AS MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM (SELECT CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,AVG(TIPO_CAMBIO) OVER (PARTITION BY FCH_CONTABLE) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM,MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM BDDLALM.ALM_SOLICITUD_PAGO WHERE BAN_CONTABLE = 1 AND CVE_SISTEMA = 'INFO' AND FCH_CONTABLE <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),1) ) T GROUP BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ORDER BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE DESC LIMIT 5 UNION ALL SELECT CVE_SISTEMA ,CAST(FCH_CONTABLE AS CHAR(10)) AS FCH_CONTABLE ,CAST(TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM AS DECIMAL(34,4)) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ,CAST(SUM(MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL) AS DECIMAL(34,3)) AS MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM (SELECT CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,AVG(TIPO_CAMBIO) OVER (PARTITION BY FCH_CONTABLE) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM,MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM BDDLALM.ALM_SOLICITUD_PAGO WHERE BAN_CONTABLE = 1 AND CVE_SISTEMA = 'RCLA' AND FCH_CONTABLE <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),1) ) T GROUP BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ORDER BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE DESC LIMIT 5 ) AS D

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_CNM_PRIMA_EMITIDA_POLIZA_ENDOSO_DLT AS
SELECT
CASE WHEN anio_mes_contable=0 THEN 140001 ELSE anio_mes_contable END AS anio_mes_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_contable IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_contable END AS fch_contable,
num_poliza,
vigencia_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
num_poliza_cobranza,
num_endoso,
forma_pago,
cve_tipo_endoso,
mto_prima_tecnica,
mto_recargo_descuento,
mto_prima_neta,
mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
pct_pago_prima,
mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
mto_derecho_poliza,
mto_cesion_comision,
mto_iva_poliza,
mto_prima_total,
cve_cobertura_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_emision IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_emision END AS fch_emision,
NVL(segmento, '') AS segmento,
NVL(desc_segmento, '') AS desc_segmento,
NVL(negocio, '') AS negocio,
NVL(desc_negocio, '') AS desc_negocio,
NVL(bonos, '') AS bonos,
NVL(desc_bonos, '') AS desc_bonos,
NVL(plan_incentivos, '') AS plan_incentivos,
NVL(pol_contr, '') AS pol_contr,
NVL(desc_pol_contr, '') AS desc_pol_contr,
NVL(contrb, '') AS contrb,
NVL(pol_prest, '') AS pol_prest,
NVL(desc_pol_prest, '') AS desc_pol_prest,
NVL(mot_exc, '') AS mot_exc,
NVL(desc_mot_exc, '') AS desc_mot_exc,
cve_canal_venta_alterno,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''))) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''),
NVL(forma_pago,'') ,NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_tecnica AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_descuento AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_cesion_comision AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(pct_pago_prima AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_derecho_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_iva_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_total AS INT),0) AS STRING),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT),0) AS STRING))) as idmd5completo,
from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS FECHAAUD,
cve_sistema_int
FROM(
select * from  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_DLT
) AS STG_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA
ORDER BY fch_contable,num_poliza,num_version_poliza, cve_sistema_int

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_recibo_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    bddlalm.alm_recibo        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_INFO_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA as
SELECT
CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT) AS anio_mes_contable ,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_contable,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,7,2)," 00:00:00") AS timestamp) as fch_contable ,
CAST (num_poliza as varchar(14)) as num_poliza ,
CAST (indicador_vigencia as int) as vigencia_poliza,
CAST (num_version_poliza as int) as num_version_poliza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(8)) as num_poliza_cobranza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(6)) as num_endoso  ,
CAST (forma_pago as String) as forma_pago,
CAST ('' as varchar(3)) as cve_tipo_endoso,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_tecnica) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_tecnica,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_descuento) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_descuento,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta)AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_prima_neta,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado)AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
CAST (pct_pago_prima AS DECIMAL(11,6)) as pct_pago_prima ,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
CAST (SUM(mto_derecho_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_cesion_comision) AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_cesion_comision,
CAST (SUM(mto_iva_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_iva_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_total) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_total,
CAST(SUBSTR (cve_cobertura_contable,2,3) as varchar(3)) as cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_emision,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,7,2)) AS timestamp) as fch_emision,
CAST(segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS segmento,
CAST(desc_segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_segmento,
CAST(negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS negocio,
CAST(desc_negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_negocio,
CAST(bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS bonos,
CAST(desc_bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_bonos,
CAST(plan_incentivos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS plan_incentivos,
CAST(pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_contr,
CAST(desc_pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_contr,
CAST(contrb AS VARCHAR(300)) AS contrb,
CAST(pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_prest,
CAST(desc_pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_prest,
CAST(mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS mot_exc,
CAST(desc_mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_mot_exc,
'' as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS fechaaud,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(10)) AS cve_sistema_int
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER  as importe
group by num_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
anio_mes_contable,
cve_cobertura_contable,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
indicador_vigencia,
fecha_contable,
forma_pago,
fecha_emision,
pct_pago_prima
ORDER BY  fch_contable,cve_sistema_int,num_poliza,num_version_poliza

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER as
SELECT
substr(CAST(FECONTAB AS string),1,6) as anio_mes_contable,
CAST(FECONTAB as String) as fecha_contable,
CDNUMPOL as num_poliza,
CTVRSPOL as num_version_poliza,
INANCACO as indicador_vigencia,
CDMCT as cobertura_contable,
CDOBJTP as objeto_codigo,
CTSECOBJ as objeto_secuencia,
TCFORPAG as forma_pago,
SIGNO * PRTECNICA as mto_prima_tecnica,
SIGNO * (PRNETA - PRTECNICA)   as mto_recargo_descuento,
SIGNO * PRNETA  as mto_prima_neta,
SIGNO * (IMREFRAC1 + IMREFRAC2) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
PORCNFP as pct_pago_prima,
SIGNO * PRNETANFP as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CASE WHEN PORCNFP > 0 THEN SIGNO * (PRNETA  - PRNETANFP) else (SIGNO * PRNETA)  END as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
SIGNO * IMDERPOL as mto_derecho_poliza,
-1 * SIGNO * PRCEDIDA as mto_cesion_comision,
SIGNO * (IMIVA + GAIVA )as mto_iva_poliza,
SIGNO * (PRNETA - PRCEDIDA +IMREFRAC1 + IMREFRAC2 + IMDERPOL + IMIVA + GAIVA) as mto_prima_total,
CDRAMDGS as cve_cobertura_contable,
nvl(segmento,'') as segmento,
nvl(desc_segmento,'') as desc_segmento,
nvl(negocio,'') as negocio,
nvl(desc_negocio,'') as desc_negocio,
nvl(bonos,'') as bonos,
nvl(desc_bonos,'') as desc_bonos,
nvl(plan_incentivos,'') as plan_incentivos,
nvl(pol_contr,'') as pol_contr,
nvl(desc_pol_contr,'') as desc_pol_contr,
nvl(contrb,0) as contrb,
nvl(pol_prest,'') as pol_prest,
nvl(desc_pol_prest,'') as desc_pol_prest,
nvl(mot_exc,'') as mot_exc,
nvl(desc_mot_exc,'') as desc_mot_exc,
CAST(FEMISION as String) AS fecha_emision
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41T_FILTER  as ktom41t
order by fecha_contable, num_poliza,num_version_poliza

, NVL(cve_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cve_estado_recibo,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo,'')
, NVL(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago,''), NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago,'')
, NVL(CAST(imp.iva AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.recargos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.derechos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.prima_neta AS STRING),'')
, NVL(CAST(rec.mto_total_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,'')
, NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,''), NVL(CAST(rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza AS STRING),''), rec.num_poliza, NVL(rec.num_recibo,'')

))                                                      AS idmd5completo

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_poliza pol ON

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco ban ON
