FROM
(
Select * from bddltrn.agrupado_gaz0_polizahis_duplicados
) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat.dirplz,'') dirplz
, nvl(cat.cdedoplz,'')  cdedoplz
, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin
,cat.GRZCVE
FROM bddlcru.cat_cagente2 cat
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz
) agente
ON gaz.pol_cve_agente = agente.clnumfol
AND gaz.pol_fec_emision_join = agente.am_proc
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_414_estatus_poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) STATUS
ON STATUS.cve_azul = gaz.pol_status_emis
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom,descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_415_forma_de_pago where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) for_pago
on for_pago.cve_azul = gaz.pol_cve_pago
LEFT JOIN(
select trim(cve_hom) cve_hom, trim(descripcion) descripcion,trim(cve_azul) cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_148_Clave_Experiencia_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
)CAT_EXPERI
ON gaz.pol_cve_experiencia=CAT_EXPERI.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_594_Tipo_Administracion_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul<>''
)CAT_ADMIN
ON CAT_ADMIN.cve_azul= gaz.pol_tipo_admon
LEFT JOIN
(
select trim(cve_pool) cve_pool, trim(pool) pool from bddlcru.cat_pool
)CAT_POOL
ON gaz.pol_pool =  CAT_POOL.cve_pool
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ
on agente.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
(
select cdtiplan, clspln,PLNDSC from bddlcru.cat_cplanes
) CAT_TERRITO
ON CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_sramo_plan
LEFT JOIN
(
select a.cdtiplan , b.cve_hom , a.cirind, a.plndsc from bddlcru.cat_cplanes a inner join
bddlcru.cat_hom_72_181_426_587_circ_med b on a.cirind=b.descripcion
)CAT_CIRCULO  ON  gaz.pol_num_tipo = cast(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan as decimal(3,0))
LEFT JOIN
(
select psramcob,subsubco cve_cobertura_contable ,subdessu descripcion_cobertura_contable from bddlcru.cat_subramo
)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE
ON CAT_CVE_CONTABLE.psramcob=gaz.pol_sramo_cont
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
cat2.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat2.dirplz,'') as dirplz
, nvl(cat2.cdedoplz,'') as cdedoplz
, nvl(cat2.am_proc,'') as am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') as dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') as dsedoplz
, cat2.redterin as redterin
,cat2.GRZCVE
FROM
( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2
where clnumfol is not null
) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat2.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat2.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz)  obtiene_agente_min
on gaz.pol_cve_agente = obtiene_agente_min.clnumfol
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN
on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
bddlcru.cat_hom_460_subramo_admvo_pol cat_sramo
on gaz.pol_sramo_cont=cat_sramo.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN
ON CAT_PLAN.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_num_tipo
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)
WHERE gaz.ultimo_reg = 1

(
select trim(cve_pool) cve_pool, trim(pool) pool from bddlcru.cat_pool
)CAT_POOL

LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ

LEFT JOIN
(
select cdtiplan, clspln,PLNDSC from bddlcru.cat_cplanes
) CAT_TERRITO

LEFT JOIN
(
select a.cdtiplan , b.cve_hom , a.cirind, a.plndsc from bddlcru.cat_cplanes a inner join

)CAT_CIRCULO  ON  gaz.pol_num_tipo = cast(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan as decimal(3,0))
LEFT JOIN
(
select psramcob,subsubco cve_cobertura_contable ,subdessu descripcion_cobertura_contable from bddlcru.cat_subramo
)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE

, nvl(cat2.dirplz,'') as dirplz

, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') as dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') as dsedoplz
, cat2.redterin as redterin
,cat2.GRZCVE
FROM
( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,

LEFT JOIN

LEFT JOIN

select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN

LEFT JOIN

) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

INSERT INTO TABLE bddltrn.stg_poliza_azul
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) as num_poliza

, -999 AS num_version_poliza
, CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
, 'AZUL' AS cve_sistema

, nvl(for_pago.descripcion,'')    as des_forma_pago
, nvl(gaz.pol_cve_agente,'') AS cve_folio
, nvl(gaz.pol_razon_soc,'')   as des_folio
, NVL(
CAST(CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),5,2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),7,2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP),

) AS fch_ini_vigencia
, NVL(
CAST(CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),5,2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),7,2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP),

) AS fch_fin_vigencia

, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cve_hom,'')    AS cve_circulo_medico

) AS fch_emision

140001

, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da

, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')

RANK () over(partition by clnumfol

cat2

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cirind,'')   as des_nivel_hospital

, nvl(CAT_ADMIN.descripcion,'') as des_admon_poliza

, nvl( CAT_TERRITO.PLNDSC,'')  as des_gama_poliza
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_plan_gama
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.plndsc,'')  as  des_plan_gama
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_territorialidad
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.clspln,'')   as  des_territorialidad
, '' AS cve_canal_venta
, ''  as  des_canal_venta
, '' AS cve_segmento
, ''   as   des_segmento
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dirplz,0) else  nvl(agente.dirplz,0) end AS cve_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS des_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz,'') else  nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz,'') end AS cve_red_territorial
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.red_terr,'') else  nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ.red_terr,'') end AS des_red_territorial
, '' AS ban_preexistencia

, '' AS num_reg_producto

, '' AS cve_reg_producto

, ''    as    des_tipo_poliza

, '' AS cve_prod_comercial
, ''  as   des_prod_comercial
, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '')
, current_timestamp() AS ts_alta_hdfs
FROM
(
Select * from bddltrn.agrupado_gaz0_polizahis_duplicados
) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat.dirplz,'') dirplz
, nvl(cat.cdedoplz,'')  cdedoplz
, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin
,cat.GRZCVE
FROM bddlcru.cat_cagente2 cat
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz
) agente
ON gaz.pol_cve_agente = agente.clnumfol
AND gaz.pol_fec_emision_join = agente.am_proc
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_414_estatus_poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) STATUS
ON STATUS.cve_azul = gaz.pol_status_emis

(
select cve_hom,descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_415_forma_de_pago where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) for_pago
on for_pago.cve_azul = gaz.pol_cve_pago
LEFT JOIN(
select trim(cve_hom) cve_hom, trim(descripcion) descripcion,trim(cve_azul) cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_148_Clave_Experiencia_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
)CAT_EXPERI
ON gaz.pol_cve_experiencia=CAT_EXPERI.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN

select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_594_Tipo_Administracion_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul<>''
)CAT_ADMIN
ON CAT_ADMIN.cve_azul= gaz.pol_tipo_admon
LEFT JOIN
(
select trim(cve_pool) cve_pool, trim(pool) pool from bddlcru.cat_pool
)CAT_POOL
ON gaz.pol_pool =  CAT_POOL.cve_pool
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ
on agente.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
(
select cdtiplan, clspln,PLNDSC from bddlcru.cat_cplanes
) CAT_TERRITO
ON CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_sramo_plan
LEFT JOIN
(
select a.cdtiplan , b.cve_hom , a.cirind, a.plndsc from bddlcru.cat_cplanes a inner join
bddlcru.cat_hom_72_181_426_587_circ_med b on a.cirind=b.descripcion
)CAT_CIRCULO  ON  gaz.pol_num_tipo = cast(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan as decimal(3,0))
LEFT JOIN
(
select psramcob,subsubco cve_cobertura_contable ,subdessu descripcion_cobertura_contable from bddlcru.cat_subramo
)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE
ON CAT_CVE_CONTABLE.psramcob=gaz.pol_sramo_cont
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
cat2.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat2.dirplz,'') as dirplz
, nvl(cat2.cdedoplz,'') as cdedoplz
, nvl(cat2.am_proc,'') as am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') as dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') as dsedoplz
, cat2.redterin as redterin
,cat2.GRZCVE
FROM
( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2
where clnumfol is not null
) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz

on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN

on gaz.pol_sramo_cont=cat_sramo.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN
ON CAT_PLAN.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_num_tipo
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)
WHERE gaz.ultimo_reg = 1

INSERT INTO TABLE bddltrn.stg_poliza_azul
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) as num_poliza

, -999 AS num_version_poliza
, CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
, 'AZUL' AS cve_sistema

140001

, nvl(CAT_POOL.pool,'')   as  des_pool

, nvl(CAT_PLAN.plntpo,'')   as  des_plan

, ''   as   des_usuario

, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cirind,'')   as des_nivel_hospital

, nvl( CAT_TERRITO.PLNDSC,'')  as des_gama_poliza

, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.clspln,'')   as  des_territorialidad
, '' AS cve_canal_venta

, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dirplz,0) else  nvl(agente.dirplz,0) end AS cve_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS des_da

, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento

,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '')

,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '')

(

) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol

, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

LEFT JOIN

LEFT JOIN(

)CAT_EXPERI

)CAT_ADMIN

)CAT_POOL

LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz

)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE

LEFT JOIN
(

,cat2.GRZCVE

( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2

) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

LEFT JOIN
(

)CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN
on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
bddlcru.cat_hom_460_subramo_admvo_pol cat_sramo

LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN

LEFT JOIN
(

WHERE gaz.ultimo_reg = 1

, ''  as  des_canal_venta

, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da

,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '')

FROM
(
Select * from bddltrn.agrupado_gaz0_polizahis_duplicados
) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat.dirplz,'') dirplz
, nvl(cat.cdedoplz,'')  cdedoplz
, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin
,cat.GRZCVE
FROM bddlcru.cat_cagente2 cat
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz
) agente
ON gaz.pol_cve_agente = agente.clnumfol
AND gaz.pol_fec_emision_join = agente.am_proc
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_414_estatus_poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) STATUS
ON STATUS.cve_azul = gaz.pol_status_emis
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom,descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_415_forma_de_pago where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) for_pago
on for_pago.cve_azul = gaz.pol_cve_pago
LEFT JOIN(
select trim(cve_hom) cve_hom, trim(descripcion) descripcion,trim(cve_azul) cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_148_Clave_Experiencia_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
)CAT_EXPERI
ON gaz.pol_cve_experiencia=CAT_EXPERI.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_594_Tipo_Administracion_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul<>''
)CAT_ADMIN
ON CAT_ADMIN.cve_azul= gaz.pol_tipo_admon
LEFT JOIN
(
select trim(cve_pool) cve_pool, trim(pool) pool from bddlcru.cat_pool
)CAT_POOL
ON gaz.pol_pool =  CAT_POOL.cve_pool
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ
on agente.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
(
select cdtiplan, clspln,PLNDSC from bddlcru.cat_cplanes
) CAT_TERRITO
ON CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_sramo_plan
LEFT JOIN
(
select a.cdtiplan , b.cve_hom , a.cirind, a.plndsc from bddlcru.cat_cplanes a inner join
bddlcru.cat_hom_72_181_426_587_circ_med b on a.cirind=b.descripcion
)CAT_CIRCULO  ON  gaz.pol_num_tipo = cast(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan as decimal(3,0))
LEFT JOIN
(
select psramcob,subsubco cve_cobertura_contable ,subdessu descripcion_cobertura_contable from bddlcru.cat_subramo
)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE
ON CAT_CVE_CONTABLE.psramcob=gaz.pol_sramo_cont
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
cat2.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat2.dirplz,'') as dirplz
, nvl(cat2.cdedoplz,'') as cdedoplz
, nvl(cat2.am_proc,'') as am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') as dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') as dsedoplz
, cat2.redterin as redterin
,cat2.GRZCVE
FROM
( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2
where clnumfol is not null
) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat2.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat2.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz)  obtiene_agente_min
on gaz.pol_cve_agente = obtiene_agente_min.clnumfol
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN
on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
bddlcru.cat_hom_460_subramo_admvo_pol cat_sramo
on gaz.pol_sramo_cont=cat_sramo.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN
ON CAT_PLAN.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_num_tipo
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)
WHERE gaz.ultimo_reg = 1

(
select trim(cve_pool) cve_pool, trim(pool) pool from bddlcru.cat_pool
)CAT_POOL

LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ

LEFT JOIN
(
select cdtiplan, clspln,PLNDSC from bddlcru.cat_cplanes
) CAT_TERRITO

LEFT JOIN
(
select a.cdtiplan , b.cve_hom , a.cirind, a.plndsc from bddlcru.cat_cplanes a inner join

)CAT_CIRCULO  ON  gaz.pol_num_tipo = cast(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan as decimal(3,0))
LEFT JOIN
(
select psramcob,subsubco cve_cobertura_contable ,subdessu descripcion_cobertura_contable from bddlcru.cat_subramo
)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE

, nvl(cat2.dirplz,'') as dirplz

, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') as dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') as dsedoplz
, cat2.redterin as redterin
,cat2.GRZCVE
FROM
( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,

LEFT JOIN

LEFT JOIN

select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN

LEFT JOIN

) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

INSERT INTO TABLE bddltrn.stg_poliza_azul
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) as num_poliza

, -999 AS num_version_poliza
, CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
, 'AZUL' AS cve_sistema

, nvl(for_pago.descripcion,'')    as des_forma_pago
, nvl(gaz.pol_cve_agente,'') AS cve_folio
, nvl(gaz.pol_razon_soc,'')   as des_folio
, NVL(
CAST(CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),5,2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),7,2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP),

) AS fch_ini_vigencia
, NVL(
CAST(CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),5,2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),7,2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP),

) AS fch_fin_vigencia

, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cve_hom,'')    AS cve_circulo_medico

) AS fch_emision

140001

, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da

, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')

RANK () over(partition by clnumfol

cat2

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cirind,'')   as des_nivel_hospital

, nvl(CAT_ADMIN.descripcion,'') as des_admon_poliza

, nvl( CAT_TERRITO.PLNDSC,'')  as des_gama_poliza
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_plan_gama
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.plndsc,'')  as  des_plan_gama
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_territorialidad
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.clspln,'')   as  des_territorialidad
, '' AS cve_canal_venta
, ''  as  des_canal_venta
, '' AS cve_segmento
, ''   as   des_segmento
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dirplz,0) else  nvl(agente.dirplz,0) end AS cve_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS des_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz,'') else  nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz,'') end AS cve_red_territorial
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.red_terr,'') else  nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ.red_terr,'') end AS des_red_territorial
, '' AS ban_preexistencia

, '' AS num_reg_producto

, '' AS cve_reg_producto

, ''    as    des_tipo_poliza

, '' AS cve_prod_comercial
, ''  as   des_prod_comercial
, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '')
, current_timestamp() AS ts_alta_hdfs
FROM
(
Select * from bddltrn.agrupado_gaz0_polizahis_duplicados
) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat.dirplz,'') dirplz
, nvl(cat.cdedoplz,'')  cdedoplz
, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin
,cat.GRZCVE
FROM bddlcru.cat_cagente2 cat
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz
) agente
ON gaz.pol_cve_agente = agente.clnumfol
AND gaz.pol_fec_emision_join = agente.am_proc
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_414_estatus_poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) STATUS
ON STATUS.cve_azul = gaz.pol_status_emis

(
select cve_hom,descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_415_forma_de_pago where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) for_pago
on for_pago.cve_azul = gaz.pol_cve_pago
LEFT JOIN(
select trim(cve_hom) cve_hom, trim(descripcion) descripcion,trim(cve_azul) cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_148_Clave_Experiencia_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
)CAT_EXPERI
ON gaz.pol_cve_experiencia=CAT_EXPERI.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN

select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_594_Tipo_Administracion_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul<>''
)CAT_ADMIN
ON CAT_ADMIN.cve_azul= gaz.pol_tipo_admon
LEFT JOIN
(
select trim(cve_pool) cve_pool, trim(pool) pool from bddlcru.cat_pool
)CAT_POOL
ON gaz.pol_pool =  CAT_POOL.cve_pool
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ
on agente.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
(
select cdtiplan, clspln,PLNDSC from bddlcru.cat_cplanes
) CAT_TERRITO
ON CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_sramo_plan
LEFT JOIN
(
select a.cdtiplan , b.cve_hom , a.cirind, a.plndsc from bddlcru.cat_cplanes a inner join
bddlcru.cat_hom_72_181_426_587_circ_med b on a.cirind=b.descripcion
)CAT_CIRCULO  ON  gaz.pol_num_tipo = cast(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan as decimal(3,0))
LEFT JOIN
(
select psramcob,subsubco cve_cobertura_contable ,subdessu descripcion_cobertura_contable from bddlcru.cat_subramo
)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE
ON CAT_CVE_CONTABLE.psramcob=gaz.pol_sramo_cont
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
cat2.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat2.dirplz,'') as dirplz
, nvl(cat2.cdedoplz,'') as cdedoplz
, nvl(cat2.am_proc,'') as am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') as dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') as dsedoplz
, cat2.redterin as redterin
,cat2.GRZCVE
FROM
( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2
where clnumfol is not null
) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz

on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN

on gaz.pol_sramo_cont=cat_sramo.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN
ON CAT_PLAN.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_num_tipo
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)
WHERE gaz.ultimo_reg = 1

INSERT INTO TABLE bddltrn.stg_poliza_azul
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) as num_poliza

, -999 AS num_version_poliza
, CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
, 'AZUL' AS cve_sistema

140001

, nvl(CAT_POOL.pool,'')   as  des_pool

, nvl(CAT_PLAN.plntpo,'')   as  des_plan

, ''   as   des_usuario

, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cirind,'')   as des_nivel_hospital

, nvl( CAT_TERRITO.PLNDSC,'')  as des_gama_poliza

, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.clspln,'')   as  des_territorialidad
, '' AS cve_canal_venta

, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dirplz,0) else  nvl(agente.dirplz,0) end AS cve_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS des_da

, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento

,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '')

,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '')

(

) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol

, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

LEFT JOIN

LEFT JOIN(

)CAT_EXPERI

)CAT_ADMIN

)CAT_POOL

LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz

)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE

LEFT JOIN
(

,cat2.GRZCVE

( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2

) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

LEFT JOIN
(

)CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN
on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
bddlcru.cat_hom_460_subramo_admvo_pol cat_sramo

LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN

LPAD(CAST(pol.POLIZA_POLIZA AS VARCHAR(6)),6,"0"))
AS VARCHAR( 8))                                         NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA

, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(20))                 CURP

,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist

GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,conendoso_poliza,idnom_cont_poliza,rfc_poliza,nombre_poliza,telefono_poliza,fechemipoliza

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_POLIZA as
SELECT
SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),1,6) AS anio_mes_contable
,CAST('1400-01-01 00:00:00' AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_contable
,CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) AS num_poliza
,-999 AS vigencia_poliza
,-999 AS num_version_poliza
,CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
,'000000' AS num_endoso
,SDPOLIZA.FORMAPAGO_POLIZA AS cve_forma_pago
,'' AS cve_tipo_endoso
,0 AS mto_prima_tecnica
,SDPOLIZA.DESCVOL_POLIZA/100 AS mto_recargo_descuento
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_neta
,SDPOLIZA.RECARGO_POLIZA/100 AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,0 AS pct_pago_prima
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,0 AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,SDPOLIZA.GASTOS_POLIZA/100 AS mto_derecho_poliza
,0 AS mto_cesion_comision
,SDPOLIZA.IMPORIMP_POLIZA/100 AS mto_iva_poliza
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.RECARGO_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.IMPORIMP_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.DESCVOL_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.GASTOS_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_total
,COALESCE(CAT_SUBRAMO.SUBSUBCO,'') AS cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),7,2),' 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_emision
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '') as segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '') as negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '') as bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '') as contrb
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
)SDPOLIZA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SUBRAMO CAT_SUBRAMO
ON SDPOLIZA.SUBRAMO_POLIZA = CAT_SUBRAMO.PSRAMCOB
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
)SDPOLIZA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SUBRAMO CAT_SUBRAMO
ON SDPOLIZA.SUBRAMO_POLIZA = CAT_SUBRAMO.PSRAMCOB
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_POLIZA as
SELECT
SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),1,6) AS anio_mes_contable
,CAST('1400-01-01 00:00:00' AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_contable
,CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) AS num_poliza
,-999 AS vigencia_poliza
,-999 AS num_version_poliza
,CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
,'000000' AS num_endoso
,SDPOLIZA.FORMAPAGO_POLIZA AS cve_forma_pago
,'' AS cve_tipo_endoso
,0 AS mto_prima_tecnica
,SDPOLIZA.DESCVOL_POLIZA/100 AS mto_recargo_descuento
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_neta
,SDPOLIZA.RECARGO_POLIZA/100 AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,0 AS pct_pago_prima
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,0 AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,SDPOLIZA.GASTOS_POLIZA/100 AS mto_derecho_poliza
,0 AS mto_cesion_comision
,SDPOLIZA.IMPORIMP_POLIZA/100 AS mto_iva_poliza
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.RECARGO_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.IMPORIMP_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.DESCVOL_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.GASTOS_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_total
,COALESCE(CAT_SUBRAMO.SUBSUBCO,'') AS cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),7,2),' 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_emision
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '') as segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '') as negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '') as bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '') as contrb
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
)SDPOLIZA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SUBRAMO CAT_SUBRAMO
ON SDPOLIZA.SUBRAMO_POLIZA = CAT_SUBRAMO.PSRAMCOB
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

SELECT NDV(num_poliza) AS num_poliza, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(num_poliza)), AVG(length(num_poliza)), NDV(num_version) AS num_version, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), 4, CAST(4 as DOUBLE), NDV(cve_sistema) AS cve_sistema, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(cve_sistema)), AVG(length(cve_sistema)), NDV(cve_prod_tecnico) AS cve_prod_tecnico, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(cve_prod_tecnico)), AVG(length(cve_prod_tecnico)), NDV(cve_prod_comercial) AS cve_prod_comercial, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(cve_prod_comercial)), AVG(length(cve_prod_comercial)), NDV(cve_ramo) AS cve_ramo, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(cve_ramo)), AVG(length(cve_ramo)), NDV(descr_ramo) AS descr_ramo, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(descr_ramo)), AVG(length(descr_ramo)), NDV(cve_cobertura) AS cve_cobertura, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(cve_cobertura)), AVG(length(cve_cobertura)), NDV(desc_cobertura) AS desc_cobertura, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(desc_cobertura)), AVG(length(desc_cobertura)), NDV(fch_inicio_cob) AS fch_inicio_cob, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), 16, CAST(16 as DOUBLE), NDV(fch_fin_cob) AS fch_fin_cob, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), 16, CAST(16 as DOUBLE), NDV(suma_asegurada) AS suma_asegurada, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), 16, CAST(16 as DOUBLE), NDV(deducible) AS deducible, CAST(-1 as BIGINT), MAX(length(deducible)), AVG(length(deducible)) FROM m_crm_coberturas_autos

CREATE  TABLE IF NOT EXISTS bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_sdpoliza_cbza1 AS
SELECT
CAST(pol.POLORI_POLIZA        AS VARCHAR(14))                 NUM_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS smallint)                    VIGENCIA_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS INT)                         NUM_VERSION_POLIZA
, CAST(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(pol.OFNA_POLIZA   AS VARCHAR(2)),2,"0"),
LPAD(CAST(pol.POLIZA_POLIZA AS VARCHAR(6)),6,"0"))
AS VARCHAR( 8))                                         NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA
, CAST('000000' AS VARCHAR(6))                                  NUM_ENDOSO
, CAST(pol.idnom_cont_poliza    AS VARCHAR(10))                 CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN
, CAST('CBZA'                   AS VARCHAR( 4))                 CVE_SISTEMA
, CAST('CBZA'                   AS VARCHAR( 4))                 CVE_SISTEMA_INT
, CAST(pol.rfc_poliza           AS VARCHAR(16))                 RFC
, pol.nombre_poliza                                             NOMBRE
, pol.nombre_poliza                                             RAZON_SOCIAL
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(75))                 CORREO_ELECTRONICO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(20))                 CURP
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 3))                 CVE_PAIS_NACIMIENTO
, CAST(NULL                     AS STRING)                      NACIONALIDAD
, CAST(NULL                     AS STRING)                      NACIONALIDAD_RESIDENCIA
, CAST(
CASE
WHEN (lg_rfc > 3 AND regexp_extract(substr(pol.rfc_poliza,1,4), '^[A-Za-z]*$', 0) <> '')
THEN 'F'
WHEN (lg_rfc > 3 AND regexp_extract(substr(pol.rfc_poliza,1,4), '^[A-Za-z]*$', 0) = '')
THEN 'J'
ELSE NULL
END  AS VARCHAR( 1)
)                                                           CVE_TIPO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 1))                 CVE_SEXO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 1))                 CVE_ESTATUS
, CAST(pol.telefono_poliza      AS VARCHAR(75))                 TELEFONO1
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(75))                 TELEFONO2
, pol.fechemipoliza                                             FCH_ALTA
, CAST(NULL                     AS DECIMAL(8,0))                FCH_BAJA
, CAST(NULL                     AS TIMESTAMP)                   FECHAAUD
, CAST('C1'                     AS VARCHAR(2))                  ORI_CONTRATANTE
, pol.fechaaud                                                  TSULTMOD_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(32))                 IDMD5
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(32))                 IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,conendoso_poliza,idnom_cont_poliza,rfc_poliza,nombre_poliza,telefono_poliza,fechemipoliza, LENGTH(rfc_poliza) lg_rfc
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist, MAX(fechaaud) fechaaud
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,conendoso_poliza,idnom_cont_poliza,rfc_poliza,nombre_poliza,telefono_poliza,fechemipoliza
) pol

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'

insert overwrite   table bddlalm.alm_prima_pagada_poliza_asegurado_cobertura
Partition (anio_mes_partition = 201911, cve_sistema_partition='INFO')
SELECT
anio_mes_contable
,fch_contable
,cast(num_poliza as VARCHAR(14)) as num_poliza
,vigencia_poliza
,num_version_poliza
,num_poliza_cobranza
,num_endoso
,cast(CTSECOBJ as int ) as contador_secuencia_objeto
,cast(cve_asegurado as varchar(10))  as tcve_asegurado
,cve_cobertura_contratada
,des_cobertura_contratada as des_cobertura_contratada
,cast(identificador_nvo_renovado as varchar(10)) as identificador_nvo_renovado
,cve_cobertura_contable
,cve_forma_pago as forma_pago
,cast(mto_prima_tecnica as DECIMAL(23,3)) as mto_prima_tecnica
,cast(mto_recargo_descuento as DECIMAL(23,3))   as mto_recargo_descuento
,cast(mto_prima_neta as DECIMAL(23,3))  mto_prima_neta
,cast(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado as DECIMAL(23,3))   as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,cast(mto_gasto as DECIMAL(23,3))  as mto_gasto
,cast(mto_iva_poliza as DECIMAL(23,3)) as mto_iva_poliza
,cast(IMPRIMPAG as DECIMAL(23,3)) as mto_prima_total
,cast('' as VARCHAR(3) ) as cve_canal_venta_alterno
,NVL(segmento,'') as segmento
,NVL(desc_segmento,'') as desc_segmento
,NVL(negocio,'') as negocio
,NVL(desc_negocio,'') as desc_negocio
,NVL(bonos,'') as bonos
,NVL(desc_bonos,'') as desc_bonos
,NVL(plan_incentivos,'') as plan_incentivos
,NVL(pol_contr,'') as pol_contr
,NVL(desc_pol_contr,'') as desc_pol_contr
,NVL(contrb, 0) as contrb
,NVL(pol_prest,'') as pol_prest
,NVL(desc_pol_prest,'') as desc_pol_prest
,NVL(mot_exc,'') as mot_exc
,NVL(desc_mot_exc,'') as desc_mot_exc
, cast('INFO' as varchar(20)) as    sistorig
, cast( reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''),
CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,'')
)) as varchar(32)) as idmd5
, cast(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
concat(
NVL(anio_mes_contable ,''),
NVL(num_poliza,''),
CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''),
NVL(CTSECOBJ ,''),
NVL(cve_asegurado ,''),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contratada ,''),
NVL(des_cobertura_contratada ,''),
NVL(identificador_nvo_renovado ,''),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable ,''),
NVL(cve_forma_pago ,''),
NVL(mto_prima_tecnica ,''),
NVL(mto_recargo_descuento ,''),
NVL(mto_gasto ,''),
NVL(mto_iva_poliza ,''),
NVL(IMPRIMPAG ,'')
)) as varchar(32)) as idmd5completo
, from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as fechaaud
from BDDLTRN.campo_nuevo_renovado_final

NVL(mto_prima_tecnica ,''),
NVL(mto_recargo_descuento ,''),
NVL(mto_gasto ,''),
NVL(mto_iva_poliza ,''),
NVL(IMPRIMPAG ,'')
)) as varchar(32)) as idmd5completo
, from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as fechaaud
from BDDLTRN.campo_nuevo_renovado_final

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ACTIVIDAD_LABORAL_DELTA_EXTRACCION
SELECT DISTINCT
CASE WHEN ASEG.NUM_POLIZA IS NULL OR TRIM(ASEG.NUM_POLIZA) = '' THEN CAST('00000000000000' AS VARCHAR(14)) ELSE CAST(ASEG.NUM_POLIZA AS VARCHAR(14)) END AS NUM_POLIZA,
CASE WHEN ASEG.VIGENCIA_POLIZA IS NULL THEN CAST(0 AS SMALLINT) ELSE CAST(ASEG.VIGENCIA_POLIZA AS SMALLINT) END AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
CASE WHEN ASEG.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA IS NULL THEN CAST(0 AS INT) ELSE CAST(ASEG.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA AS INT) END AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
CASE WHEN ASEG.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA IS NULL OR TRIM(ASEG.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA) = '' THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(8)) ELSE CAST(ASEG.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA AS VARCHAR(8)) END AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CASE WHEN ASEG.CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN IS NULL OR TRIM(ASEG.CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN) = '' THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10)) ELSE CAST(ASEG.CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN AS VARCHAR(10)) END AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
KACM08T.CDACTLAB AS CVE_ACTIVIDAD_LABORAL,
KACM08T.DSACTLAB AS DES_ACTIVIDAD_LABORAL,
KACM08T.ININCEXC AS IND_ACTIVIDAD_LABORAL,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP())  AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_DELTA_COMISIONES_PAGADAS_POLIZA_ASEGURADO_COBERTURA
select DISTINCT
stg_1.anio_mes_contable	,
stg_1.fch_contable	,
stg_1.num_poliza	,
stg_1.vigencia_poliza	,
stg_1.num_version_poliza	,
stg_1.num_poliza_cobranza	,
stg_1.num_endoso	,
stg_1.contador_secuencia_objeto	,
stg_1.cve_cobertura_contratada	,
stg_1.des_cobertura_contratada	,
stg_1.cve_asegurado	,
stg_1.identificador_nvo_renovado	,
stg_1.cve_cobertura_contable	,
stg_1.forma_pago	,
stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta,
NVL((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_derecho_poliza,0)   as mto_comision_derecho_poliza	,
NVL((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado,0)	as mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
stg_1.mto_isr_comisiones	,
NVL(stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta +((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_derecho_poliza)+
((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado),0) as mto_importe_comision_total,
stg_1.cve_identificador_intermediario	,
stg_1.des_identificador_intermediario	,
stg_1.fecha_movimiento_comision	,
stg_1.cve_canal_venta_alterno	,
stg_1.porcentaje_comision	,

stg_1.desc_segmento,
stg_1.negocio,
stg_1.desc_negocio,
stg_1.bonos,
stg_1.desc_bonos,
stg_1.plan_incentivos,
stg_1.pol_contr,
stg_1.desc_pol_contr,
stg_1.contrb,
stg_1.pol_prest,
stg_1.desc_pol_prest,
stg_1.mot_exc,
stg_1.desc_mot_exc,

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_COMISIONES_PAGADA_POLIZA_ASEGURADO
select
CAST (amo_mes_conta AS INT)             					as anio_mes_contable,
case when fecha_contable = 0 or length (fecha_contable) <8 THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(fecha_contable as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) END fecha_contable ,
LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0')        		as num_poliza,
-999                                    					as vigencia_poliza,
-999                                    					as num_version_poliza,
LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')         	as num_poliza_cobranza,
cast (ENDOSO AS varchar(6))             					as num_endoso,
0                                       					as contador_secuencia_objeto,
COBERTURA                               					as cve_cobertura_contratada,
NVL(CAT.DESCRIPCION,'')                         			as descr_cobertura_contratada,
CAST (CERTIFICADO AS varchar(10))       					as cve_asegurado,
CAST (IDEN_NEW_RENOV AS varchar(10))    					as identificador_nvo_renovado,
CASE WHEN poliza.cve_cobertura_contable IS NULL THEN   cnm_poliza.cve_cobertura_contable else  poliza.cve_cobertura_contable end as cve_cobertura_contable,
FORMA_PAGO                              					as forma_pago,
NVL(PRIMA*(porciento_com/100),0)               				as mto_comision_prima_neta,
NVL(comis_gastos,0)                            				as mto_comision_derecho_poliza,
NVL(comis_recargo,0)                           				as mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
0                                       					as mto_isr_comisiones,
NVL((comis_neta+comis_recargo+comis_gastos),0) 				as mto_importe_comision_total,
''                                      					as cve_identificador_intermediario,
''                                      					as des_identificador_intermediario,
case when fecha_pag = 0 or length (fecha_pag) <8 THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(fecha_contable as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) END as fecha_movimiento_comision,
''                                      					as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
NVL(porciento_com,0)                        				as porcentaje_comision,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.segmento), '') as segmento,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_segmento), '') as desc_segmento,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.negocio), '') as negocio,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_negocio), '') as desc_negocio,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.bonos), '') as bonos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_bonos), '') as desc_bonos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.plan_incentivos), '') as plan_incentivos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.pol_contr), '') as pol_contr,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr), '') as desc_pol_contr,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.contrb), '') as contrb,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.pol_prest), '') as pol_prest,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest), '') as desc_pol_prest,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.mot_exc), '') as mot_exc,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc), '') as desc_mot_exc,
RECIBO														as Recibo,
CAST ("AZUL" AS varchar(20))            					as cve_sistema,
CAST ("AZUL" AS varchar(20))            					as cve_sistema_int,
amo_mes_conta                           					as periodo_proceso,
'pagada'                                					as tipo_comision
from (SELECT * FROM BDDLCRU.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL PRIMA2
where amo_mes_conta = 201911
) PRIMA
LEFT JOIN
(select CVE_AZUL,DESCRIPCION from bddlcru.cat_hom_515_286_287_clave_cob_contratada_afectada where CVE_AZUL <> "") CAT
ON  TRIM(PRIMA.COBERTURA) = TRIM(CAT.CVE_AZUL)
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza,num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from  BDDLAPR.CNM_POLIZA_AZUL) poliza
ON  LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') =  poliza.num_poliza
and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = poliza.num_poliza_cobranza
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from bddlapr.cnm_poliza where cve_sistema = 'CBZA') cnm_poliza
ON cnm_poliza.num_poliza_cobranza = LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on   LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

CAST ("AZUL" AS varchar(20))            					as cve_sistema_int,
amo_mes_conta                           					as periodo_proceso,
'pagada'                                					as tipo_comision
from (SELECT * FROM BDDLCRU.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL PRIMA2
where amo_mes_conta = 201911
) PRIMA
LEFT JOIN
(select CVE_AZUL,DESCRIPCION from bddlcru.cat_hom_515_286_287_clave_cob_contratada_afectada where CVE_AZUL <> "") CAT
ON  TRIM(PRIMA.COBERTURA) = TRIM(CAT.CVE_AZUL)
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza,num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from  BDDLAPR.CNM_POLIZA_AZUL) poliza
ON  LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') =  poliza.num_poliza
and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = poliza.num_poliza_cobranza
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from bddlapr.cnm_poliza where cve_sistema = 'CBZA') cnm_poliza
ON cnm_poliza.num_poliza_cobranza = LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on   LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_COMISIONES_PAGADA_POLIZA_ASEGURADO
select
CAST (amo_mes_conta AS INT)             					as anio_mes_contable,
case when fecha_contable = 0 or length (fecha_contable) <8 THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(fecha_contable as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) END fecha_contable ,
LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0')        		as num_poliza,
-999                                    					as vigencia_poliza,
-999                                    					as num_version_poliza,
LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')         	as num_poliza_cobranza,
cast (ENDOSO AS varchar(6))             					as num_endoso,
0                                       					as contador_secuencia_objeto,
COBERTURA                               					as cve_cobertura_contratada,
NVL(CAT.DESCRIPCION,'')                         			as descr_cobertura_contratada,
CAST (CERTIFICADO AS varchar(10))       					as cve_asegurado,
CAST (IDEN_NEW_RENOV AS varchar(10))    					as identificador_nvo_renovado,
CASE WHEN poliza.cve_cobertura_contable IS NULL THEN   cnm_poliza.cve_cobertura_contable else  poliza.cve_cobertura_contable end as cve_cobertura_contable,
FORMA_PAGO                              					as forma_pago,
NVL(PRIMA*(porciento_com/100),0)               				as mto_comision_prima_neta,
NVL(comis_gastos,0)                            				as mto_comision_derecho_poliza,
NVL(comis_recargo,0)                           				as mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
0                                       					as mto_isr_comisiones,
NVL((comis_neta+comis_recargo+comis_gastos),0) 				as mto_importe_comision_total,
''                                      					as cve_identificador_intermediario,
''                                      					as des_identificador_intermediario,
case when fecha_pag = 0 or length (fecha_pag) <8 THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(fecha_contable as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) END as fecha_movimiento_comision,
''                                      					as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
NVL(porciento_com,0)                        				as porcentaje_comision,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.segmento), '') as segmento,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_segmento), '') as desc_segmento,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.negocio), '') as negocio,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_negocio), '') as desc_negocio,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.bonos), '') as bonos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_bonos), '') as desc_bonos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.plan_incentivos), '') as plan_incentivos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.pol_contr), '') as pol_contr,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr), '') as desc_pol_contr,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.contrb), '') as contrb,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.pol_prest), '') as pol_prest,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest), '') as desc_pol_prest,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.mot_exc), '') as mot_exc,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc), '') as desc_mot_exc,
RECIBO														as Recibo,
CAST ("AZUL" AS varchar(20))            					as cve_sistema,
CAST ("AZUL" AS varchar(20))            					as cve_sistema_int,
amo_mes_conta                           					as periodo_proceso,

and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = poliza.num_poliza_cobranza
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from bddlapr.cnm_poliza where cve_sistema = 'CBZA') cnm_poliza
ON cnm_poliza.num_poliza_cobranza = LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')
LEFT JOIN

) EMAZ
on   LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

create table if not exists bddldes.bov_cifras1
as
Select
cast(A.CDSINIES as char(28)) AS NUM_SINIESTRO_RECLAMACION,
cast(B.CDFACTMI as char(8)) as FOLIO_SEGUIMIENTO_PROVEEDOR,
Cast(0 as char(8)) AS NUM_PAGO_FACTURA,
cast(E.NUMOVECO as char(12)) AS NUM_PETICION_PAGO,
cast('INFO' as  char(4) ) as CVE_SISTEMA ,
cast('A' as char(1))  as CVE_RAMO,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_CONTABLE,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_CAPTURA_SISTEMA_ORIGEN,
case when trim(C.TCCDMONE)='MXP' then cast('MXN' as char(4)) else case when  trim(C.TCCDMONE)='USD' then cast('USD' as char(4)) else cast('MXN' as char(4)) end end AS CVE_MONEDA,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_PAGO,
cast(D.CDREFCAB as char(20))  AS REFERENCIA_ASIENTO_CONTABLE,
cast(SUBSTR(E.CDCUENTA,2,4) as char(4)) AS TERMINACION_CUENTA_BANCARIA,
cast(Z.DESCRIPCION as char(50)) AS ENTIDAD_FINANCIERA,
cast(current_date() as timestamp) as TS_ALTA_AUDIT,
cast(current_date()  as timestamp) as TS_ACTUALIZA_AUDIT,
cast('DATALAKE' as char(12) ) as USUARIO_AUDIT
FROM  (select CDSINIES,TCTIPSIN from bddlcru.KSIM10T where TCTIPSIN = 'AU') as A
INNER join (select CDFACTMI,CDSINIES,TCTIPSIN,numoveco from bddlcru.KTOM14T  ) B   on
A.CDSINIES = B.CDSINIES
and A.TCTIPSIN = B.TCTIPSIN
and trim(b.CDFACTMI) <> ''
INNER join (select FECONTAB,CDSINIES,numoveco,NUMOVITO,CDREFCAB from bddlcru.ktom46t  ) d on
b.numoveco = D.numoveco
and D.FECONTAB >= '20190101'
inner join (select FEOPERA,TCCDMONE,FECHAEMI,CDSINIES,numoveco from bddlcru.KSIN30T  ) C on
b.CDSINIES = c.CDSINIES and b.numoveco = C.numoveco
inner join (select NUREFECA,CDCUENTA,CDSBANCO,numoveco from bddlcru.KTOM01T ) E on
b.numoveco = E.numoveco
LEFT  OUTER JOIN (SELECT cve_info,DESCRIPCION FROM bddlcru.cat_hom_146_bancos) Z ON
trim(E.CDSBANCO) =trim(Z.cve_info)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLALM.ALM_GASTO_TABULADO
SELECT DISTINCT
NVL(ID_SOLICITUD, ''),
NVL(CVE_SISTEMA_INT, ''),
NVL(CVE_SISTEMA, ''),
NVL(NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION, 0),
NVL(NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT, 0),
NVL(MTO_AUTORIZADO, 0.0),
NVL(MTO_RECLAMADO, 0.0),
NVL(MTO_TABULADO_UNITARIO, 0.0),
NVL(MTO_TABULADO, 0.0),
NVL(PCT_AUTORIZADO_TABULADOR, 0.0),
NVL(CVE_PROFESIONAL, ''),
TRIM(NVL(DESCR_PROFESIONAL, '')),
IND_TAB_AUTOMATICA,
TRIM(NVL(TCCDCPT, '')),
NVL(CDFILMED, ''),
TRIM(NVL(RFC_MEDICO, '')),
TRIM(NVL(APELLIDO_PATERNO_MEDICO, '')),
TRIM(NVL(APELLIDO_MATERNO_MEDICO, '')),
TRIM(NVL(NOMBRE_MEDICO, '')),
TRIM(NVL(RAZON_SOCIAL, '')),
NVL(CONVENIADO, ''),
TRIM(NVL(ESPECIALIDAD, '')),
TRIM(NVL(TCCDMONE, '')),
NVL(NUDOCUCO, ''),
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', CONCAT(NVL(ID_SOLICITUD,''),NVL(CVE_SISTEMA,''),NVL(NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,0),NVL(NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,0),NVL(CVE_PROFESIONAL,''))) AS IDMD5,

FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CMM_GASTO_TABULADO_UNION

b.numoveco = D.numoveco
and D.FECONTAB >= '20190101'
INNER join (select NUREFECA,CDCUENTA,CDSBANCO,numoveco from bddlcru.KTOM01T ) E on
b.numoveco = E.numoveco
LEFT  OUTER JOIN (SELECT cve_info,DESCRIPCION FROM bddlcru.cat_hom_146_bancos) Z ON
trim(E.CDSBANCO) =trim(Z.cve_info)

create table if not exists bddldes.bov_cifras2
as
select
cast(A.CDSINIES as char(28)) AS NUM_SINIESTRO_RECLAMACION,
cast(B.CDFACTMI as char(8)) as FOLIO_SEGUIMIENTO_PROVEEDOR,
Cast(0 as char(8)) AS NUM_PAGO_FACTURA,
cast(E.NUMOVECO as char(12)) AS NUM_PETICION_PAGO,
cast('INFO' as  char(4) ) as CVE_SISTEMA ,
cast('G' as char(1))  as CVE_RAMO,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_CONTABLE,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_CAPTURA_SISTEMA_ORIGEN,
case when trim(C.TCCDMONE)='MXP' then cast('MXN' as char(4)) else case when  trim(C.TCCDMONE)='USD' then cast('USD' as char(4)) else cast('MXN' as char(4)) end end AS CVE_MONEDA,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_PAGO,
cast(D.CDREFCAB as char(20))  AS REFERENCIA_ASIENTO_CONTABLE,
cast(SUBSTR(E.CDCUENTA,2,4) as char(4)) AS TERMINACION_CUENTA_BANCARIA,
cast(Z.DESCRIPCION as char(50)) AS ENTIDAD_FINANCIERA,
cast(current_date() as timestamp) as TS_ALTA_AUDIT,
cast(current_date()  as timestamp) as TS_ACTUALIZA_AUDIT,
cast('DATALAKE' as char(12) ) as USUARIO_AUDIT
FROM  (select CDSINIES,TCTIPSIN from bddlcru.KSIM10T where TCTIPSIN = 'SA') as A
INNER join (select CDFACTMI,CDSINIES,TCTIPSIN,numoveco,TCCDPAG from bddlcru.KTOM14T) B   on
A.CDSINIES = B.CDSINIES
and A.TCTIPSIN = B.TCTIPSIN
AND B.TCCDPAG NOT IN ('REE','REC')
and trim(b.CDFACTMI) <> ''
INNER join (select FEOPERA,TCCDMONE,FECHAEMI,CDSINIES,numoveco from bddlcru.KSIN30T ) C on
b.CDSINIES = c.CDSINIES and b.numoveco = C.numoveco
INNER join (select FECONTAB,CDSINIES,numoveco,NUMOVITO,CDREFCAB from bddlcru.ktom46t  ) d on
b.numoveco = D.numoveco
and D.FECONTAB >= '20190101'
INNER join (select NUREFECA,CDCUENTA,CDSBANCO,numoveco from bddlcru.KTOM01T ) E on
b.numoveco = E.numoveco
LEFT  OUTER JOIN (SELECT cve_info,DESCRIPCION FROM bddlcru.cat_hom_146_bancos) Z ON
trim(E.CDSBANCO) =trim(Z.cve_info)

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_DELTA_PRIMA_PAGADA_POLIZA_ASEGURADO
select DISTINCT
stg_1.anio_mes_contable,
stg_1.fch_contable,
stg_1.num_poliza,
stg_1.vigencia_poliza	,
stg_1.num_version_poliza,
stg_1.num_poliza_cobranza,
stg_1.num_endoso,
stg_1.contador_secuencia_objeto,
stg_1.cve_asegurado,
stg_1.cve_cobertura_contratada,
stg_1.des_cobertura_contratada,
stg_1.identificador_nvo_renovado,
stg_1.cve_cobertura_contable,
stg_1.forma_pago,
stg_1.mto_prima_tecnica,
NVL((stg_1.mto_recargo_descuento * stg_1.mto_prima_neta)/ stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta,0)	mto_recargo_descuento,
stg_1.mto_prima_neta,
NVL((stg_1.mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado * stg_1.mto_prima_neta)/ stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta,0) mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
NVL((stg_1.mto_derecho_poliza * stg_1.mto_prima_neta)/ stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta,0) mto_derecho_poliza,
NVL((stg_1.mto_iva_poliza * stg_1.mto_prima_neta)/ stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta,0) mto_iva_poliza,
NVL((NVL((stg_1.mto_derecho_poliza * stg_1.mto_prima_neta)/ stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta,0) + NVL((stg_1.mto_recargo_descuento * stg_1.mto_prima_neta)/ stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta,0) +
NVL((stg_1.mto_iva_poliza * stg_1.mto_prima_neta)/ stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta,0) + stg_1.mto_prima_neta),0) mto_prima_total,
stg_1.cve_canal_venta_alterno,
stg_1.segmento,
stg_1.desc_segmento,
stg_1.negocio,
stg_1.desc_negocio,
stg_1.bonos,
stg_1.desc_bonos,
stg_1.plan_incentivos,
stg_1.pol_contr,
stg_1.desc_pol_contr,
stg_1.contrb,
stg_1.pol_prest,
stg_1.desc_pol_prest,
stg_1.mot_exc,
stg_1.desc_mot_exc,
stg_1.cve_sistema	,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', concat(NVL(stg_1.num_poliza,''),NVL(stg_1.num_poliza_cobranza,''),NVL(stg_1.cve_asegurado,''),NVL(stg_1.cve_cobertura_contratada,''))) IDMD5,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', concat(CAST(nvl(stg_1.anio_mes_contable,0) AS STRING),NVL(stg_1.num_poliza,''),CAST(nvl(stg_1.vigencia_poliza,0) AS STRING),
CAST(nvl(stg_1.num_version_poliza,0) AS STRING),nvl(stg_1.num_poliza_cobranza,''),nvl(stg_1.num_endoso,''),CAST(nvl(stg_1.contador_secuencia_objeto,0) AS STRING),nvl(stg_1.cve_asegurado,''),nvl(stg_1.cve_cobertura_contratada,''),
nvl(stg_1.des_cobertura_contratada,''),nvl(stg_1.identificador_nvo_renovado,''),nvl(stg_1.cve_cobertura_contable,''),nvl(stg_1.forma_pago,''),CAST(nvl(stg_1.mto_prima_tecnica,0)AS STRING),CAST(nvl(stg_1.mto_recargo_descuento,0) AS STRING),
CAST(nvl(stg_1.mto_prima_neta,0) AS STRING),CAST(nvl(stg_1.mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,0) AS STRING),CAST(nvl(stg_1.mto_derecho_poliza,0) AS STRING),CAST(nvl(stg_1.mto_iva_poliza,0) AS STRING),
CAST(nvl(stg_1.mto_prima_total,0) AS STRING),nvl(stg_1.cve_canal_venta_alterno,''),nvl(stg_1.cve_sistema	,''))) IDMD5COMPLETO,
from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as fechaaud ,
STG_1.Recibo
from BDDLTRN.STG_PRIMA_PAGADA_POLIZA_ASEGURADO  stg_1
inner join
( select num_poliza,num_poliza_cobranza,num_endoso,recibo,sum(mto_prima_neta) sum_comi_prima_neta
from BDDLTRN.STG_PRIMA_PAGADA_POLIZA_ASEGURADO
group by num_poliza,num_poliza_cobranza,num_endoso,recibo ) stg_2
on  stg_1.num_poliza=stg_2.num_poliza
and stg_1.num_poliza_cobranza=stg_2.num_poliza_cobranza
and stg_1.num_endoso=stg_2.num_endoso
and stg_1.recibo = stg_2.recibo

create table if not exists bddldes.bov_cifras3
as select concat(
CAST(B.RCL_NUM as CHAR(20))  ,CAST(B.SLR_NUM_TMT as CHAR(8))) AS num_siniestro_reclamacion,
CAST(B.DOG_NUM as CHAR(8) ) AS folio_seguimiento_proveedor	,
cast(substring(C.CRQ_RFR,1,8)  as char(8)) AS num_pago_factura	,
cast(concat(CAST (F.CRQ_NUM as CHAR(6) ) ,  cast(F.CRQ_CNS as CHAR(2)) ) as CHAR(12))  AS NUM_PETICION_PAGO,
cast('RCLA' as char(4)) as cve_sistema	,
cast('G' as char(1)) AS cve_ramo	,
cast(C.IFP_FEC_APL_CON as timestamp) AS FECHA_CONTABLE,
cast(D.LTD_FEC_REC as timestamp) AS fecha_captura_sistema_origen,
CASE WHEN B.MON_CVE = 'U002'  THEN cast('MXN' as char(4) )  ELSE  cast('USD' as char(4)) END as cve_moneda ,
CAST (F.CRQ_FEC_PEI as timestamp) AS  FECHA_PAGO,
cast(C.IFP_NUM_LCN as char(20)) AS REFERENCIA_ASIENTO_CONTABLE,
case when trim(G.TKP_BCO_CVE) = '012'   then cast('4826' as char(4))  else
case when trim(G.TKP_BCO_CVE) = '002'   then cast('9390' as char(4))  else  cast('4826' as char(4))  end end  AS terminacion_cuenta_bancaria,
case when trim(G.TKP_BCO_CVE) = '012'  then cast('Bancomer' as char(50)) else
case when trim(G.TKP_BCO_CVE) = '002'  then cast('Banamex' as char(50)) else  cast('Bancomer' as char(50)) end end  AS entidad_financiera,
cast(current_date() as timestamp) as TS_ALTA_AUDIT,
cast(current_date()  as timestamp) as TS_ACTUALIZA_AUDIT,
cast('DATALAKE' as char(12) ) as USUARIO_AUDIT
FROM BDDLCRU.NRLTSLR0 A, BDDLCRU.NRLTDOG0 B, BDDLCRU.NRLTIFP0 C,BDDLCRU.NRLTLTD0 D,BDDLCRU.NRLTCBH0 E,BDDLCRU.NRLTCRQ0 F,BDDLCRU.NRLTTKP0 G
WHERE  C.IFP_FEC_APL_CON >= '2019-01-01'
AND SUBSTRING(D.LTD_ANU,1,2)  = 'PD'
and a.RCL_NUM = B.RCL_NUM
AND A.SLR_NUM_TMT = B.SLR_NUM_TMT
and A.RCL_NUM = C.RCL_NUM
AND F.CRQ_NUM= C.CRQ_NUM
AND F.CRQ_CNS= C.CRQ_CNS
AND A.SLR_NUM_TMT= C.SLR_TMT_NUM
AND B.LTD_NUM = D.LTD_NUM
AND B.LTD_ANU = D.LTD_ANU
AND B.DOG_FOL = E.DOG_FOL
AND B.LTD_ANU = E.LTD_ANU
AND B.LTD_NUM = E.LTD_NUM
AND E.CRQ_NUM= F.CRQ_NUM
AND E.CRQ_CNS= F.CRQ_CNS
AND E.CRQ_NUM= G.CRQ_NUM
AND E.CRQ_CNS= G.CRQ_CNS

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_PRIMA_PAGADA_POLIZA_ASEGURADO
select
CAST (amo_mes_conta AS INT)             					as amo_mes_conta,
case when fecha_contable = 0 or length (fecha_contable) <8 THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(fecha_contable as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) END fecha_contable ,
LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0')        		as num_poliza,
-999 														as vigencia_poliza,
-999 														as num_version_poliza,
LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')         	as num_poliza_cobranza,
cast (ENDOSO AS varchar(6))             					as num_endoso,
0 															as contador_secuencia_objeto,
CAST (CERTIFICADO AS varchar(10))       					as cve_asegurado,
COBERTURA 													as cve_cobertura_contratada,
NVL(CAT.DESCRIPCION,'')										as descr_cobertura_contratada,
CAST (IDEN_NEW_RENOV AS varchar(10))    					as identificador_nvo_renovado,
CASE WHEN poliza.cve_cobertura_contable IS NULL THEN   cnm_poliza.cve_cobertura_contable else  poliza.cve_cobertura_contable end as cve_cobertura_contable,
NVL(FORMA_PAGO,'')											as forma_pago,
0          													as mto_prima_tecnica,
NVL(RECARGO_ASEG,0) 										as mto_recargo_descuento,
NVL(PRIMA,0)  												as mto_prima_neta,
0 															as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
NVL(DERECHO_ASEG,0) 										as mto_derecho_poliza,
NVL(IVA1,0)    											    as mto_iva_poliza,
NVL(PRIMA_TOTAL_PAG,0)										as mto_prima_total,
ENDOSO_ORIGINAL_AJU   										as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.segmento), '') as segmento,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_segmento), '') as desc_segmento,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.negocio), '') as negocio,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_negocio), '') as desc_negocio,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.bonos), '') as bonos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_bonos), '') as desc_bonos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.plan_incentivos), '') as plan_incentivos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.pol_contr), '') as pol_contr,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr), '') as desc_pol_contr,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.contrb), '') as contrb,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.pol_prest), '') as pol_prest,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest), '') as desc_pol_prest,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.mot_exc), '') as mot_exc,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc), '') as desc_mot_exc,
RECIBO														as Recibo,
CAST ("AZUL" AS varchar(20))            					as cve_sistema
from (SELECT amo_mes_conta,fecha_contable,POLIZA_ORI,POLIZA_COB,ENDOSO,CERTIFICADO,COBERTURA,IDEN_NEW_RENOV,FORMA_PAGO,RECARGO_ASEG,PRIMA,
DERECHO_ASEG,IVA1,PRIMA_TOTAL_PAG,ENDOSO_ORIGINAL_AJU,RECIBO  FROM BDDLCRU.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL
where amo_mes_conta = 201911
) PRIMA
LEFT JOIN
(select CVE_AZUL,DESCRIPCION from bddlcru.cat_hom_515_286_287_clave_cob_contratada_afectada where CVE_AZUL <> "") CAT
ON  TRIM(PRIMA.COBERTURA) = TRIM(CAT.CVE_AZUL)
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza,num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from  BDDLAPR.CNM_POLIZA_AZUL) poliza
ON  LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') =  poliza.num_poliza
and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = poliza.num_poliza_cobranza
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from bddlapr.cnm_poliza where cve_sistema = 'CBZA') cnm_poliza
ON cnm_poliza.num_poliza_cobranza = LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

from (SELECT amo_mes_conta,fecha_contable,POLIZA_ORI,POLIZA_COB,ENDOSO,CERTIFICADO,COBERTURA,IDEN_NEW_RENOV,FORMA_PAGO,RECARGO_ASEG,PRIMA,
DERECHO_ASEG,IVA1,PRIMA_TOTAL_PAG,ENDOSO_ORIGINAL_AJU,RECIBO  FROM BDDLCRU.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL
where amo_mes_conta = 201911
) PRIMA
LEFT JOIN
(select CVE_AZUL,DESCRIPCION from bddlcru.cat_hom_515_286_287_clave_cob_contratada_afectada where CVE_AZUL <> "") CAT
ON  TRIM(PRIMA.COBERTURA) = TRIM(CAT.CVE_AZUL)
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza,num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from  BDDLAPR.CNM_POLIZA_AZUL) poliza
ON  LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') =  poliza.num_poliza
and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = poliza.num_poliza_cobranza
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from bddlapr.cnm_poliza where cve_sistema = 'CBZA') cnm_poliza
ON cnm_poliza.num_poliza_cobranza = LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

SELECT
