,0 AS imp_operaciones_crelint
,CAST( CRE.num_operaciones_cargadas AS INT) AS num_operaciones_cargadas
,CAST( CRE.imp_operaciones_cargadas AS DECIMAL(17,3)) AS imp_operaciones_cargadas
,CAST( MAE.num_operaciones_procesadas AS INT) AS num_operaciones_procesadas
,CAST( MAE.imp_operaciones_procesadas AS DECIMAL(17,3)) AS imp_operaciones_procesadas
,0 AS num_operaciones_cargadas_gcp
,0 AS imp_operaciones_cargadas_gcp
,0 AS num_operaciones_procesadas_adc
,0 AS imp_operaciones_procesadas_adc
,0 AS num_operaciones_alertadas
,20191127 AS FECHA_PROCESO
FROM (
SELECT COUNT(*) AS num_operaciones_cargadas, SUM(IMREMCCO) AS imp_operaciones_cargadas, FECHA_PROCESO
FROM bddlapr.adc_crelint_hist WHERE fecha_proceso = 20191127
GROUP BY fecha_proceso
) CRE
INNER JOIN (
SELECT COUNT(*) AS num_operaciones_procesadas, SUM(CRE.IMREMCCO) AS imp_operaciones_procesadas, CRE.Fecha_Proceso

INNER JOIN bddlapr.adc_alertascumplimiento_golden_record CRM

AND CRM.Fecha_Proceso = 20191127
INNER JOIN bddlapr.adc_alertascumplimiento_datos_info INF
ON CRE.CDNUMPOL = INF.NUM_POLIZA
AND INF.Fecha_Proceso = 20191127
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.cat_colonia col
on  CRM.CVE_COLONIA = TRIM(col.cve_colonia)
and CRM.CVE_ESTADO = TRIM(col.cve_estado)
WHERE   CRE.Fecha_Proceso = 20191127
GROUP BY CRE.Fecha_Proceso
) MAE
ON CRE.fecha_proceso = MAE.fecha_proceso

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_ASEGURADO_DATOS_ADICIONALES STORED AS RCFile AS
SELECT
IF(NUM_POLIZA IS NULL,'',NUM_POLIZA)                                               AS NUM_POLIZA,
CAST(IF(VIGENCIA_POLIZA IS NULL,'',VIGENCIA_POLIZA) AS SMALLINT)                   AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
IF(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA IS NULL,'',NUM_VERSION_POLIZA)                               AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
IF(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA IS NULL,'',NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA)                             AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
IF(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN IS NULL,'',TRIM(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN))                         AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
CVE_SISTEMA_INT                                                                    AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CVE_SISTEMA                                                                        AS CVE_SISTEMA,
IF(IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL IS NULL,'',IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL)                 AS IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,
IF(CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL IS NULL,'',CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL)                         AS CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,
IF(CAST(IND_OBJETO AS INT) IS NULL,0,IND_OBJETO)                                   AS IND_OBJETO,
IF(CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION IS NULL,'',CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION)                         AS CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION,
IF(ZONA_TARIFICACION IS NULL,'',ZONA_TARIFICACION)                                 AS ZONA_TARIFICACION,
IF(CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION IS NULL,'',CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION)               AS CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION,
IF(POBLACION IS NULL,'',POBLACION)                                                 AS POBLACION,
IF(ESTADO IS NULL,'',ESTADO)                                                       AS ESTADO,
IF(APELLIDO_PATERNO IS NULL,'',APELLIDO_PATERNO)                                   AS APELLIDO_PATERNO,
IF(APELLIDO_MATERNO IS NULL,'',APELLIDO_MATERNO)                                   AS APELLIDO_MATERNO,
IF(NOMBRE IS NULL,'',NOMBRE)                                                       AS NOMBRE,
IF(BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO IS NULL,'',BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO)                               AS BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO,
IF(CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO IS NULL,'',CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO)               AS CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,
IF(PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO IS NULL,'',PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO)                       AS PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,
IF( FCH_ALTA  IS NULL OR FCH_ALTA <14000101,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ALTA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))          AS FCH_ALTA,
IF( FCH_BAJA IS NULL OR FCH_BAJA   <14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_BAJA   as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))        AS FCH_BAJA,
IF( FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO  IS NULL OR FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO  <14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO  as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))   AS FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO,
IF( FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO IS NULL OR FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO <14000101  ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD<14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC<14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT <14000101,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA <14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA <14000101,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA,
IF( FCH_NACIMIENTO IS NULL OR FCH_NACIMIENTO <14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_NACIMIENTO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))   AS FCH_NACIMIENTO,
CAST(IF(CVE_SEXO IS NULL,'',CVE_SEXO) AS VARCHAR(1))                                                 AS CVE_SEXO,
IF(SEXO IS NULL,'',SEXO)                                                           AS SEXO,
CAST(IF(CVE_SEXO IS NULL,'',CVE_ESTATUS_ASEGURADO) AS VARCHAR(1))                                                 AS CVE_ESTATUS_ASEGURADO,
IF(SEXO IS NULL,'',ESTATUS_ASEGURADO)                                                           AS ESTATUS_ASEGURADO,
CAST(IF(IND_ULT_SITUACION IS NULL,'',IND_ULT_SITUACION) AS CHAR(1))                AS IND_ULT_SITUACION,
IF(IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE IS NULL,'',IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE)                     AS IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,
IF(TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE IS NULL,'',TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE)                             AS TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,
IF(IND_RELACION IS NULL,'',IND_RELACION)                                           AS IND_RELACION,
IF(RELACION IS NULL,'',RELACION)                                                   AS RELACION,
IF(IND_GRATUIDAD IS NULL,'',IND_GRATUIDAD)                                         AS IND_GRATUIDAD,
IF(GRATUIDAD IS NULL,'',GRATUIDAD)                                                 AS GRATUIDAD,
IF(CAST(EDAD_EQUIVALENTE AS STRING) IS NULL,'',EDAD_EQUIVALENTE)                   AS EDAD_EQUIVALENTE,
IF(CVE_ESTADO_CIVIL IS NULL,'',CVE_ESTADO_CIVIL)                                   AS CVE_ESTADO_CIVIL,
IF(ESTADO_CIVIL IS NULL,'',ESTADO_CIVIL)                                           AS ESTADO_CIVIL,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_DEPORTE AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_DEPORTE,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LAB_DEP AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LAB_DEP,
IF(IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE IS NULL,'',IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE)               AS IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_LABORAL AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_LABORAL,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LABORAL AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LABORAL,
CAST( IF(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD IS NULL, '0',PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD) AS STRING ) AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD,
CAST( IF(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD IS NULL, '0',PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD) AS STRING ) AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD,
IF(CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA IS NULL,'',CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA)             AS CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,
IF(TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA IS NULL,'',TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA)                     AS TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,
IF(VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD IS NULL,'',VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD)                             AS VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD,
IF( FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA IS NULL OR FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA<14000101  ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA,
IF( FCH_FIN_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA IS NULL OR FCH_FIN_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA<14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_FIN_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_FIN_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA,
IF(NOMBRE_OTRA_CIA IS NULL, '', NOMBRE_OTRA_CIA)                                   AS NOMBRE_OTRA_CIA,
CAST( PESO AS STRING )                                                             AS PESO,
CAST( TALLA AS STRING )                                                            AS TALLA,
IF(BAN_IMC IS NULL,'',BAN_IMC)                                                     AS BAN_IMC,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT AS STRING )                                               AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN AS STRING )                                               AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN,
IF(CVE_TIPO_DICTAMEN IS NULL,'',CVE_TIPO_DICTAMEN)                                 AS CVE_TIPO_DICTAMEN,
IF(TIPO_DICTAMEN IS NULL,'',TIPO_DICTAMEN)                                         AS TIPO_DICTAMEN,
IF(CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE IS NULL,'',CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE)                       AS CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,
CAST( IF(PCT_DESCUENTO IS NULL, 0, PCT_DESCUENTO)  AS STRING )                     AS PCT_DESCUENTO,
IF(BAN_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL IS NULL,'',BAN_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL)                       AS BAN_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL,
CAST( IMP_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL AS STRING )                                           AS IMP_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL,
IF(RFC_ASEGURADO IS NULL,'',RFC_ASEGURADO)                                         AS RFC_ASEGURADO,
IF(BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP IS NULL,'',BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP)                         AS BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP,
IF(BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                             AS BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,
IF(VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                             AS VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,
IF(DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                                     AS DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP())  AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CASE WHEN CVE_SISTEMA = 'INFO' THEN CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''), CAST(NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0) AS STRING), NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), NVL(CAST(IND_OBJETO AS STRING),''))) AS VARCHAR(32)) ELSE CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''), CAST(NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0) AS STRING), NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), NVL(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,''))) AS VARCHAR(32)) END AS IDMD5,
CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''),NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0),NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0),NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''),NVL(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,''),NVL(IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,''),NVL(CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,''),NVL(IND_OBJETO,''),NVL(CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION,''),NVL(ZONA_TARIFICACION,''),NVL(CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION,''),NVL(POBLACION,''),NVL(ESTADO,''),NVL(APELLIDO_PATERNO,''),NVL(APELLIDO_MATERNO,''),NVL(NOMBRE,''),NVL(BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO,''),NVL(CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,''),NVL(PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,''),NVL(CVE_SEXO,''),NVL(SEXO,''),NVL(IND_ULT_SITUACION,''),NVL(IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,''),NVL(TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,''),NVL(IND_RELACION,''),NVL(RELACION,''),NVL(IND_GRATUIDAD,''),NVL(GRATUIDAD,''),NVL(EDAD_EQUIVALENTE,0),NVL(CVE_ESTADO_CIVIL,''),NVL(ESTADO_CIVIL,''),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_DEPORTE,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LAB_DEP,0),NVL(IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,''),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_LABORAL,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LABORAL,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD,0),NVL(CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,''),NVL(TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,''),NVL(VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD,''),NVL(NOMBRE_OTRA_CIA,''),NVL(PESO,0),NVL(TALLA,0),NVL(BAN_IMC,''),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN,0),NVL(CVE_TIPO_DICTAMEN,''),NVL(TIPO_DICTAMEN,''),NVL(CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,''),NVL(PCT_DESCUENTO,0),NVL(BAN_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL,''),NVL(IMP_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL,0),NVL(RFC_ASEGURADO,''),NVL(BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP,''),NVL(BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,''),NVL(VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,''),NVL(DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,''))
)AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_UNION_ASEG_AD

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlapr.adc_alertascumplimiento_maestra
Partition (Fecha_Proceso)
SELECT
DISTINCT
from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(Concat(Cast(CRE.FECHAEMI as char(8)),'000000'),'yyyyMMddHHmmss'),'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')  AS fch_operacion
,CRE.CDUNIHIJ AS oficina_servicio
,CRE.IMREMCCO AS imp_pago_operacion
,CRE.TCCDMONE AS cve_moneda
,CRE.CDMEDPAG AS instrumento_monetario
,CRE.CDNUMPOL AS num_poliza
,CRE.CDCIAGRU AS ramo
,CRM.FCH_VIGENCIA_INICIAL AS fch_inicio_vigencia
,CRM.FCH_VIGENCIA_FINAL AS fch_fin_vigencia
,CAST( COALESCE(INF.des_producto,'') AS VARCHAR(60)) AS producto
,CRM.MTO_PRIMA_TOTAL AS prima_total_anualizada
,from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(Concat(Cast(CRE.FECHAEMI as char(8)),'000000'),'yyyyMMddHHmmss'),'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')  AS fch_ultimo_pago
,NULL AS valor_fondo_ahorro
,INF.suma_asegurada
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.NOMBRES_AG,'') AS VARCHAR(100)) AS nombre_agente
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.APELLIDO_PATERNO_AG,'') AS VARCHAR(30)) AS a_paterno_agente
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.APELLIDO_MATERNO_AG,'') AS VARCHAR(30)) AS a_materno_agente
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.CVE_DA,'') AS CHAR(4)) AS direccion_agencia
,CRE.CDUNIHIJ AS oficina_agente
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.RFC_AG, '') AS CHAR(16)) AS rfc_agente
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.CURP_AG,'') AS CHAR(23)) AS curp_agente
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.NOMBRES,'') AS VARCHAR(100)) AS nombre_contratante
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.APELLIDO_PATERNO,'') AS VARCHAR(30)) AS a_paterno_contratante
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.APELLIDO_MATERNO,'') AS VARCHAR(30)) AS a_materno_contratante
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.CVE_PROFESION,'') AS CHAR(4)) AS ocupacion_contratante
,INF.ingresos_declarados
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.VALOR_MEDIO_CONTACTO_M,'') AS VARCHAR(60)) AS email_contratante
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.calle,'') AS VARCHAR(60)) AS calle
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.num_exterior,'') AS CHAR(10)) AS num_exterior
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.num_interior,'') AS CHAR(10)) AS num_interior
,CAST( COALESCE( COALESCE(col.codigo_postal,CRM.codigo_postal),'') AS CHAR(8)) AS codigo_postal
,CAST( COALESCE(col.colonia,'') AS CHAR(80)) AS colonia
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.cve_municipio,'') AS CHAR(3)) AS cve_municipio
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.cve_estado,'') AS CHAR(2)) AS cve_estado
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.cve_pais,'') AS CHAR(3)) as pais
,CAST( CONCAT(TRIM(COALESCE(CRM.LADA_INT,'')), TRIM(COALESCE(CRM.LADA,'')), TRIM(COALESCE(CRM.VALOR_MEDIO_CONTACTO_T,''))) AS VARCHAR(69)) AS telefono
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.RFC,'') AS CHAR(16)) AS rfc_contratante
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.CURP,'') AS CHAR(23)) AS curp_contratante
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.CVE_NACIONALIDAD,'') AS VARCHAR(50)) AS nacionalidad_contratante
,CRM.FCH_NACIMIENTO AS fch_nacimiento_constitucion
,CRM.TIPO_PARTICIPANTE AS tipo_persona
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.CVE_PROFESION,'') AS CHAR(7)) AS actividad_economica
,Cast('OPR' AS CHAR(3)) AS estatus_alerta
,cAST('OPEREL' as CHAR(30)) AS des_estatus
,CRE.NUMOVECO AS num_cobro
,CRE.CDUNIHIJ AS num_oficina
,CRE.NUCAJA AS num_caja
,CRE.NUCORCAJ AS num_corte_caja
,CRE.FECHAEMI AS fch_emision
,CRE.CDFILPER AS cod_fil_pagador
,CRE.IMPORTPA AS imp_total_cobro
,CRE.TCCDMONE AS moneda_cobro
,CRE.CDMEDPAG AS cod_medio_pago
,CRE.TCFOMEPA AS medio_pago
,CRE.NUREFEDA AS detalle_medio_pago
,CRE.NUREFER AS num_referencia
,CRE.ESTADOCP AS estado_cobro
,CRE.CDTIPELE AS tipo_elemento
,CRE.CDNUMREC AS cve_agente
,CRE.CDREFELE AS num_rbfa
,CRE.CLCONCE AS cve_concepto
,CRE.IMTOTREC AS imp_total_recibo
,CRE.IMTORECO AS recibo_contraval
,CRE.IMREMECO AS imp_asociado
,CRE.IMREMCCO AS imp_medio_cobro
,CRE.NUMEDPAG AS cod_asoc_rb
,CRE.NUDOCUCO AS num_doc_cobro
,CRE.NUCOBPAR AS num_asoc_rb
,CRE.IMPORTCO AS imp_total_mcobro
,CRE.CDNUMPOL AS num_poliza_cobro
,CRE.CDFILPAG AS cod_filiacion_pag
,CRE.CDINTERM AS cod_intermediario
,CRE.CDCIAGRU AS linea_negocio
,CRE.CDUSUARI AS num_usuario
,CRE.TSULTMOD AS tsultmod
,CRM.ID_PARTICIPANTE_CONSOLIDADO AS id_cliente
,CAST( CONCAT( Nvl( TRIM( CRE.NUMOVECO ), ''), Nvl( CAST(CRE.FECHAEMI AS STRING), ''), Nvl( CAST(CRE.IMREMCCO AS STRING), ''), Nvl( TRIM( CRE.CDNUMPOL ), '') ) AS VARCHAR(55)) AS id_registro
,CAST( COALESCE(INF.localidad,'') AS CHAR(8)) AS localidad
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.CVE_PROD_COMERCIAL,'') AS CHAR(10)) AS cve_producto_comercial
,CAST( COALESCE(CRM.CVE_PROD_TECNICO,'') AS CHAR(10)) AS cve_producto_tecnico
,CAST( COALESCE(INF.cve_tipo_seguro,'') AS CHAR(1)) AS cve_tipo_seguro
,Cast(CRM.CVE_SISTEMA AS VARCHAR(30)) AS Campo1
,Cast('' AS VARCHAR(30)) AS Campo2
,Cast('' AS VARCHAR(30)) AS Campo3
,0 AS Campo4
,from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS Campo5
,20191127 AS Fecha_Proceso
FROM bddlapr.adc_crelint_hist CRE
INNER JOIN bddlapr.adc_alertascumplimiento_golden_record CRM
ON CRE.CDNUMPOL = CRM.NUM_POLIZA
AND CRM.Fecha_Proceso = 20191127
INNER JOIN BDDLAPR.adc_alertascumplimiento_datos_info INF
ON CRE.CDNUMPOL = INF.NUM_POLIZA
AND INF.Fecha_Proceso = 20191127
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.cat_colonia col
on  CRM.CVE_COLONIA = TRIM(col.cve_colonia)
and CRM.CVE_ESTADO = TRIM(col.cve_estado)
WHERE   CRE.Fecha_Proceso = 20191127

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_COMPROBANTE_delta
SELECT Z.*
FROM
(
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_COMPROBANTE           actual
INNER JOIN BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_COMPROBANTE_DELTA    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5
WHERE   NVL(actual.idmd5completo,'') <>  NVL(stg.idmd5completo,'')
UNION ALL
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_COMPROBANTE_DELTA        stg
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLALM.ALM_COMPROBANTE actual ON
stg.idmd5 = actual.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU

ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

SELECT

NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
RFC_HOSPITAL,
NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,

CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
DES_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,

PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CASE CVE_SISTEMA_INT WHEN 'INFO' THEN REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', NVL(ID_SOLICITUD, ''))
WHEN 'AZUL' THEN REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', CONCAT(ID_SOLICITUD, NVL(CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,''))) END AS IDMD5,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', concat(

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_COMPROBANTE_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_COMPROBANTE        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_COMPROBANTE_DELTA ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_FORMATEO
SELECT
CASE WHEN ID_SOLICITUD IS NULL OR TRIM(ID_SOLICITUD) = '' THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(11)) ELSE CAST(ID_SOLICITUD AS VARCHAR(11)) END AS ID_SOLICITUD,
CASE WHEN NUM_POLIZA IS NULL OR TRIM(NUM_POLIZA) = '' THEN CAST('00000000000000' AS VARCHAR(14)) ELSE CAST(NUM_POLIZA AS VARCHAR(14)) END AS NUM_POLIZA,
NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
CASE WHEN CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'INFO' THEN '' WHEN CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'AZUL' AND (TRIM(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA) = '' OR NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA IS NULL) THEN '' ELSE CAST(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA AS VARCHAR(8)) END AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
NUM_RENOVACION_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,
CASE WHEN CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN IS NULL OR TRIM(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN) = '' THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10)) ELSE CAST(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN AS VARCHAR(10)) END AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
CASE WHEN NUM_RECLAMACION IS NULL OR TRIM(NUM_RECLAMACION) = '' THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(15)) ELSE CAST(NUM_RECLAMACION AS VARCHAR(15)) END AS NUM_RECLAMACION,
CASE WHEN CVE_SISTEMA_INT IS NULL OR TRIM(CVE_SISTEMA_INT) = '' THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(4)) ELSE CAST(CVE_SISTEMA_INT AS VARCHAR(4)) END AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
DES_SISTEMA_INT,
CASE WHEN CVE_SISTEMA IS NULL OR TRIM(CVE_SISTEMA) = '' THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(4)) ELSE CAST(CVE_SISTEMA AS VARCHAR(4)) END AS CVE_SISTEMA,
DES_SISTEMA,
NOMBRE_MED_TRATANTE,
APELLIDO_PATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
APELLIDO_MATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
RFC_MEDICO_TRATANTE,
CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
DES_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
IND_TRAMITE_FONDO_CASHFLOW,
CVE_MODALIDAD,
CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
CASE WHEN FOLIO_SOLICITUD IS NULL THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(15)) ELSE CAST(FOLIO_SOLICITUD AS VARCHAR(15)) END AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
CVE_HOSPITAL_ORIGEN,
CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
DES_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
CVE_TIPO_EVENTO,
CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITALARIO,
CASE WHEN FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL IS NULL OR TRIM(FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL) = '1000-01-01' OR TRIM(FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL) = '--' THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING), 1, 4), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING), 6, 2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING), 9, 2))), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) AS TIMESTAMP) END AS FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL IS NULL OR TRIM(FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL) = '1000-01-01' OR TRIM(FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL) = '--' THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING), 1, 4), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING), 6, 2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING), 9, 2))), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) AS TIMESTAMP) END AS FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO IS NULL OR TRIM(FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO) = '1000-01-01' OR TRIM(FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO) = '--' THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO AS STRING), 1, 4), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO AS STRING), 6, 2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO AS STRING), 9, 2))), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) AS TIMESTAMP) END AS FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO IS NULL OR TRIM(FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO) = '1000-01-01' OR TRIM(FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO) = '--' THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO AS STRING), 1, 4), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO AS STRING), 6, 2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO AS STRING), 9, 2))), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) AS TIMESTAMP) END AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL IS NULL OR BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL < 0 THEN CAST('' AS VARCHAR(1)) ELSE CAST(BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL AS VARCHAR(1)) END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
DES_BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,

CASE WHEN FCH_DICTAMEN IS NULL OR TRIM(FCH_DICTAMEN) = '1000-01-01' OR TRIM(FCH_DICTAMEN) = '--' THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING), 1, 4), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING), 6, 2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING), 9, 2))), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) AS TIMESTAMP) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
DES_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
NVL(MTO_DEDUCIBLE, 0),
CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
NVL(PCT_COASEGURO, 0),
NVL(PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP, 0),
NVL(PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP, 0),
NVL(PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL, 0),
NVL(PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP, 0),
CTNUICD,
CDSECUEN
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_CATALOGOS

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_CATALOGOS
SELECT
ALMSOL.ID_SOLICITUD,
ALMSOL.NUM_POLIZA,
ALMSOL.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
ALMSOL.VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
ALMSOL.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
ALMSOL.NUM_RENOVACION_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
ALMSOL.CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,
ALMSOL.CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
ALMSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,
ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
COALESCE(CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN_INT.SISTEMA,'') AS DES_SISTEMA_INT,
ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA,
COALESCE(CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN.SISTEMA,'') AS DES_SISTEMA,
ALMSOL.NOMBRE_MED_TRATANTE,
ALMSOL.APELLIDO_PATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,

ALMSOL.IND_TRAMITE_FONDO_CASHFLOW,
ALMSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD,
ALMSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
ALMSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
ALMSOL.CVE_HOSPITAL_ORIGEN,
ALMSOL.CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
CASE ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT WHEN 'INFO' THEN NVL(CAT_CIR_INFO.DESCRIPCION, '') WHEN 'AZUL' THEN NVL(CAT_CIR_AZUL.DESCRIPCION, '') ELSE '' END AS DES_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
ALMSOL.CVE_TIPO_EVENTO,
ALMSOL.CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITALARIO,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO,
ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
ALMSOL.BAN_CAE,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_CAE WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_CAE,
ALMSOL.BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,
ALMSOL.BAN_CAB,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_CAB WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_CAB,
ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,
ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
ALMSOL.BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_URGENCIA WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_URGENCIA,
ALMSOL.BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,

ALMSOL.BAN_READMISION,

ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
ALMSOL.CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
ALMSOL.CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
ALMSOL.CVE_ACCIDENTE,
ALMSOL.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
ALMSOL.BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_MAMA_BIEN WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
ALMSOL.BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_BEBE_BIEN WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
ALMSOL.CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
ALMSOL.CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
ALMSOL.CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
ALMSOL.HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
ALMSOL.NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
ALMSOL.BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
CASE ALMSOL.BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO WHEN 1 THEN 'S' WHEN 0 THEN 'N' ELSE '' END AS DES_BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
COALESCE(RESDICT.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_DL,'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(RESDICT.DESCR_HOMOLOGADA_DL,'') AS DES_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
ALMSOL.CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
ALMSOL.CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
ALMSOL.CVE_AGENTE,
ALMSOL.CVE_DA_AGENTE,
ALMSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
ALMSOL.RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
ALMSOL.CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
ALMSOL.CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
ALMSOL.RFC_HOSPITAL,
ALMSOL.NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
ALMSOL.APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
ALMSOL.APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
ALMSOL.CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
CASE WHEN ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'INFO' THEN
CASE ALMSOL.CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN WHEN 'AP' THEN 'APROBADO' WHEN 'RC' THEN 'RECHAZADO' ELSE '' END
ELSE COALESCE(TRIM(EDLC.EDL_DES),'')
END AS DES_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
ALMSOL.MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
COALESCE(ALMSOL.CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,'') AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO,
ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
ALMSOL.CTNUICD,
ALMSOL.CDSECUEN
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_UNION  ALMSOL
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN_INT
ON ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN_INT.CVE_SISTEMA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN
ON ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA = CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN.CVE_SISTEMA
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT ICD_CVE,ICD_DES FROM BDDLCRU.GCCTICDC) CAT_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD
ON ALMSOL.CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD = TRIM(CAT_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD.ICD_CVE)
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.cat_hom_69_72_181_426_587_circ_med CAT_CIR_INFO
ON ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'INFO'
AND CAST(ALMSOL.CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO AS INT) = CAST(CAT_CIR_INFO.CVE_INFO AS INT)
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.cat_hom_69_72_181_426_587_circ_med CAT_CIR_AZUL
ON  ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'AZUL'
AND CAST(ALMSOL.CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO AS INT) = CAST(CAT_CIR_AZUL.CVE_SASS AS INT)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NRLTEDLC EDLC
ON TRIM(ALMSOL.CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN) = TRIM(EDLC.EDL_CVE)
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.CAT_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN_DL_NORM RESDICT
ON ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = CASE WHEN RESDICT.CVE_SISTEMA_INT='RCLA' THEN 'AZUL' ELSE RESDICT.CVE_SISTEMA_INT END
AND ALMSOL.CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN = RESDICT.CVE_ORIGEN

CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,

COALESCE(RESDICT.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_DL,'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(RESDICT.DESCR_HOMOLOGADA_DL,'') AS DES_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
ALMSOL.CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
ALMSOL.CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
ALMSOL.CVE_AGENTE,
ALMSOL.CVE_DA_AGENTE,
ALMSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,

ALMSOL.CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
ALMSOL.RFC_HOSPITAL,
ALMSOL.NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
ALMSOL.APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
ALMSOL.APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(ALMSOL.FCH_DICTAMEN AS STRING),7,2)) AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
ALMSOL.CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
CASE WHEN ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'INFO' THEN
CASE ALMSOL.CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN WHEN 'AP' THEN 'APROBADO' WHEN 'RC' THEN 'RECHAZADO' ELSE '' END
ELSE COALESCE(TRIM(EDLC.EDL_DES),'')
END AS DES_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
ALMSOL.MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
COALESCE(ALMSOL.CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,'') AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO,

ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
ALMSOL.PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
ALMSOL.CTNUICD,
ALMSOL.CDSECUEN
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_UNION  ALMSOL
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN_INT
ON ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN_INT.CVE_SISTEMA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN
ON ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA = CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN.CVE_SISTEMA

LEFT JOIN bddlcru.cat_hom_69_72_181_426_587_circ_med CAT_CIR_INFO
ON ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'INFO'
AND CAST(ALMSOL.CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO AS INT) = CAST(CAT_CIR_INFO.CVE_INFO AS INT)
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.cat_hom_69_72_181_426_587_circ_med CAT_CIR_AZUL
ON  ALMSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'AZUL'
AND CAST(ALMSOL.CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO AS INT) = CAST(CAT_CIR_AZUL.CVE_SASS AS INT)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NRLTEDLC EDLC
ON TRIM(ALMSOL.CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN) = TRIM(EDLC.EDL_CVE)
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.CAT_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN_DL_NORM RESDICT

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    BDDLCRU.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLINT.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_COMPROBANTE_DELTA
SELECT
FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
ID_SOLICITUD,
NUM_COMPROBANTE,
NUM_ORDEN_PAGO,
NUM_CONSECUTIVO_ORDEN_PAGO,
CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CVE_SISTEMA,
CVE_CODIGO_BENEFICIO,
DESCR_CODIGO_BENEFICIO,
RFC_PROVEEDOR,
RFC_HOSPITAL,
RFC_MEDICO,
MTO_TOTAL_MON_ORG,
MTO_IMPROCEDENTE_MON_ORG,
CVE_UNIDAD_MON_ORG,
DESCR_UNIDAD_MON_ORG,
FCH_APROBACION,
FCH_RECEPCION,
FCH_RECHAZO,
MTO_IMPROCEDENTE_MON_NAL,
MTO_PROCEDENTE_MON_NAL,
CVE_ESTATUS_COMPROBANTE,
DESCR_ESTATUS_COMPROBANTE,
FOLIO_COMPROBANTE,
FCH_INICIO,
FCH_FIN,
FCH_COMPROBANTE_GASTO,
CVE_MOTIVO_RECHAZO,
NUM_LOTE_COMPROBANTE_GTO,
PREF_LOTE_COMPROBANTE_GTO,
CVE_PROVEEDOR_ORIGEN,
CONT_GAS_COMPROBANTE,
MTO_IMPORTE_DESGLOSE,
MTO_ISR,
MTO_IVA,
MTO_IMPUESTO_RETENIDO,
MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
MTO_COASEGURO,
MTO_IVA_DEDUCIBLE,
MTO_IVA_COASEGURO,
MTO_DEDUCIBLE_SIN_IVA,
MTO_COASEGURO_SIN_IVA,
MTO_COASEGURO_HON_MED,
MTO_GASTO_NETO,
MTO_DESCUENTO,
MTO_RECLAMADO,
MTO_COASEGURO_HOSP,
MTO_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
MTO_IVA_COASEGURO_HOSP,
CVE_ESTATUS_GASTO,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_ASEGURADO_INFO_UNICO  STORED AS RCFile
AS select DDA1.* from
(select * from BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_INFO_ASEG_DATOS_ADICIONALES
) as DDA1
JOIN
(select num_poliza,VIGENCIA_POLIZA,NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,IND_OBJETO, max(nvl(fch_antiguedad_nac_ot_cia, 14000101)) as fch_antiguedad_nac_ot_cia
from BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_INFO_ASEG_DATOS_ADICIONALES
group by num_poliza,VIGENCIA_POLIZA,NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,IND_OBJETO) DDA2
ON DDA1.num_poliza = DDA2.NUM_POLIZA
AND DDA1.VIGENCIA_POLIZA=DDA2.VIGENCIA_POLIZA
AND DDA1.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA=DDA2.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA
AND DDA1.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA=DDA2.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA
AND DDA1.IND_OBJETO=DDA2.IND_OBJETO
AND DDA1.fch_antiguedad_nac_ot_cia = DDA2.fch_antiguedad_nac_ot_cia

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLINT.COMPROBANTE_RFC_PROVEEDOR
SELECT DISTINCT
CASE WHEN LOCATE('R', TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD), 1) = 0 THEN TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD) ELSE SUBSTRING(TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD),1,LOCATE('R', TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD), 1) -1) END AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD
,TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD) AS NUM_SOLICITUD, TRIM(STS.NUM_RECLAMACION) AS NUM_RECLAMACION, STS.ID_TRANSACCION
,SCSM.FOLIO_SOLICITUD_MEDICA, UPPER(SCSM.ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL) AS ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL
,TRIM(BCF.FOLIO_INTERNO_COMPROBANTE) AS FOLIO_INTERNO_COMPROBANTE, BCF.MTO_TOTAL_CFD, BCF.TS_EXPEDICION_CFD, TRIM(BCF.RFC_EMISOR) AS rfc_proveedor, BCF.RAZON_SOCIAL_EMISOR_FACTURA, TRIM(BCF.RFC_RECEPTOR) AS RFC_RECEPTOR, BCF.RAZON_SOCIAL_RECEPTOR_FACTURA
FROM BDDLCRU.SIN_TRAMITE_SINIESTRO STS
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.SIN_COMPROBANTE_SOLICITUD_MEDICA SCSM
ON STS.ID_TRANSACCION = SCSM.FOLIO_SOLICITUD_MEDICA
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT UPPER(ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL) AS ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL
,FOLIO_INTERNO_COMPROBANTE, MTO_TOTAL_CFD, TS_EXPEDICION_CFD, RFC_EMISOR, RAZON_SOCIAL_EMISOR_FACTURA, RFC_RECEPTOR, RAZON_SOCIAL_RECEPTOR_FACTURA
,RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY UPPER(ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL), FOLIO_INTERNO_COMPROBANTE ORDER BY TS_ALTA_AUDIT DESC) AS RNK_RFC
FROM BDDLCRU.BUF_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL
) BCF
ON BCF.RNK_RFC = 1
AND UPPER(SCSM.ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL) = BCF.ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL
WHERE TRIM(STS.CVE_TIPO_TRANSACCION) = '8'

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddltrn.stg_gmm_solicitud_circulo_med_rcla
SELECT DISTINCT
cm.ceo_cve
, cm.mda_cve
, cm.slr_num_fol
, cm.rfc_medico_tratante
, NVL(cm_duplicados.cve_circulo_medico, cm.cve_circulo_medico)
, cm.fch_registro_tramite
FROM bddltrn.stg_gmm_solicitud_circulo_med_rcla cm
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT ceo_cve, mda_cve, slr_num_fol, COUNT(cve_circulo_medico) cnt, -999 cve_circulo_medico
FROM bddltrn.stg_gmm_solicitud_circulo_med_rcla
GROUP BY ceo_cve, mda_cve, slr_num_fol
HAVING  cnt > 1
) cm_duplicados
ON  cm.ceo_cve = cm_duplicados.ceo_cve
AND cm.mda_cve = cm_duplicados.mda_cve
AND cm.slr_num_fol = cm_duplicados.slr_num_fol

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_delta
SELECT Z.*
FROM
(
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO           actual
INNER JOIN BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5
WHERE   NVL(actual.idmd5completo,'') <>  NVL(stg.idmd5completo,'')
UNION ALL
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA        stg
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLALM.ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO actual ON
stg.idmd5 = actual.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLORG.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL_SPLIT_MAP  AS
select
tipo_recibo,amo_mes_conta,endoso_original_aju,cobertura_contable,derecho_poliza,folio_fiscal,fecha_contable,fecha_pago,forma_pago,
iden_new_renov,iva1,prima_neta,prima_total_pag,cve_agente1,partici_agente1,cve_agente2,partici_agente2,porciento_com,poliza_ori,

IF(BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP IS NULL,'',BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP)                         AS BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP,
IF(BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                             AS BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,
IF(VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                             AS VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,
IF(DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                                     AS DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_ASEGURADO_ADICIONALES_COMPLEMENTO
SELECT max (id) from bddladm.adm_monitor_blocks
SELECT max (id) from bddladm.adm_monitor_blocks

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLORG.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL_NORMALIZER  AS
SELECT
cast(TIPO_RECIBO        	as VARCHAR(2)) TIPO_RECIBO,
cast(AMO_MES_CONTA      	as int) AMO_MES_CONTA,
cast(ENDOSO_ORIGINAL_AJU   	as VARCHAR(2)) ENDOSO_ORIGINAL_AJU,
cast(COBERTURA_CONTABLE 	as VARCHAR(3)) COBERTURA_CONTABLE,
cast(DERECHO_POLIZA     	as decimal (11,2))/100  DERECHO_POLIZA,
cast(FOLIO_FISCAL        	as VARCHAR(10))   FOLIO_FISCAL,
cast(FECHA_CONTABLE     	as int) FECHA_CONTABLE,
cast(FECHA_PAGO         	as int)FECHA_PAGO,
cast(FORMA_PAGO         	as VARCHAR(1))FORMA_PAGO,
cast(IDEN_NEW_RENOV     	as VARCHAR(2))IDEN_NEW_RENOV,
cast(IVA1              		as decimal (11,2))/100 IVA1,
cast(PRIMA_NETA        		as decimal (11,2))/100 PRIMA_NETA,
cast(PRIMA_TOTAL_PAG   		as decimal (11,2))/100 PRIMA_TOTAL_PAG,
cast(CVE_AGENTE1       		as int)CVE_AGENTE1,
cast(PARTICI_AGENTE1   		as decimal (6,2))/100 PARTICI_AGENTE1,
cast(CVE_AGENTE2       		as int)CVE_AGENTE2,
cast(PARTICI_AGENTE2   		as decimal (6,2))/100  PARTICI_AGENTE2,
cast(PORCIENTO_COM     		as decimal (6,2))/100  PORCIENTO_COM,
cast(POLIZA_ORI        		as int) POLIZA_ORI,
cast(POLIZA_COB 			as int) POLIZA_COB,
cast(ENDOSO     			as int) ENDOSO,
cast(RECIBO     			as int) RECIBO,
cast(FEC_INI_REC			as int) FEC_INI_REC,
cast(FEC_FIN_REC			as int) FEC_FIN_REC,
cast(FECHA_PAG  			as int) FECHA_PAG,
cast(CERTIFICADO	        as VARCHAR(8)) CERTIFICADO,
cast(DERECHO_ASEG			as decimal (11,2))/100  DERECHO_ASEG,
cast(RECARGO_ASEG 			as decimal (11,2))/100  RECARGO_ASEG,
cast(IVA_ASEG        		as decimal (11,2))/100  IVA_ASEG,
cast(COMIS_NETA   			as decimal (11,2))/100  COMIS_NETA,
cast(COMIS_RECARGO			as decimal (11,2))/100  COMIS_RECARGO,
cast(COMIS_GASTOS 			as decimal (11,2))/100  COMIS_GASTOS,
MAP(
'COBERTURA', concat(cast(COBERTURA_1 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_1 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA2', concat(cast(COBERTURA_2 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_2 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA3', concat(cast(COBERTURA_3 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_3 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA4', concat(cast(COBERTURA_4 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_4 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA5', concat(cast(COBERTURA_5 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_5 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA6', concat(cast(COBERTURA_6 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_6 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA7', concat(cast(COBERTURA_7 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_7 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA8', concat(cast(COBERTURA_8 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_8 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA9', concat(cast(COBERTURA_9 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_9 as decimal (11,2))/100),
'COBERTURA10', concat(cast(COBERTURA_10 as VARCHAR(3)),'-',cast(PRIMA_10 as decimal (11,2))/100)
) AS COBERTURA_PRIMA,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS FECHAAUD ,
'AZUL' AS SISTORIG
FROM BDDLORG.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddltrn.stg_gmm_solicitud_circulo_med_rcla
SELECT DISTINCT
circulo_med.ceo_cve
, circulo_med.mda_cve
, circulo_med.slr_num_fol
, circulo_med.rfc_medico_tratante
, npmtgcm0.tmd_cve
, circulo_med.fch_registro_tramite
FROM  bddltrn.stg_gmm_solicitud_circulo_med_rcla circulo_med
INNER JOIN (SELECT med_rfc, tmd_cve, gcm_fec_ini, gcm_fec_fin FROM bddlorg.npmtgcm0 UNION ALL
SELECT med_rfc, tmd_cve, gcm_fec_ini, gcm_fec_fin FROM bddlcru.npmhgcm0) npmtgcm0
ON TRIM(circulo_med.rfc_medico_tratante) = TRIM(npmtgcm0.med_rfc)
WHERE    npmtgcm0.gcm_fec_ini <= circulo_med.fch_registro_tramite
AND (npmtgcm0.gcm_fec_fin >= circulo_med.fch_registro_tramite OR npmtgcm0.gcm_fec_fin is null)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_INFO
SELECT DISTINCT
KSIM10T.CDSINIES			AS ID_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDNUMPOL),'') AS NUM_POLIZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTVRSPOL,-999) AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
KSIM10T.inancaco AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
'' AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
-999 AS NUM_RENOVACION_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTSECOBJ, -999) AS CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC),'') AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
KACM50T.CDRECICD 			AS NUM_RECLAMACION,
-999 						AS CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
NVL(KACM50T.TCMODALI, '')	AS CVE_MODALIDAD,
KSIA12T.CDSINIZU			AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNNOMRZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNNOMRZS,'')) END AS NOMBRE_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP1RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP1RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP2RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP2RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN COALESCE(TRIM(KPEM08T_MEDT.CDRFC),'')
ELSE '' END AS RFC_MEDICO_TRATANTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.TCCDICD),'') AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.INAPSLCF),'') AS IND_TRAMITE_FONDO_CASHFLOW,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS),'') AS CVE_HOSPITAL_ORIGEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCCDCMED),'') AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INACCIDE),'')='S' THEN 'AC' ELSE 'EN' END AS CVE_TIPO_EVENTO,
COALESCE(CAST(KACM50T.VAHOSPI AS STRING),'') AS CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITALARIO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEINGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEINGRES) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEINGRES < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEINGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEEGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEEGRES) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEEGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FECOMUNI = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI) < 8 OR KSIM10T.FECOMUNI < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI,10000101) END AS FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN,10000101) END AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '3' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '2' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '1' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAB,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCADMIS),'') AS CVE_TIPO_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_READMISION,
COALESCE(KACM50T.NUDIAINT,-999) AS NUM_DIAS_TERAPIA_INTENSIVA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDCAUACC),'') AS CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDLUGACC),'') AS CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDACTDEP),'') AS CVE_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(KACM57T.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,-1) AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTMAD = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTMAD ) < 8 OR KACM56T.FEANTMAD < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTMAD,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTTIT = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTTIT ) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTTIT,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGIN,-999) AS CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGFI,-999) AS CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INESTVAL),'') AS CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEESTVAL = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEESTVAL) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEESTVAL,10000101) END AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPRIVIS = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS,10000101) END AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS,240101) IN (0,240101) THEN '00:00:00' ELSE
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),1,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),3,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),5,2))
END AS HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPROME = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPROME) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEPROME < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPROME,10000101) END AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.NUMHABIT),'') AS NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INRESDIC),'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCSITSIN),'') AS CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCMOTTER),'') AS CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDINTERM),'') AS CVE_AGENTE,
'' AS CVE_DA_AGENTE,
-999 AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) = 0 THEN ''
WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) > 1 THEN
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA,''))
ELSE (CASE WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE = 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTHOS0.HOS_NOM,''))
WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE > 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTSAU0.SAU_NOM_PEE,''))
ELSE ''
END
)
END
ELSE ''
END AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCT),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCR),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.CDRFC,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNNOMRZS,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP1RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP2RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FERESDIC = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FERESDIC) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FERESDIC,10000101) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(KACM50T.INRESDIC,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
KACM54T.VADEDNAP AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
'MXP' AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
KACM50T.POCOASHM AS PCT_COASEGURO,
KACM50T.POCOASGH AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
KACM50T.PORECARG AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
KACM50T.POCOAADI AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
KACM50T.POCOAGFH AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
KACM51T.CTNUICD  as CTNUICD,
KACA53T.CDSECUEN AS CDSECUEN
FROM
(
SELECT KSI.*, KCI.inancaco
FROM (
SELECT CDSINIES,INAPSLCF,FECOMUNI,FEOCUSIN,TCSITSIN,TCMOTTER,CDNUMPOL,CTVRSPOL,CDINTERM,CTSECOBJ
FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM10T
WHERE TCTIPSIN = 'SA'
AND fechaaud > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) KSI
JOIN (SELECT cdnumpol,CTVRSPOL,inancaco FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T WHERE cdciagru = 'SA') KCI
ON  KCI.cdnumpol = KSI.cdnumpol
AND KCI.CTVRSPOL = KSI.CTVRSPOL
) KSIM10T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM50T KACM50T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,TCCDICD,INPRINCI,CTNUICD
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM51T WHERE INPRINCI = 'S' ) KACM51T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES =  KACM51T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN =  KACM51T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM54T KACM54T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM54T.CDSINIES
AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM54T.CTNUPOIN   AND  KACM50T.CDMCT = KACM54T.CDMCT    AND  KACM50T.CDMCR = KACM54T.CDMCR
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM56T KACM56T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM56T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM56T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CASE WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(INSIANTE),'') = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM57T  GROUP BY CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN ) KACM57T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM57T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM57T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_MEDT
ON KACM50T.CDFILDOC = KPEM08T_MEDT.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CDSINIES,TCPEROBJ,CDFILIAC FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM20T where TCPEROBJ = 'ASG') KSIM20T_ASG
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KSIM20T_ASG.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_ASG
ON KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC = KPEM08T_ASG.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_PROV
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = KPEM08T_PROV.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN
(select DNNOMRZS,DNAP1RZS,DNAP2RZS,CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CDSECUEN from BDDLCRU.KACA53T  where INMEDTRA = 'S' ) KACA53T
ON KACA53T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES	AND KACA53T.CTNUPOIN = KACM50T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTRPV0 NPMTRPV0
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = NPMTRPV0.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTHOS0 NPMTHOS0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTHOS0.HOS_RFC) AND NPMTRPV0.RPV_SCR_CVE = NPMTHOS0.HOS_SCR_CVE
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTSAU0 NPMTSAU0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTSAU0.SAU_RFC_PEE)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_INFO
SELECT DISTINCT
KSIM10T.CDSINIES			AS ID_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDNUMPOL),'') AS NUM_POLIZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTVRSPOL,-999) AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
KSIM10T.inancaco AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
'' AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
-999 AS NUM_RENOVACION_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTSECOBJ, -999) AS CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC),'') AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
KACM50T.CDRECICD 			AS NUM_RECLAMACION,
-999 						AS CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
NVL(KACM50T.TCMODALI, '')	AS CVE_MODALIDAD,
KSIA12T.CDSINIZU			AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNNOMRZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNNOMRZS,'')) END AS NOMBRE_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP1RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP1RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP2RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP2RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN COALESCE(TRIM(KPEM08T_MEDT.CDRFC),'')
ELSE '' END AS RFC_MEDICO_TRATANTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.TCCDICD),'') AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.INAPSLCF),'') AS IND_TRAMITE_FONDO_CASHFLOW,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS),'') AS CVE_HOSPITAL_ORIGEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCCDCMED),'') AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INACCIDE),'')='S' THEN 'AC' ELSE 'EN' END AS CVE_TIPO_EVENTO,
COALESCE(CAST(KACM50T.VAHOSPI AS STRING),'') AS CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITALARIO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEINGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEINGRES) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEINGRES < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEINGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEEGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEEGRES) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEEGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FECOMUNI = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI) < 8 OR KSIM10T.FECOMUNI < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI,10000101) END AS FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN,10000101) END AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '3' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '2' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '1' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAB,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCADMIS),'') AS CVE_TIPO_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_READMISION,
COALESCE(KACM50T.NUDIAINT,-999) AS NUM_DIAS_TERAPIA_INTENSIVA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDCAUACC),'') AS CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDLUGACC),'') AS CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDACTDEP),'') AS CVE_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(KACM57T.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,-1) AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTMAD = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTMAD ) < 8 OR KACM56T.FEANTMAD < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTMAD,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTTIT = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTTIT ) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTTIT,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGIN,-999) AS CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGFI,-999) AS CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INESTVAL),'') AS CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEESTVAL = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEESTVAL) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEESTVAL,10000101) END AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPRIVIS = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS,10000101) END AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS,240101) IN (0,240101) THEN '00:00:00' ELSE
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),1,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),3,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),5,2))
END AS HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPROME = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPROME) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEPROME < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPROME,10000101) END AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.NUMHABIT),'') AS NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INRESDIC),'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCSITSIN),'') AS CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCMOTTER),'') AS CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDINTERM),'') AS CVE_AGENTE,
'' AS CVE_DA_AGENTE,
-999 AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) = 0 THEN ''
WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) > 1 THEN
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA,''))
ELSE (CASE WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE = 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTHOS0.HOS_NOM,''))
WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE > 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTSAU0.SAU_NOM_PEE,''))
ELSE ''
END
)
END
ELSE ''
END AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCT),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCR),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.CDRFC,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNNOMRZS,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP1RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP2RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FERESDIC = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FERESDIC) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FERESDIC,10000101) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(KACM50T.INRESDIC,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
KACM54T.VADEDNAP AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
'MXP' AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
KACM50T.POCOASHM AS PCT_COASEGURO,
KACM50T.POCOASGH AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
KACM50T.PORECARG AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
KACM50T.POCOAADI AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
KACM50T.POCOAGFH AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
KACM51T.CTNUICD  as CTNUICD,
KACA53T.CDSECUEN AS CDSECUEN
FROM
(
SELECT KSI.*, KCI.inancaco
FROM (
SELECT CDSINIES,INAPSLCF,FECOMUNI,FEOCUSIN,TCSITSIN,TCMOTTER,CDNUMPOL,CTVRSPOL,CDINTERM,CTSECOBJ
FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM10T
WHERE TCTIPSIN = 'SA'
AND fechaaud > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) KSI
JOIN (SELECT cdnumpol,CTVRSPOL,inancaco FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T WHERE cdciagru = 'SA') KCI
ON  KCI.cdnumpol = KSI.cdnumpol
AND KCI.CTVRSPOL = KSI.CTVRSPOL
) KSIM10T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM50T KACM50T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,TCCDICD,INPRINCI,CTNUICD
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM51T WHERE INPRINCI = 'S' ) KACM51T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES =  KACM51T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN =  KACM51T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM54T KACM54T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM54T.CDSINIES
AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM54T.CTNUPOIN   AND  KACM50T.CDMCT = KACM54T.CDMCT    AND  KACM50T.CDMCR = KACM54T.CDMCR
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM56T KACM56T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM56T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM56T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CASE WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(INSIANTE),'') = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM57T  GROUP BY CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN ) KACM57T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM57T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM57T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_MEDT
ON KACM50T.CDFILDOC = KPEM08T_MEDT.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CDSINIES,TCPEROBJ,CDFILIAC FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM20T where TCPEROBJ = 'ASG') KSIM20T_ASG
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KSIM20T_ASG.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_ASG
ON KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC = KPEM08T_ASG.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_PROV
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = KPEM08T_PROV.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN
(select DNNOMRZS,DNAP1RZS,DNAP2RZS,CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CDSECUEN from BDDLCRU.KACA53T  where INMEDTRA = 'S' ) KACA53T
ON KACA53T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES	AND KACA53T.CTNUPOIN = KACM50T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTRPV0 NPMTRPV0
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = NPMTRPV0.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTHOS0 NPMTHOS0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTHOS0.HOS_RFC) AND NPMTRPV0.RPV_SCR_CVE = NPMTHOS0.HOS_SCR_CVE
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTSAU0 NPMTSAU0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTSAU0.SAU_RFC_PEE)

CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='S' THEN 1

CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='S' THEN 1

ELSE -1 END AS BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='S' THEN 1
