INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO_delta
SELECT Z.*
FROM
(
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO           actual
INNER JOIN BDDLTRN.DELTA_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5
WHERE   NVL(actual.idmd5completo,'') <>  NVL(stg.idmd5completo,'')
UNION ALL
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    BDDLTRN.DELTA_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO        stg
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLALM.ALM_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO actual ON
stg.idmd5 = actual.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

insert into table bddldes.m_crm_sin_persona_rol_poliza
SELECT
Distinct
trim(roles_compl.num_poliza) as num_poliza,
roles_compl.num_version as num_version,
trim(roles_compl.id_participante) as id_participante,
trim(COALESCE(polizas.id_participante_consolidado,'')) as id_participante_consolidado,
trim(roles_compl.cve_cliente_origen) as cve_cliente_origen,
trim(COALESCE(cat_prod.cve_linea_negocio,'')) as cve_ramo,
trim(COALESCE(poliza.cve_clasificacion_seguro,'')) as cve_linea_negocio,
trim(roles_compl.cve_rol) as cve_rol,
trim(cat_rol.rol) as descr_rol,
trim(roles_compl.cve_sistema) as cve_sistema,
CASE
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='TOM' THEN '1'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='PAG' THEN '2'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='ASG' THEN '3'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='BEN' THEN '4'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='COH' THEN '5'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='INT' THEN '6'
ELSE '' end as ind_rol,
adic.ind_titular_dependiente,
adic.ind_relacion,
adic.des_relacion
FROM
(
SELECT
coalesce(num_poliza,'') as num_poliza,
coalesce(num_version, -999) as num_version,
coalesce(id_participante, '') as id_participante,
coalesce(cve_cliente_origen, '') as cve_cliente_origen,
'TOM' as cve_rol,
coalesce(cve_sistema ,'') as cve_sistema
FROM bddlcru.CRM_CONTRATANTE_POLIZA
WHERE coalesce(TRIM(cve_estatus_participante),'') != 'C'
) AS roles_compl
LEFT JOIN (
select
per_con.id_participante_consolidado,
per_con.id_participante
from bddlcru.crm_participante per_con
) polizas
on TRIM(polizas.id_participante)    	= TRIM(roles_compl.id_participante)
inner join bddlcru.crm_poliza as poliza
on trim(roles_compl.cve_sistema) = trim(poliza.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.num_poliza)  = trim(poliza.num_poliza)
left join bddlcru.cat_producto as cat_prod
on poliza.cve_prod_tecnico   = cat_prod.cve_prod_tecnico
and poliza.cve_prod_comercial = cat_prod.cve_prod_comercial
left join bddlcru.cat_rol as cat_rol
on trim(roles_compl.cve_rol) = trim(cat_rol.cve_rol)
left join bddlapr.cnm_asegurado_datos_adicionales as adic
on trim(poliza.num_poliza) = trim(adic.num_poliza)
and adic.num_version_poliza = roles_compl.num_version
and trim(poliza.cve_sistema) = trim(adic.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.cve_cliente_origen) = trim(adic.cve_cliente_origen)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLTRN.DELTA_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.DELTA_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO
SELECT
STG1.num_reclamacion,
STG1.cve_sistema_int,
STG1.descr_sistema_int,
STG1.cve_sistema,
STG1.descr_sistema,
STG1.num_consecutivo_acumulado,
STG1.cve_tipo_mov_producido,
STG1.cve_estatus_acumulado,
STG1.cve_cobertura_afectada,
STG1.descr_cobertura_afectada,
STG1.mto_suma_asegurada,
STG1.mto_suma_asegurada_pagada,
STG1.mto_suma_asegurada_remte,
STG1.cve_unidad_suma_asegurada,
STG1.nom_unidad_suma_asegurada,
STG1.mto_deducible_nacional,
STG1.mto_deducible_nacional_pagado,
STG1.mto_deducible_nacional_remte,
STG1.cve_unidad_deducible_nacional,
STG1.nom_unidad_deducible_nacional,
STG1.mto_deducible_internal,
STG1.mto_deducible_internal_pagado,
STG1.mto_deducible_internal_remte,
STG1.cve_unidad_deducible_internal,
STG1.nom_unidad_deducible_internal,
STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal,
STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_pagado,
STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_remte,
STG1.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,
STG1.nom_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,
STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl,
STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_pagado,
STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_remte,
STG1.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,
STG1.nom_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,
STG1.pct_coaseguro_nacional,
STG1.pct_coaseguro_internacional,
STG1.ts_alta_hdfs,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', concat(NVL(STG1.num_reclamacion,''),NVL(STG1.CVE_SISTEMA,''),NVL(STG1.NUM_CONSECUTIVO_ACUMULADO,''))) AS IDMD5,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', concat(nvl(STG1.num_reclamacion,''),nvl(STG1.cve_sistema_int,''),nvl(STG1.descr_sistema_int,''),nvl(STG1.cve_sistema,''),nvl(STG1.descr_sistema,''),nvl(STG1.num_consecutivo_acumulado,0),
nvl(STG1.cve_tipo_mov_producido,''),nvl(STG1.cve_estatus_acumulado,''),nvl(STG1.cve_cobertura_afectada,''),nvl(STG1.descr_cobertura_afectada,''),nvl(STG1.mto_suma_asegurada,0),
nvl(STG1.mto_suma_asegurada_pagada,0),nvl(STG1.mto_suma_asegurada_remte,0),nvl(STG1.cve_unidad_suma_asegurada,''),nvl(STG1.nom_unidad_suma_asegurada,''),nvl(STG1.mto_deducible_nacional,0),
nvl(STG1.mto_deducible_nacional_pagado,0),nvl(STG1.mto_deducible_nacional_remte,0),nvl(STG1.cve_unidad_deducible_nacional,''),nvl(STG1.nom_unidad_deducible_nacional,''),nvl(STG1.mto_deducible_internal,0),
nvl(STG1.mto_deducible_internal_pagado,0),nvl(STG1.mto_deducible_internal_remte,0),nvl(STG1.cve_unidad_deducible_internal,''),nvl(STG1.nom_unidad_deducible_internal,''),nvl(STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal,0),
nvl(STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_pagado,0),nvl(STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_remte,0),nvl(STG1.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,''),nvl(STG1.nom_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,''),nvl(STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl,0),
nvl(STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_pagado,0),nvl(STG1.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_remte,0),nvl(STG1.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,''),nvl(STG1.nom_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,''),nvl(STG1.pct_coaseguro_nacional,0),
nvl(STG1.pct_coaseguro_internacional,0)))  AS IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM
(
SELECT
STG.num_reclamacion,
STG.cve_sistema_int,
IF(ISNULL(STG.sistema_int),'',STG.sistema_int) as descr_sistema_int,
STG.cve_sistema,
IF(ISNULL(STG.sistema),'',STG.sistema) AS descr_sistema,
STG.num_consecutivo_acumulado,
STG.cve_tipo_mov_producido,
STG.cve_estatus_acumulado,
IF(ISNULL(STG.cve_cobertura_afectada),'',STG.cve_cobertura_afectada) AS cve_cobertura_afectada,
IF(ISNULL(descr_larga_cobertura_afectada),'',descr_larga_cobertura_afectada) AS descr_cobertura_afectada,
STG.mto_suma_asegurada,
STG.mto_suma_asegurada_pagada,
STG.mto_suma_asegurada_remte,
IF(ISNULL(STG.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_SUM_ASG),'',STG.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_SUM_ASG)AS cve_unidad_suma_asegurada,
IF(ISNULL(STG.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_SUM_ASG),'',STG.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_SUM_ASG) AS nom_unidad_suma_asegurada,
STG.mto_deducible_nacional,
STG.mto_deducible_nacional_pagado,
STG.mto_deducible_nacional_remte,
IF(ISNULL(STG.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_NAC),'',STG.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_NAC)AS cve_unidad_deducible_nacional,
IF(ISNULL(STG.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_NAC),'',STG.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_NAC) AS nom_unidad_deducible_nacional,
STG.mto_deducible_internal,
STG.mto_deducible_internal_pagado,
STG.mto_deducible_internal_remte,
IF(ISNULL(STG.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_INTER),'',STG.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_INTER)AS cve_unidad_deducible_internal,
IF(ISNULL(STG.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_INTER),'',STG.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_INTER) AS nom_unidad_deducible_internal,
STG.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal,
STG.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_pagado,
STG.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_remte,
IF(ISNULL(STG.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_COA_NAC),'',STG.CVE_HOMOLOGADA_COA_NAC)AS cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,
IF(ISNULL(STG.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA__COA_NAC ),'',STG.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA__COA_NAC )AS nom_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,
STG.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl,
STG.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_pagado,
STG.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_remte,
IF(ISNULL(STG.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl),'',STG.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl)  AS cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,
IF(ISNULL(CUMDN.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA),'',CUMDN.DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA) AS nom_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,
STG.pct_coaseguro_nacional,
STG.pct_coaseguro_internacional,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS ts_alta_hdfs
FROM
(	SELECT
sistema,

pct_coaseguro_internacional,
ts_alta_hdfs,
cve_cobertura_afectada1,
descr_larga_cobertura_afectada,
cve_origen_INFO,
CVE_HOMOLOGADA_SUM_ASG,
DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_SUM_ASG,
CVE_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_NAC,
DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_NAC
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_STR_UNID_MED_DED_INTER) SUMDI
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
CVE_ORIGEN,
CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CVE_HOMOLOGADA AS CVE_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_INTER,
DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA AS DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA_UNI_MED_DED_INTER
FROM bddlint.CAT_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_DL_NORM
ORDER BY CVE_ORIGEN,CVE_SISTEMA_INT  ASC
)CUMDN
ON SUMDI.cve_unidad_deducible_internal = CUMDN.CVE_ORIGEN
AND SUMDI.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = CUMDN.CVE_SISTEMA_INT
ORDER BY SUMDI.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal ,SUMDI.cve_sistema_int
)SUMDI2
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
CVE_ORIGEN,
CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CVE_HOMOLOGADA AS CVE_HOMOLOGADA_COA_NAC,
DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA AS DESCR_LARGA_HOMOLOGADA__COA_NAC
FROM bddlint.CAT_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_DL_NORM
ORDER BY CVE_ORIGEN,CVE_SISTEMA_INT  ASC
)CUMDN2
ON SUMDI2.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal = CUMDN2.CVE_ORIGEN
AND SUMDI2.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = CUMDN2.CVE_SISTEMA_INT
ORDER BY SUMDI2.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl ,SUMDI2.cve_sistema_int

insert into table bddldes.m_crm_sin_persona_rol_poliza
SELECT
Distinct
trim(roles_compl.num_poliza) as num_poliza,
roles_compl.num_version as num_version,
trim(roles_compl.id_participante) as id_participante,
trim(COALESCE(polizas.id_participante_consolidado,'')) as id_participante_consolidado,
trim(roles_compl.cve_cliente_origen) as cve_cliente_origen,
trim(COALESCE(cat_prod.cve_linea_negocio,'')) as cve_ramo,
trim(COALESCE(poliza.cve_clasificacion_seguro,'')) as cve_linea_negocio,
trim(roles_compl.cve_rol) as cve_rol,
trim(cat_rol.rol) as descr_rol,
trim(roles_compl.cve_sistema) as cve_sistema,
CASE
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='TOM' THEN '1'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='PAG' THEN '2'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='ASG' THEN '3'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='BEN' THEN '4'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='COH' THEN '5'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='INT' THEN '6'
ELSE '' end as ind_rol,
adic.ind_titular_dependiente,
adic.ind_relacion,
adic.des_relacion
FROM
(
SELECT
coalesce(num_poliza,'') as num_poliza,
coalesce(num_version, -999) as num_version,
coalesce(id_participante, '') as id_participante,
coalesce(cve_cliente_origen, '') as cve_cliente_origen,
'PAG' as cve_rol,
coalesce(cve_sistema ,'') as cve_sistema
FROM bddlcru.CRM_PAGADOR_POLIZA
UNION ALL
SELECT
coalesce(num_poliza,'') as num_poliza,
coalesce(num_version, -999) as num_version,
coalesce(id_agente, '') as id_participante,
coalesce(cve_cliente_origen, '') as cve_cliente_origen,
coalesce(cve_rol,'') as cve_rol,
coalesce(cve_sistema ,'') as cve_sistema
FROM bddlcru.CRM_AGENTE_POLIZA
) AS roles_compl
LEFT JOIN (
select
per_con.id_participante_consolidado,
per_con.id_participante
from bddlcru.crm_participante per_con
) polizas
on TRIM(polizas.id_participante)    	= TRIM(roles_compl.id_participante)
inner join bddlcru.crm_poliza as poliza
on trim(roles_compl.cve_sistema) = trim(poliza.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.num_poliza)  = trim(poliza.num_poliza)
left join bddlcru.cat_producto as cat_prod
on poliza.cve_prod_tecnico   = cat_prod.cve_prod_tecnico
and poliza.cve_prod_comercial = cat_prod.cve_prod_comercial
left join bddlcru.cat_rol as cat_rol
on trim(roles_compl.cve_rol) = trim(cat_rol.cve_rol)
left join bddlapr.cnm_asegurado_datos_adicionales as adic
on trim(poliza.num_poliza) = trim(adic.num_poliza)
and adic.num_version_poliza = roles_compl.num_version
and trim(poliza.cve_sistema) = trim(adic.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.cve_cliente_origen) = trim(adic.cve_cliente_origen)

FROM bddlcru.CRM_PAGADOR_POLIZA
UNION ALL
SELECT
coalesce(num_poliza,'') as num_poliza,
coalesce(num_version, -999) as num_version,
coalesce(id_agente, '') as id_participante,
coalesce(cve_cliente_origen, '') as cve_cliente_origen,
coalesce(cve_rol,'') as cve_rol,
coalesce(cve_sistema ,'') as cve_sistema
FROM bddlcru.CRM_AGENTE_POLIZA
) AS roles_compl
LEFT JOIN (
select
per_con.id_participante_consolidado,
per_con.id_participante
from bddlcru.crm_participante per_con
) polizas
on TRIM(polizas.id_participante)    	= TRIM(roles_compl.id_participante)
inner join bddlcru.crm_poliza as poliza
on trim(roles_compl.cve_sistema) = trim(poliza.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.num_poliza)  = trim(poliza.num_poliza)
left join bddlcru.cat_producto as cat_prod
on poliza.cve_prod_tecnico   = cat_prod.cve_prod_tecnico
and poliza.cve_prod_comercial = cat_prod.cve_prod_comercial
left join bddlcru.cat_rol as cat_rol
on trim(roles_compl.cve_rol) = trim(cat_rol.cve_rol)
left join bddlapr.cnm_asegurado_datos_adicionales as adic
on trim(poliza.num_poliza) = trim(adic.num_poliza)
and adic.num_version_poliza = roles_compl.num_version
and trim(poliza.cve_sistema) = trim(adic.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.cve_cliente_origen) = trim(adic.cve_cliente_origen)

ARA1.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl,
ARA1.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_pagado,

ARA1.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,
ARA1.pct_coaseguro_nacional,

ARA1.ts_alta_hdfs
from
(
select
CSO.sistema,
ARA.num_reclamacion,
ARA.cve_sistema_int,
ARA.cve_sistema,
ARA.num_consecutivo_acumulado,
ARA.cve_tipo_mov_producido,

ARA.cve_cobertura_afectada,

ARA.cve_unidad_deducible_nacional,
ARA.mto_deducible_internal,

ARA.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,
ARA.pct_coaseguro_nacional,
ARA.pct_coaseguro_internacional,
ARA.ts_alta_hdfs
from bddltrn.RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO ARA
LEFT JOIN
bddlcru.cat_sistema_origen CSO
on CSO.cve_sistema = ARA.cve_sistema_int
order by ARA.cve_sistema
) ARA1
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_sistema,sistema
from bddlcru.cat_sistema_origen
order by cve_sistema
)CSO1
ON 	ARA1.cve_sistema = CSO1.cve_sistema
WHERE 	ARA1.cve_sistema in ('RCLA','AZUL'))INFO
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
cve_homologada_dl as cve_cobertura_afectada1,
descr_larga_homologada_dl as descr_larga_cobertura_afectada ,
cve_origen_NZ
FROM bddlcru.CAT_COBERTURA_AFECTADA_DL
)CCAD
ON INFO.cve_cobertura_afectada = CCAD.cve_origen_NZ

INSERT INTO  bddltrn.STG_RECLA_ACUMULADO_KAC
SELECT

CA60T1.IMDEDPEE		AS 	mto_deducible_internal_remte	,

CA60T1.IMCOAPEN		AS 	mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_remte	,
CA60T1.TCCDMOCO		AS 	cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal	,
CA60T1.IMCOATOI		AS 	mto_tope_coaseguro_intl	,
CA60T1.IMCOIPAG		AS 	mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_pagado	,
CA60T1.IMCOAPEI		AS 	mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_remte	,
CA60T1.TCCDMOCI		AS 	cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_inl	,
CA60T1.POCOACON		AS 	pct_coaseguro_nacional	,
CA60T1.POCOACOE		AS 	pct_coaseguro_internacional	,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP())		AS 	ts_alta_hdfs
FROM
(
SELECT
CA60T.cdrecicd,
CA60T.ctnumovi,
CA60T.tccdtimr,
CA60T.cdmcr,
CA60T.imsacon,
CA60T.tccdmosa,
CA60T.imsarema,
CA60T.imdedcon,
CA60T.imdedcoe,
CA60T.tccdmodi,
CA60T.tccdmode,
CA60T.imdedpen,
CA60T.imdedpee,
CA60T.pocoacon,
CA60T.pocoacoe,
CA60T.imcoatop,
CA60T.tccdmoco,
CA60T.imcoapen,
CA60T.imsuaspa,
CA60T.imdenapa,
CA60T.imdeexpa,
CA60T.imcospag,
CA60T.imcoatoi,
CA60T.tccdmoci,
CA60T.imcoapei,
CA60T.imcoipag
FROM bddlcru.KACA60T CA60T
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(fechaaud) AS fechaaud FROM bddlcru.KACA60T) AS T2
ON TO_DATE(T2.fechaaud) = TO_DATE(CA60T.fechaaud)
)	AS CA60T1
INNER JOIN
(
SELECT CM60T.cdrecicd
FROM bddlcru.KACM60T   CM60T
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(fechaaud) AS fechaaud FROM bddlcru.KACM60T) AS T2
ON TO_DATE(T2.fechaaud) = TO_DATE(CM60T.fechaaud)
) AS CM60T1
ON CA60T1.cdrecicd = CM60T1.cdrecicd

INSERT INTO bddltrn.STG_RECLA_ACUMULADO_LMP
select
AUR1.rlc_num 			 AS num_reclamacion,
'AZUL' 					 AS cve_sistema_int,
IF (RCL01.rcl_org = 'AZ','AZUL','RCLA') AS cve_sistema,
CAST(AUR1.aur_cns AS INT)  AS num_consecutivo_acumulado,
'' 						 AS cve_tipo_mov_producido,
AUR1.AUR_ESS_ACU_INF 	 AS cve_estatus_acumulado,
AUR1.COB_CVE 			 AS cve_cobertura_afectada,
AUR1.AUR_SUM_CNR         AS mto_suma_asegurada,
AUR_SUM_EJR				 AS mto_suma_asegurada_pagada,
IF(AUR1.AUR_SUM_CNR= -1,-1,IF(AUR1.AUR_SUM_EJR > AUR1.AUR_SUM_CNR,0,AUR1.AUR_SUM_CNR - AUR1.AUR_SUM_EJR )) AS mto_suma_asegurada_remte,
AUR1.AUR_UNI_SUM 		 AS cve_unidad_suma_asegurada,
AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL         AS mto_deducible_nacional ,
AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL_ACU     AS mto_deducible_nacional_pagado,
IF(AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL = -1,-1,IF(AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL_ACU > AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL,0,AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL - AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL_ACU))AS mto_deducible_nacional_remte,
AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL_UNI     AS cve_unidad_deducible_nacional,
AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT         AS mto_deducible_internal,
AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT_ACU     AS mto_deducible_internal_pagado,
IF(AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT = -1,-1,IF(AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT_ACU > AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT,0,AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT - AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT_ACU))AS mto_deducible_internal_remte,
AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT_UNI     AS cve_unidad_deducible_internal,
AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL     AS mto_tope_coaseguro_nal,
AUR1.AUR_COA_ACU         AS mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_pagado,
IF(AUR_LIM_COA_VAL = -1,-1,IF(AUR_COA_ACU > AUR_LIM_COA_VAL,0,AUR_LIM_COA_VAL - AUR_COA_ACU)) AS mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_remte,
AUR1.AUR_UNI_LIM_COA     AS cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,
AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL_EXT AS mto_tope_coaseguro_intl,
AUR1.AUR_COA_ACU_EXT     AS mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_pagado,
IF(AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL_EXT = -1,-1,IF(AUR1.AUR_COA_ACU_EXT > AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL_EXT,0,AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL_EXT - AUR1.AUR_COA_ACU_EXT)) AS mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_remte,
AUR1.AUR_UNI_LIM_COA_EXT AS cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_inl,
AUR_COA_CNR/100          AS pct_coaseguro_nacional,
AUR_COA_CNR_EXT/100      AS pct_coaseguro_internacional,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS ts_alta_hdfs
From
(
SELECT
RCL0.rcl_num,
RCL0.rcl_org
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTRCL0 RCL0
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(fechaaud) AS fechaaud FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTRCL0) AS T2
ON TO_DATE(T2.fechaaud) = TO_DATE(RCL0.fechaaud)
) AS RCL01
INNER JOIN
(
SELECT
AUR.rlc_num ,
AUR.cob_cve,
AUR.aur_sum_cnr,
AUR.aur_uni_sum,
AUR.aur_sum_ejr,
AUR.aur_ded_nal,
AUR.aur_ded_nal_uni,
AUR.aur_ded_nal_acu,
AUR.aur_ded_ext,
AUR.aur_ded_ext_uni,
AUR.aur_ded_ext_acu,
AUR.aur_lim_coa_val,
AUR.aur_uni_lim_coa,
AUR.aur_coa_acu,
AUR.aur_coa_cnr,
AUR.aur_cns,
AUR.aur_ess_acu_inf,
AUR.aur_lim_coa_val_ext,
AUR.aur_uni_lim_coa_ext,

AUR.aur_coa_cnr_ext

insert into table bddldes.m_crm_sin_persona_rol_poliza
SELECT
Distinct
trim(roles_compl.num_poliza) as num_poliza,
roles_compl.num_version as num_version,
trim(roles_compl.id_participante) as id_participante,
trim(COALESCE(polizas.id_participante_consolidado,'')) as id_participante_consolidado,
trim(roles_compl.cve_cliente_origen) as cve_cliente_origen,
trim(COALESCE(cat_prod.cve_linea_negocio,'')) as cve_ramo,
trim(COALESCE(poliza.cve_clasificacion_seguro,'')) as cve_linea_negocio,
trim(roles_compl.cve_rol) as cve_rol,
trim(cat_rol.rol) as descr_rol,
trim(roles_compl.cve_sistema) as cve_sistema,
CASE
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='TOM' THEN '1'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='PAG' THEN '2'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='ASG' THEN '3'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='BEN' THEN '4'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='COH' THEN '5'
WHEN trim(roles_compl.cve_rol)='INT' THEN '6'
ELSE '' end as ind_rol,
adic.ind_titular_dependiente,
adic.ind_relacion,
adic.des_relacion
FROM
(
SELECT
coalesce(num_poliza,'') as num_poliza,
coalesce(num_version, -999) as num_version,
coalesce(id_participante, '') as id_participante,
coalesce(cve_cliente_origen, '') as cve_cliente_origen,
'BEN' as cve_rol,
coalesce(cve_sistema ,'') as cve_sistema
FROM bddlcru.CRM_BENEFICIARIO_POLIZA
UNION ALL
SELECT
coalesce(num_poliza,'') as num_poliza,
coalesce(cast(num_version as int), -999) as num_version,
coalesce(id_participante, '') as id_participante,
coalesce(cve_cliente_origen, '') as cve_cliente_origen,
'COH' as cve_rol,
coalesce(cve_sistema ,'') as cve_sistema
FROM bddlcru.CRM_CONDUCTOR_HABITUAL_POLIZA
) AS roles_compl
LEFT JOIN (
select
per_con.id_participante_consolidado,
per_con.id_participante
from bddlcru.crm_participante per_con
) polizas
on TRIM(polizas.id_participante)    	= TRIM(roles_compl.id_participante)
inner join bddlcru.crm_poliza as poliza
on trim(roles_compl.cve_sistema) = trim(poliza.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.num_poliza)  = trim(poliza.num_poliza)
left join bddlcru.cat_producto as cat_prod
on poliza.cve_prod_tecnico   = cat_prod.cve_prod_tecnico
and poliza.cve_prod_comercial = cat_prod.cve_prod_comercial
left join bddlcru.cat_rol as cat_rol
on trim(roles_compl.cve_rol) = trim(cat_rol.cve_rol)
left join bddlapr.cnm_asegurado_datos_adicionales as adic
on trim(poliza.num_poliza) = trim(adic.num_poliza)
and adic.num_version_poliza = roles_compl.num_version
and trim(poliza.cve_sistema) = trim(adic.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.cve_cliente_origen) = trim(adic.cve_cliente_origen)

coalesce(num_version, -999) as num_version,
coalesce(id_participante, '') as id_participante,
coalesce(cve_cliente_origen, '') as cve_cliente_origen,
'BEN' as cve_rol,
coalesce(cve_sistema ,'') as cve_sistema
FROM bddlcru.CRM_BENEFICIARIO_POLIZA
UNION ALL
SELECT
coalesce(num_poliza,'') as num_poliza,
coalesce(cast(num_version as int), -999) as num_version,
coalesce(id_participante, '') as id_participante,
coalesce(cve_cliente_origen, '') as cve_cliente_origen,
'COH' as cve_rol,
coalesce(cve_sistema ,'') as cve_sistema
FROM bddlcru.CRM_CONDUCTOR_HABITUAL_POLIZA
) AS roles_compl
LEFT JOIN (
select
per_con.id_participante_consolidado,
per_con.id_participante
from bddlcru.crm_participante per_con
) polizas
on TRIM(polizas.id_participante)    	= TRIM(roles_compl.id_participante)
inner join bddlcru.crm_poliza as poliza
on trim(roles_compl.cve_sistema) = trim(poliza.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.num_poliza)  = trim(poliza.num_poliza)
left join bddlcru.cat_producto as cat_prod
on poliza.cve_prod_tecnico   = cat_prod.cve_prod_tecnico
and poliza.cve_prod_comercial = cat_prod.cve_prod_comercial
left join bddlcru.cat_rol as cat_rol
on trim(roles_compl.cve_rol) = trim(cat_rol.cve_rol)
left join bddlapr.cnm_asegurado_datos_adicionales as adic
on trim(poliza.num_poliza) = trim(adic.num_poliza)
and adic.num_version_poliza = roles_compl.num_version
and trim(poliza.cve_sistema) = trim(adic.cve_sistema)
and trim(roles_compl.cve_cliente_origen) = trim(adic.cve_cliente_origen)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.ADC_T_INF_INGRESOS_DECLARADO
SELECT  UNI.CDNUMPOL
,UNI.CTVRSPOL
,UNI.NURELREO
,UNI.CTSECOBJ
,UNI.FEINIOBJ
,UNI.IMCAOP19
,UNI.IMCAOP20
,UNI.TXCAOP21
,UNI.IMCAOP43
FROM (
SELECT  K18T.CDNUMPOL
,K18T.CTVRSPOL
,K18T.NURELREO
,K18T.CTSECOBJ
,K18T.FEINIOBJ
,K18T.IMCAOP19
,K18T.IMCAOP20
,K18T.TXCAOP21
,K18T.IMCAOP43
,ROW_NUMBER() over(PARTITION BY K18T.CDNUMPOL, K18T.CTVRSPOL ORDER BY K18T.CTVRSPOL Desc, K18T.CTSECOBJ) AS Orden
FROM    BDDLCRU.KCIM18T K18T
INNER JOIN BDDLTRN.ADC_T_INF_UNI_POLIZA_VERSION PV
ON K18T.CDNUMPOL = PV.CDNUMPOL
AND K18T.CTVRSPOL = PV.CTVRSPOL
WHERE   K18T.NURELREO = 1
) UNI
WHERE   UNI.Orden = 1

IND_OBJETO,
CVE_SISTEMA,
CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
IF (CVE_COBERTURA IS NULL,'',CVE_COBERTURA)                                           AS CVE_COBERTURA,

IF (VAL_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL IS NULL,0.0,VAL_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL)                        AS VAL_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL,

cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_INI_COBERTURA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_INI_COBERTURA,
IF( FCH_FIN_COBERTURA IS NULL OR FCH_FIN_COBERTURA =0 OR TRIM(FCH_FIN_COBERTURA )='' ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_FIN_COBERTURA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_FIN_COBERTURA,

cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
IF( FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO IS NULL OR FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO=0 OR TRIM(FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO)='' ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO,
IF (IND_NIVEL_ASIGNACION IS NULL,'',IND_NIVEL_ASIGNACION)                             AS IND_NIVEL_ASIGNACION,
IF (VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_OBESIDAD IS NULL,'',VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_OBESIDAD)                       AS VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_OBESIDAD,
IF (VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_DICTAMEN IS NULL,'',VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_DICTAMEN)                       AS VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_DICTAMEN,
CVE_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA,
DES_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA,
IF (CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE IS NULL,'',CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE)                         AS CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,

IF (VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_INTERNACIONAL IS NULL,'',VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_INTERNACIONAL)     AS VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_INTERNACIONAL,
IF (CVE_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NAL_INTERNAL IS NULL,'',CVE_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NAL_INTERNAL) AS CVE_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NAL_INTERNAL,

IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD=0  OR TRIM(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD)='',

cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))   AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD,

IF (CVE_CONCEPTO_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA IS NULL,'',CVE_CONCEPTO_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA)     AS CVE_CONCEPTO_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA,

IF (PCT_DESCUENTO_COMERCIAL_COBERTURA IS NULL,'',PCT_DESCUENTO_COMERCIAL_COBERTURA)   AS PCT_DESCUENTO_COMERCIAL_COBERTURA,

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_ASEGURADO_CBZA_UNICO STORED AS RCFile AS
select  distinct ADD1.* from
(SELECT * FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_ASEG_DATOS_ADICIONALES ) ADD1
join
(select num_poliza,VIGENCIA_POLIZA,NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
max(fch_alta)fch_alta, max(fch_antiguedad_nac)fch_antiguedad_nac,
max(fch_antiguedad_int)fch_antiguedad_int
from BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_ASEG_DATOS_ADICIONALES
group by num_poliza,VIGENCIA_POLIZA,NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN) ADD2
ON ADD1.num_poliza = ADD2.num_poliza
AND ADD1.VIGENCIA_POLIZA=ADD2.VIGENCIA_POLIZA
AND ADD1.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA=ADD2.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA
AND ADD1.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA=ADD2.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA
AND ADD1.CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN=ADD2.CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN
AND ADD1.fch_alta = ADD2.fch_alta
AND ADD1.fch_antiguedad_nac= ADD2.fch_antiguedad_nac
AND ADD1.fch_antiguedad_int= ADD2.fch_antiguedad_int

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_ASEG_DATOS_ADICIONALES STORED AS RCFile
AS SELECT
COMPLEMENTO.NUM_POLIZA,
CAST(-999 AS SMALLINT )  AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
-999                      AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
COMPLEMENTO.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
TRIM(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN)  AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
'AZUL'                    AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'AZUL'                    AS CVE_SISTEMA,
''                        AS IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,
''                        AS CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,
-999                      AS IND_OBJETO,
''                        AS CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION,
''                        AS ZONA_TARIFICACION,
0                         AS CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION,
0                         AS POBLACION,
0                         AS ESTADO,
APELLIDO_PATERNO,
APELLIDO_MATERNO,
NOMBRE,
''                        AS BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO,
''                        AS CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,
''                        AS PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,
IF(FCH_ALTA = 0 OR FCH_ALTA IS NULL ,'14000101',FCH_ALTA) AS FCH_ALTA,
IF(FCH_BAJA = 0 OR FCH_BAJA IS NULL ,'14000101',FCH_BAJA) AS FCH_BAJA,
'14000101' AS FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO,
'14000101' AS FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO,
CASE WHEN NOT POLIZA.CVE_PLAN IN ('17','31','33','CON31')
THEN FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC
ELSE FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT
END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD,
IF(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC = 0 OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC IS NULL ,'14000101',FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC,
IF(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT = 0 OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT IS NULL ,'14000101',FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT,
'14000101' AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA,
'14000101' AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA,
IF(FCH_NACIMIENTO = 0 OR FCH_NACIMIENTO IS NULL ,'14000101',FCH_NACIMIENTO) AS FCH_NACIMIENTO,
CVE_SEXO,
SEXO,
CVE_ESTATUS_ASEGURADO,
ESTATUS_ASEGURADO,
''	AS	IND_ULT_SITUACION,
IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE	AS	IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,
TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,
IND_RELACION,
RELACION,

''	AS	GRATUIDAD,
0	AS	EDAD_EQUIVALENTE,

''	AS	ESTADO_CIVIL,

''	AS	PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LAB_DEP,
''	AS	IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,

''	AS	PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LABORAL,
''	AS	PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD,
''	AS	PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD,
''	AS	CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,
''	AS	TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,
''	AS	VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD,
'14000101' AS FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA,

''	AS	BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP,
''	AS	BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,

FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_ASEG_AD_CBZA_FILTER AS COMPLEMENTO

titular_dependienteMap[0] as ind_titular_dependiente,
titular_dependienteMap[1] as titular_dependiente,
FILTER.ind_relacion, FILTER.relacion

AND CBZA_ULTIMO.END_FECHA_INI =FILTER.END_FECHA_INI
AND CBZA_ULTIMO.FCH_NACIMIENTO=FILTER.FCH_NACIMIENTO

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_ASEG_CBZA_CATALOG AS
SELECT FILTER.NUM_POLIZA, FILTER.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA, FILTER.CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN, FILTER.APELLIDO_PATERNO, FILTER.APELLIDO_MATERNO, FILTER.NOMBRE,
FILTER.FCH_ALTA, FILTER.FCH_BAJA, FILTER.FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC,FILTER.FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT, FILTER.FCH_NACIMIENTO, FILTER.CVE_SEXO,
CASE
WHEN FILTER.CVE_SEXO = ('F')
THEN 'FEMENINO'
WHEN FILTER.CVE_SEXO = 'M'
THEN 'MASCULINO'
ELSE ''
END	AS SEXO,
FILTER.CVE_ESTATUS AS CVE_ESTATUS_ASEGURADO,
CASE
WHEN FILTER.CVE_ESTATUS IN ('V', 'R', 'A', '')
THEN 'VIGENTE'
WHEN FILTER.CVE_ESTATUS= 'B'
THEN 'BAJA'
ELSE ''
END	AS ESTATUS_ASEGURADO,
FILTER.end_fecha_ini,
FILTER.end_status, FILTER.CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE, split(FILTER.ind_titular_dependiente,'-') as titular_dependienteMap, FILTER.ind_relacion, FILTER.relacion
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_ASEG_AD_CBZA_RELACION FILTER

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_COB_DATOS_ADICIONALES AS
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_oficina ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS NUM_POLIZA,
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
CONCAT(NVL(gaz0_asegurado.ase_num_certif, ''), NVL(gaz0_asegurado.ase_cve_parien, '')) AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
gaz0_poliza.pol_nombre_cob,
CAST(pol_suma_aseg AS DECIMAL(18,2)) AS val_suma_asegurada,
CAST(pol_deducible AS DECIMAL (18,2))/100 AS val_deducible_nacional,
gaz0_poliza.pol_coaseguro,
CAST(gaz0_poliza.pol_plan as VARCHAR(1)) AS pol_plan  ,
CAST(gaz0_poliza.pol_stdr as VARCHAR(1)) AS pol_stdr
,CAST(gaz0_poliza.cve_unidad AS VARCHAR(15)) as cve_unidad
,CAST(gaz0_poliza.cve_moneda AS VARCHAR(15)) AS cve_moneda
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_CAT_TIPO_UNIDAD as gaz0_poliza
LEFT JOIN  BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_UNION_GAZ0_ASEGURADO as gaz0_asegurado
ON gaz0_poliza.pol_oficina = gaz0_asegurado.ase_pol_ofna
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_numero = gaz0_asegurado.ase_pol_num
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_ofi_renovac = gaz0_asegurado.pol_ofi_renovac
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_num_renovac = gaz0_asegurado.pol_num_renovac
AND gaz0_poliza.end_fecha_ini = gaz0_asegurado.end_fecha_ini
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_oficina = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_oficina
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_tipo = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_tipo
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_consec = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_consec
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_control = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_control
AND gaz0_poliza.end_liga_pol_ase = gaz0_asegurado.end_liga_pol_ase
AND gaz0_poliza.end_incluye_aseg = gaz0_asegurado.end_incluye_aseg
AND gaz0_poliza.end_subramo = gaz0_asegurado.end_subramo
AND gaz0_poliza.end_fecha_fin = gaz0_asegurado.end_fecha_fin

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_COB_DATOS_ADICIONALES AS
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_oficina ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS NUM_POLIZA,
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
CONCAT(NVL(gaz0_asegurado.ase_num_certif, ''), NVL(gaz0_asegurado.ase_cve_parien, '')) AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
gaz0_poliza.pol_nombre_cob,
CAST(pol_suma_aseg AS DECIMAL(18,2)) AS val_suma_asegurada,
CAST(pol_deducible AS DECIMAL (18,2))/100 AS val_deducible_nacional,
gaz0_poliza.pol_coaseguro,
CAST(gaz0_poliza.pol_plan as VARCHAR(1)) AS pol_plan  ,
CAST(gaz0_poliza.pol_stdr as VARCHAR(1)) AS pol_stdr
,CAST(gaz0_poliza.cve_unidad AS VARCHAR(15)) as cve_unidad
,CAST(gaz0_poliza.cve_moneda AS VARCHAR(15)) AS cve_moneda
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_CAT_TIPO_UNIDAD as gaz0_poliza
LEFT JOIN  BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_UNION_GAZ0_ASEGURADO as gaz0_asegurado
ON gaz0_poliza.pol_oficina = gaz0_asegurado.ase_pol_ofna
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_numero = gaz0_asegurado.ase_pol_num
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_ofi_renovac = gaz0_asegurado.pol_ofi_renovac
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_num_renovac = gaz0_asegurado.pol_num_renovac
AND gaz0_poliza.end_fecha_ini = gaz0_asegurado.end_fecha_ini
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_oficina = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_oficina
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_tipo = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_tipo
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_consec = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_consec
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_control = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_control
AND gaz0_poliza.end_liga_pol_ase = gaz0_asegurado.end_liga_pol_ase
AND gaz0_poliza.end_incluye_aseg = gaz0_asegurado.end_incluye_aseg
AND gaz0_poliza.end_subramo = gaz0_asegurado.end_subramo
AND gaz0_poliza.end_fecha_fin = gaz0_asegurado.end_fecha_fin

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_INFO_COBER_DATOS_ADICIONALES  AS
SELECT NUM_POLIZA,VIGENCIA_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
''                               AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
CDFILIAC                         AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
CAST(SEC_OBJETO AS INT)          AS IND_OBJETO,
'INFO'                           AS CVE_SISTEMA,
CAST('INFO'  AS STRING)          AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CVE_COBERTURA                    AS CVE_COBERTURA,
''                               AS CVE_PLAN_COBERTURA,
''                               AS CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITAL,
CAST(CPASEGUR AS DECIMAL(16,4))  AS VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA,
CAST(TCCDMOSA AS STRING)         AS CVE_UNIDAD_SUMA_ASEGURADA,
CAST(VADEDUNA AS DECIMAL(16,4))  AS VAL_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL,
CAST(TCCDMODE AS STRING)         AS CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL,
CAST(VADEDUIN AS STRING)         AS VAL_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL,
CAST(TCCDMODI AS STRING)         AS CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL,
CAST(CDCOAINT AS STRING)         AS PCT_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,
CAST(VALIMCOA AS STRING)         AS LIM_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,
CAST(TCCDMOCO AS STRING)         AS CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,
CAST(CDCOAINT AS STRING)         AS PCT_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,
CAST(VALIMCOI AS STRING)         AS LIM_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,
CAST(TCCDMOCI AS STRING)         AS CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,
CAST(ESMCT    AS STRING)         AS CVE_ESTATUS_COBERTURA,
CAST(FEINIMCT AS STRING)         AS FCH_INI_COBERTURA,
CAST(FEFINMCT AS STRING)         AS FCH_FIN_COBERTURA,
CAST(FEEFTOMO AS STRING)         AS FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
CAST(FEFINEFE AS STRING)         AS FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO,
CAST(INNIVEAS AS STRING)         AS IND_NIVEL_ASIGNACION,
CAST(VAEXTOBS AS STRING)         AS VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_OBESIDAD,
CAST(VAEXTDIC AS STRING)         AS VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_DICTAMEN,
CASE WHEN INPREEXT IS NULL   THEN CAST('' AS STRING)
WHEN TRIM(INPREEXT) = ''   THEN CAST('' AS STRING)
ELSE    CAST(INPREEXT AS STRING)
END AS CVE_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA,
CASE WHEN INPREEXT IS NULL   THEN CAST('SIN IND TIPO DE PREEXISTENCIA' AS STRING)
WHEN TRIM(INPREEXT) = ''   THEN CAST('SIN IND TIPO DE PREEXISTENCIA' AS STRING)
ELSE   CAST(upper( DES_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA) AS STRING)
END  AS DES_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA,
CAST(CVE_COBERTURA AS STRING)    AS CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,
CAST(FESALIDA AS STRING)         AS FCH_SALIDA_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
CAST(FEREGRES AS STRING)         AS FCH_REGRESO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
CAST(CDESTAN  AS STRING)         AS CVE_PERIODO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
CAST(CDDESTI  AS STRING)         AS CVE_DESTINO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
CAST(TCTIPCAG AS STRING)         AS CVE_TARIFICAR_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
CAST(CPASENAC AS STRING)         AS VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NACIONAL,
CAST(CPASINTR AS STRING)         AS VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_INTERNACIONAL,
CAST(TCCDMOSA AS STRING)         AS CVE_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NAL_INTERNAL,
CAST(VARECCOB AS STRING)         AS VAL_RECARGO,
CAST(FEANTCOB AS STRING)         AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD,
CAST(CDSUASDI AS STRING)         AS COD_SUMA_ASEGURADA_DIARIA,
CAST(INHOSPIT AS STRING)         AS BAN_HOSPITALIZACION,
CAST(PODESAGE AS STRING)         AS PCT_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA,
CAST(CDDESCTO AS STRING)         AS CVE_CONCEPTO_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA,
CAST(POPAGHON AS STRING)         AS PCT_PAGO_HONORARIOS,
CAST(INDESRIE AS STRING)         AS PCT_DESCUENTO_RIESGO_SELECTO,
CAST(POREDE03 AS STRING)         AS PCT_DESCUENTO_COMERCIAL_COBERTURA,
CAST(CPASERFA AS STRING)         AS SUM_ASEGURADA_DEPENDIENTES_FALLECIMIENTO,
CASE WHEN CDPERESP IS NULL   THEN CAST('' AS STRING)
ELSE   CAST(CDPERESP AS STRING)
END        AS CVE_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE,
CASE WHEN CDPERESP IS NULL   THEN CAST('NINGUNO' AS STRING)
ELSE   CAST(upper( trim(DES_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE)) AS STRING)
END   AS DES_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_COBERTURA_ADICIONALES_COMPLEMENTO stg
LEFT JOIN bddldes.cat_preexistencia  as cat_preexistencia
on trim(stg.INPREEXT) = trim(cat_preexistencia.cve_preexistencia_cobertura)
LEFT JOIN bddldes.cat_periodo_espera as cat_periodo_espera
on trim(stg.CDPERESP) = trim(cat_periodo_espera.CVE_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLAPR.CNM_ENDOSO
SELECT DISTINCT
num_poliza
,num_poliza_cobranza
,cve_oficina_endoso
,descr_oficina_endoso
,num_endoso
,cve_tipo_endoso
,descr_tipo_endoso
,descr_nivel_aplicacion
,certificado_endoso
,cve_endoso_exclusion
,texto_endoso
,fch_ini_vig_endoso
,fch_fin_vig_endoso
,cve_usuario_endoso
,nombre_usuario_endoso
,cve_estatus_endoso
,descr_estatus_endoso
,fch_emision_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_titulo), "") as des_titulo_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var1), "") as des_var1_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var2), "") as des_var2_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var3), "") as des_var3_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var4), "") as des_var4_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var5), "") as des_var5_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var6), "") as des_var6_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var7), "") as des_var7_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var8), "") as des_var8_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(exc_estatus_endoso), "") as ind_endoso_cancelado
,reflect(
'org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''),
NVL(CAST(num_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),
NVL(cve_endoso_exclusion,''))) AS idmd5
,reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''),
NVL(CAST(cve_oficina_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(descr_oficina_endoso,''),
NVL(CAST(num_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),
NVL(descr_tipo_endoso,''),
NVL(descr_nivel_aplicacion,''),
NVL(certificado_endoso,''),
NVL(cve_endoso_exclusion,''),
NVL(texto_endoso,''),
NVL(CAST(fch_ini_vig_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(CAST(fch_fin_vig_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(cve_usuario_endoso,''),
NVL(nombre_usuario_endoso,''),
NVL(cve_estatus_endoso,''),
NVL(descr_estatus_endoso,''),
NVL(CAST(fch_emision_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_titulo, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var1, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var2, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var3, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var4, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var5, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var6, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var7, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var8, ""),
NVL(exc_estatus_endoso, ""),
NVL(CAST(fechaaud AS STRING), ''),
NVL(cve_subtipo_endoso,''),
NVL(cve_sistema,''))) AS idmd5completo
,fechaaud
,cve_subtipo_endoso
,cve_sistema
FROM BDDLALM.ALM_ENDOSO_EXC
WHERE CVE_TIPO_ENDOSO IN ('A','B','P')
UNION ALL
SELECT EH.*
FROM (SELECT * FROM BDDLAPR.CNM_ENDOSO WHERE CVE_TIPO_ENDOSO IN ('A','B','P')) EH
FULL JOIN (SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.ALM_ENDOSO_EXC WHERE CVE_TIPO_ENDOSO IN ('A','B','P')) E
ON EH.num_poliza = E.num_poliza
AND EH.num_poliza_cobranza = E.num_poliza_cobranza
WHERE E.cve_tipo_endoso IS NULL

,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var1), "") as des_var1_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var2), "") as des_var2_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var3), "") as des_var3_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var4), "") as des_var4_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var5), "") as des_var5_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var6), "") as des_var6_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var7), "") as des_var7_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(descr_texto_endoso_var8), "") as des_var8_endoso
,NVL(TRIM(exc_estatus_endoso), "") as ind_endoso_cancelado
,reflect(
'org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''),
NVL(CAST(num_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),
NVL(cve_endoso_exclusion,''))) AS idmd5
,reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''),
NVL(CAST(cve_oficina_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(descr_oficina_endoso,''),
NVL(CAST(num_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),
NVL(descr_tipo_endoso,''),
NVL(descr_nivel_aplicacion,''),
NVL(certificado_endoso,''),
NVL(cve_endoso_exclusion,''),
NVL(texto_endoso,''),
NVL(CAST(fch_ini_vig_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(CAST(fch_fin_vig_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(cve_usuario_endoso,''),
NVL(nombre_usuario_endoso,''),
NVL(cve_estatus_endoso,''),
NVL(descr_estatus_endoso,''),
NVL(CAST(fch_emision_endoso AS STRING), ''),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_titulo, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var1, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var2, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var3, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var4, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var5, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var6, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var7, ""),
NVL(descr_texto_endoso_var8, ""),
NVL(exc_estatus_endoso, ""),
NVL(CAST(fechaaud AS STRING), ''),
NVL(cve_subtipo_endoso,''),
NVL(cve_sistema,''))) AS idmd5completo
,fechaaud
,cve_subtipo_endoso
,cve_sistema
FROM BDDLALM.ALM_ENDOSO_EXC
WHERE CVE_TIPO_ENDOSO IN ('A','B','P')
UNION ALL
SELECT EH.*
FROM (SELECT * FROM BDDLAPR.CNM_ENDOSO WHERE CVE_TIPO_ENDOSO IN ('A','B','P')) EH
FULL JOIN (SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.ALM_ENDOSO_EXC WHERE CVE_TIPO_ENDOSO IN ('A','B','P')) E
ON EH.num_poliza = E.num_poliza
AND EH.num_poliza_cobranza = E.num_poliza_cobranza
WHERE E.cve_tipo_endoso IS NULL

create table bddldes.cat_preexistencia as
select trim(kget.cdelemen)as cve_preexistencia_cobertura , trim(kget.dselemen) as DES_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA
from  bddlcru.ktctget kget
where trim(cdtabla) = 'KTPT6EG'

create table bddldes.cat_periodo_espera as
select trim(kget.cdelemen)as CVE_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE , trim(kget.dselemen) as DES_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE
from  bddlcru.ktctget kget
where trim(cdtabla) = 'KTPT4PG'

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_CAT_TIPO_UNIDAD AS
SELECT
gaz0_poliza.*
,nvl(trim(tipo_unidad_sum.dca_desc), '') as cve_unidad
,nvl(trim(tipo_unidad_dedu.dca_desc), '')  AS cve_moneda
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_TRANSPOSE_COBERTURA as gaz0_poliza
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.gaz0_cat_tipo_unidad as tipo_unidad_sum
on trim(gaz0_poliza.pol_uni_sum) = trim(tipo_unidad_sum.dca_clave)
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.gaz0_cat_tipo_unidad as tipo_unidad_dedu
on trim(gaz0_poliza.pol_uni_dedu) = trim(tipo_unidad_dedu.dca_clave)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_CAT_TIPO_UNIDAD AS
SELECT
gaz0_poliza.*
,nvl(trim(tipo_unidad_sum.dca_desc), '') as cve_unidad
,nvl(trim(tipo_unidad_dedu.dca_desc), '')  AS cve_moneda
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_TRANSPOSE_COBERTURA as gaz0_poliza
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.gaz0_cat_tipo_unidad as tipo_unidad_sum
on trim(gaz0_poliza.pol_uni_sum) = trim(tipo_unidad_sum.dca_clave)
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.gaz0_cat_tipo_unidad as tipo_unidad_dedu
on trim(gaz0_poliza.pol_uni_dedu) = trim(tipo_unidad_dedu.dca_clave)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_COBERTURA_ADICIONALES_COMPLEMENTO AS
SELECT
POLIZA_ADICIONALES.NUM_POLIZA,
POLIZA_ADICIONALES.VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
POLIZA_ADICIONALES.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
GM_COB.CDFILIAC, GM_COB.SEC_OBJETO,
GM_COB.CPASEGUR,
GM_COB.TCCDMOSA, GM_COB.VADEDUNA,
GM_COB.TCCDMODE, GM_COB.VADEDUIN,
GM_COB.TCCDMODI, GM_COB.CDCOAINT,
GM_COB.VALIMCOI,
GM_COB.VALIMCOA, GM_COB.TCCDMOCO,
GM_COB.TCCDMOCI, GM_COB.ESMCT,
GM_COB.FEINIMCT, GM_COB.FEFINMCT,
GM_COB.FEEFTOMO, GM_COB.FEFINEFE,
GM_COB.INNIVEAS, GM_COB.VAEXTOBS,
GM_COB.VAEXTDIC, GM_COB.INPREEXT,
GM_COB.CVE_COBERTURA,
GM_COB.FESALIDA, GM_COB.FEREGRES,
GM_COB.CDESTAN,  GM_COB.CDDESTI,
GM_COB.TCTIPCAG, GM_COB.CPASENAC,
GM_COB.CPASINTR, GM_COB.VARECCOB,
GM_COB.FEANTCOB, GM_COB.CDSUASDI,
GM_COB.INHOSPIT, GM_COB.PODESAGE,
GM_COB.CDDESCTO, GM_COB.POPAGHON,
GM_COB.INDESRIE, GM_COB.POREDE03,
GM_COB.CPASERFA, GM_COB.CDPERESP
FROM BDDLAPR.CNM_POLIZA_DATOS_ADICIONALES POLIZA_ADICIONALES
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT
COB.NUM_POLIZA,COB.NUM_VERSION, ASEG.CDFILIAC, COB.SEC_OBJETO,
COB.CPASEGUR, COB.TCCDMOSA, COB.VADEDUNA, COB.TCCDMODE, COB.VADEDUIN, COB.TCCDMODI,
COB.CDCOAINT, COB.VALIMCOA, COB.VALIMCOI, COB.TCCDMOCO, COB.TCCDMOCI, COB.ESMCT,    COB.FEINIMCT,
COB.FEFINMCT, COB.FEEFTOMO, COB.FEFINEFE, COB.INNIVEAS, COB.VAEXTOBS, COB.VAEXTDIC,
COB.INPREEXT, COB.CVE_COBERTURA,COB.FESALIDA,
COB.FEREGRES,COB.CDESTAN,   COB.CDDESTI,  COB.TCTIPCAG, COB.CPASENAC, COB.CPASINTR,
COB.VARECCOB, COB.FEANTCOB, COB.CDSUASDI, COB.INHOSPIT, COB.PODESAGE, COB.CDDESCTO,
COB.POPAGHON, COB.INDESRIE, COB.POREDE03, COB.CPASERFA , COB.CDPERESP
FROM (SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_COBERTURA UNION ALL SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_COBERTURA_RELLENO) COB
INNER JOIN (
SELECT NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION, SEC_OBJETO, CVE_COBERTURA, MAX(TSULTMOD) TSULTMOD
FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_COBERTURA
GROUP BY NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION, SEC_OBJETO, CVE_COBERTURA
UNION ALL
SELECT NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION, SEC_OBJETO, CVE_COBERTURA, MAX(TSULTMOD) TSULTMOD
FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_COBERTURA_RELLENO
GROUP BY NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION, SEC_OBJETO, CVE_COBERTURA
) MAXIMOS ON COB.NUM_POLIZA = MAXIMOS.NUM_POLIZA AND COB.NUM_VERSION = MAXIMOS.NUM_VERSION AND COB.SEC_OBJETO = MAXIMOS.SEC_OBJETO AND COB.CVE_COBERTURA = MAXIMOS.CVE_COBERTURA AND COB.TSULTMOD = MAXIMOS.TSULTMOD
LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_OBJETO UNION ALL SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_OBJETO_RELLENO) ASEG
ON ASEG.NUM_POLIZA = COB.NUM_POLIZA
AND ASEG.NUM_VERSION = COB.NUM_VERSION
AND CAST(ASEG.SEC_OBJETO AS DECIMAL(5,0)) = COB.SEC_OBJETO
AND ASEG.CVE_PROD_TECNICO = COB.CVE_PROD_TECNICO
AND ASEG.CVE_PROD_COMERCIAL=COB.CVE_PROD_COMERCIAL
)as GM_COB
ON POLIZA_ADICIONALES.NUM_POLIZA = GM_COB.NUM_POLIZA
AND POLIZA_ADICIONALES.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA = GM_COB.NUM_VERSION

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_COBERTURA_ADICIONALES_COMPLEMENTO AS
SELECT
POLIZA_ADICIONALES.NUM_POLIZA,
POLIZA_ADICIONALES.VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
POLIZA_ADICIONALES.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
GM_COB.CDFILIAC, GM_COB.SEC_OBJETO,
GM_COB.CPASEGUR,
GM_COB.TCCDMOSA, GM_COB.VADEDUNA,
GM_COB.TCCDMODE, GM_COB.VADEDUIN,
GM_COB.TCCDMODI, GM_COB.CDCOAINT,
GM_COB.VALIMCOI,
GM_COB.VALIMCOA, GM_COB.TCCDMOCO,
GM_COB.TCCDMOCI, GM_COB.ESMCT,
GM_COB.FEINIMCT, GM_COB.FEFINMCT,
GM_COB.FEEFTOMO, GM_COB.FEFINEFE,
GM_COB.INNIVEAS, GM_COB.VAEXTOBS,
GM_COB.VAEXTDIC, GM_COB.INPREEXT,
GM_COB.CVE_COBERTURA,
GM_COB.FESALIDA, GM_COB.FEREGRES,
GM_COB.CDESTAN,  GM_COB.CDDESTI,
GM_COB.TCTIPCAG, GM_COB.CPASENAC,
GM_COB.CPASINTR, GM_COB.VARECCOB,
GM_COB.FEANTCOB, GM_COB.CDSUASDI,
GM_COB.INHOSPIT, GM_COB.PODESAGE,
GM_COB.CDDESCTO, GM_COB.POPAGHON,
GM_COB.INDESRIE, GM_COB.POREDE03,
GM_COB.CPASERFA, GM_COB.CDPERESP
FROM BDDLAPR.CNM_POLIZA_DATOS_ADICIONALES POLIZA_ADICIONALES
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT
COB.NUM_POLIZA,COB.NUM_VERSION, ASEG.CDFILIAC, COB.SEC_OBJETO,
COB.CPASEGUR, COB.TCCDMOSA, COB.VADEDUNA, COB.TCCDMODE, COB.VADEDUIN, COB.TCCDMODI,
COB.CDCOAINT, COB.VALIMCOA, COB.VALIMCOI, COB.TCCDMOCO, COB.TCCDMOCI, COB.ESMCT,    COB.FEINIMCT,
COB.FEFINMCT, COB.FEEFTOMO, COB.FEFINEFE, COB.INNIVEAS, COB.VAEXTOBS, COB.VAEXTDIC,
COB.INPREEXT, COB.CVE_COBERTURA,COB.FESALIDA,
COB.FEREGRES,COB.CDESTAN,   COB.CDDESTI,  COB.TCTIPCAG, COB.CPASENAC, COB.CPASINTR,
COB.VARECCOB, COB.FEANTCOB, COB.CDSUASDI, COB.INHOSPIT, COB.PODESAGE, COB.CDDESCTO,
COB.POPAGHON, COB.INDESRIE, COB.POREDE03, COB.CPASERFA , COB.CDPERESP
FROM (SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_COBERTURA UNION ALL SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_COBERTURA_RELLENO) COB
INNER JOIN (
SELECT NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION, SEC_OBJETO, CVE_COBERTURA, MAX(TSULTMOD) TSULTMOD
FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_COBERTURA
GROUP BY NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION, SEC_OBJETO, CVE_COBERTURA
UNION ALL
SELECT NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION, SEC_OBJETO, CVE_COBERTURA, MAX(TSULTMOD) TSULTMOD
FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_COBERTURA_RELLENO
GROUP BY NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION, SEC_OBJETO, CVE_COBERTURA
) MAXIMOS ON COB.NUM_POLIZA = MAXIMOS.NUM_POLIZA AND COB.NUM_VERSION = MAXIMOS.NUM_VERSION AND COB.SEC_OBJETO = MAXIMOS.SEC_OBJETO AND COB.CVE_COBERTURA = MAXIMOS.CVE_COBERTURA AND COB.TSULTMOD = MAXIMOS.TSULTMOD
LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_OBJETO UNION ALL SELECT * FROM BDDLALM.GMM_ELEMENTO_OBJETO_RELLENO) ASEG
ON ASEG.NUM_POLIZA = COB.NUM_POLIZA
AND ASEG.NUM_VERSION = COB.NUM_VERSION
AND CAST(ASEG.SEC_OBJETO AS DECIMAL(5,0)) = COB.SEC_OBJETO
AND ASEG.CVE_PROD_TECNICO = COB.CVE_PROD_TECNICO
AND ASEG.CVE_PROD_COMERCIAL=COB.CVE_PROD_COMERCIAL
)as GM_COB
ON POLIZA_ADICIONALES.NUM_POLIZA = GM_COB.NUM_POLIZA
AND POLIZA_ADICIONALES.NUM_VERSION_POLIZA = GM_COB.NUM_VERSION

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_TRANSPOSE_DATOS_ADICIONALES_ASEGURADO AS
SELECT * FROM(
SELECT ASE_POL_NUM, ASE_POL_OFNA, POL_OFI_RENOVAC, POL_NUM_RENOVAC,
ASE_NUM_CERTIF, ASE_CVE_PARIEN, ASE_PAT, ASE_MAT, ASE_NOMBRE1, ASE_NOMBRE2,
ASE_FEC_ALTA, ASE_FEC_BAJA, ASE_FEC_ANTIGUEDAD, ASE_FEC_ANTIG_EXT, ASE_FEC_NAC,
ASE_SEXO, ASE_STATUS, END_FECHA_INI, END_STATUS,END_NUM_CONSEC                       ,
ASEGURADOMAP[0] AS POL_RAMO,
ASEGURADOMAP[1] AS POL_PLAN,
ASEGURADOMAP[2] AS POL_PRIMA,
ASEGURADOMAP[3] AS POL_TARIFA
FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_TMP_DATOS_ADICIONLES_ASEGURADO_TRANSPOSE_MAP
) AS TMP

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_TMP_DATOS_ADICIONLES_ASEGURADO_TRANSPOSE_MAP AS
SELECT ASE_POL_NUM, ASE_POL_OFNA, POL_OFI_RENOVAC, POL_NUM_RENOVAC,
ASE_NUM_CERTIF, ASE_CVE_PARIEN, ASE_PAT, ASE_MAT, ASE_NOMBRE1, ASE_NOMBRE2,
ASE_FEC_ALTA, ASE_FEC_BAJA, ASE_FEC_ANTIGUEDAD, ASE_FEC_ANTIG_EXT, ASE_FEC_NAC,
ASE_SEXO, ASE_STATUS, END_FECHA_INI, END_STATUS,END_NUM_CONSEC,NUM_ASEGURADO, SPLIT(ASEGURADO,'-') AS ASEGURADOMAP
FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_TMP_DATOS_ADICIONLES_ASEGURADO_TRANSPOSE
LATERAL VIEW EXPLODE(ASEGURADOAZUL) EXPLODE_TABLE AS NUM_ASEGURADO, ASEGURADO

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_TRANSPOSE_COBERTURA AS
select * FROM(
select pol_oficina, pol_numero,pol_ofi_renovac,pol_num_renovac,
end_fecha_ini,end_num_oficina,end_num_tipo,end_num_consec,
end_num_control,end_liga_pol_ase,end_incluye_aseg,end_subramo ,end_fecha_fin,
cobeturaMap[0] as pol_nombre_cob,
cobeturaMap[1] as pol_coaseguro,
cobeturaMap[2] as pol_suma_aseg,
cobeturaMap[3] as pol_deducible,
cobeturaMap[4] as pol_plan,
cobeturaMap[5] as pol_stdr
,cobeturaMap[6] as pol_uni_sum,
cobeturaMap[7] as pol_uni_dedu
FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_TMP_SPLIT_MAP_COBERTURA ) as TMP
where pol_nombre_cob != ''

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_TMP_SPLIT_MAP_COBERTURA AS
SELECT pol_oficina, pol_numero,pol_ofi_renovac,pol_num_renovac,
end_fecha_ini,end_num_oficina,end_num_tipo,end_num_consec,
end_num_control,end_liga_pol_ase,end_incluye_aseg,end_subramo ,end_fecha_fin,
num_cobertura, split(cobertura,'-') as cobeturaMap
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_TMP_TRANSPOSE_COBERTURA
LATERAL VIEW EXPLODE(coberturaAZUL) explode_table AS num_cobertura, cobertura

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLDES.STG_GMM_CON_ENR_SOLICITUD_RCLA_DG
SELECT
CAST(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(SLR0.CEO_CVE AS STRING),2,'0'),SLR0.MDA_CVE, LPAD(CAST(SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING),7,'0')) AS VARCHAR(11)) AS id_solicitud,
CAST(COALESCE(TRIM(SLR0.RCL_NUM),'') AS VARCHAR(15)) AS num_reclamacion,
CAST('AZUL' AS VARCHAR(4)) AS cve_sistema_int,
CAST('RCLA' AS VARCHAR(4)) AS cve_sistema,
COALESCE(SLR0.CEO_CVE,-999) AS cve_centro_regional,
COALESCE(SLR0.MDA_CVE,'') AS cve_modalidad,
CAST(COALESCE(CAST(SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING),'') AS VARCHAR(15)) AS folio_solicitud,
COALESCE(SLR0.SLR_NUM_TMT, -1) AS num_solicitud_tramite,
-999 AS num_ente_interviniente,
CAST((CASE WHEN A.CMP_MOO_IMR_KTA IS NOT NULL THEN A.CMP_MOO_IMR_KTA ELSE DIM0.DIM_MOO_IMR_KPS END) AS DECIMAL(15,3))AS mto_impreso_carta,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS fch_registro_solicitud,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_ACT AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_ACT AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_ACT AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS fch_ctrl_act_solicitud,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_CTR_TRF AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_CTR_TRF AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_CTR_TRF AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS fch_ctrl_trnsf_solicitud,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TS_ALTA_HDFS
FROM
(
SELECT DISTINCT
RCL_NUM, CEO_CVE, MDA_CVE, SLR_NUM_FOL, slr_num_tmt, icd_cve, slr_fec_reo, slr_act, slr_ctr_trf
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTSLR0
) SLR0
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NRLTDIM0 AS DIM0
ON SLR0.CEO_CVE = DIM0.CEO_CVE AND SLR0.MDA_CVE = DIM0.MDA_CVE AND SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = DIM0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
CMP01.CEO_CVE,
CMP01.MDA_CVE,
CMP01.SLR_NUM_FOL,
CMP01.CMP_MOO_IMR_KTA
FROM
(
SELECT * FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTCMP0
) CMP01
INNER JOIN
(   SELECT
CEO_CVE,
MDA_CVE,
SLR_NUM_FOL,
MAX(CMP_NUM) AS MX_CMP_NUM
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTCMP0 AS CMP0
GROUP BY CEO_CVE,MDA_CVE,SLR_NUM_FOL
) A
ON A.CEO_CVE = CMP01.CEO_CVE
AND A.MDA_CVE = CMP01.MDA_CVE
AND A.SLR_NUM_FOL = CMP01.SLR_NUM_FOL
AND A.MX_CMP_NUM = CMP01.CMP_NUM
) A
ON SLR0.CEO_CVE = A.CEO_CVE AND SLR0.MDA_CVE = A.MDA_CVE AND SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = A.SLR_NUM_FOL

ON SLR0.CEO_CVE = DIM0.CEO_CVE AND SLR0.MDA_CVE = DIM0.MDA_CVE AND SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = DIM0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
CMP01.CEO_CVE,
CMP01.MDA_CVE,
CMP01.SLR_NUM_FOL,
CMP01.CMP_MOO_IMR_KTA
FROM
(
SELECT * FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTCMP0
) CMP01
INNER JOIN
(   SELECT
CEO_CVE,
MDA_CVE,
SLR_NUM_FOL,
MAX(CMP_NUM) AS MX_CMP_NUM
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTCMP0 AS CMP0
GROUP BY CEO_CVE,MDA_CVE,SLR_NUM_FOL
) A
ON A.CEO_CVE = CMP01.CEO_CVE
AND A.MDA_CVE = CMP01.MDA_CVE
AND A.SLR_NUM_FOL = CMP01.SLR_NUM_FOL
AND A.MX_CMP_NUM = CMP01.CMP_NUM
) A
ON SLR0.CEO_CVE = A.CEO_CVE AND SLR0.MDA_CVE = A.MDA_CVE AND SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = A.SLR_NUM_FOL

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLDES.STG_GMM_CON_ENR_SOLICITUD_INFO
SELECT
CAST(COALESCE(TRIM(50T.CDSINIES), '') AS VARCHAR(11)) AS ID_SOLICITUD,
CAST(COALESCE(TRIM(50T.CDRECICD),'') AS VARCHAR(15)) AS NUM_RECLAMACION,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(4)) AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(4)) AS CVE_SISTEMA,
-999 AS CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
COALESCE(TRIM(50T.TCMODALI),'') AS CVE_MODALIDAD,
CAST(COALESCE(TRIM(KSIA12T.CDSINIZU),'') AS VARCHAR(15)) AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
-999 AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
COALESCE(50T.CTNUPOIN,-999) AS NUM_ENTE_INTERVINIENTE,
CASE WHEN 51T.INPRINCI = 'N' THEN '' ELSE COALESCE(51T.TCCDICD,'') END AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(51T.CTNUICD,-999) AS NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
CASE WHEN 51T.INPRINCI = 'N' THEN '' ELSE COALESCE(51T.TCCDICD,'') END AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION,
CAST(CASE WHEN 51T.INPRINCI = 'N' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS VARCHAR(1)) AS BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL,
'' AS DETALLE_DIAGNOSTICO,
0 AS MTO_IMPORTE_RESERVA_AUT,
CASE WHEN 51T.INPRINCI = 'N' THEN 0 ELSE COALESCE(50T.NUMDIAUT, -1) END AS TOT_DIAS_AUTORIZADOS,
50T.IMPREAUT AS MTO_IMPRESO_CARTA,
10000101 AS FCH_REGISTRO_SOLICITUD,
10000101 AS FCH_CTRL_ACT_SOLICITUD,
10000101 AS FCH_CTRL_TRNSF_SOLICITUD,
10000101 AS FCH_CTRL_ACT_COMPLICACION,
10000101 AS FCH_CTRL_TRNSF_COMPLICACION,
10000101 AS FCH_REPORTE_COMPLICACION,
10000101 AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_COMPLICACION,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TS_ALTA_HDFS
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM50T 50T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON 50T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN  BDDLCRU.KACM51T 51T
ON 50T.CDSINIES =  51T.CDSINIES AND 50T.CTNUPOIN =  51T.CTNUPOIN

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLDES.STG_GMM_CON_ENR_SOLICITUD_RCLA
SELECT DISTINCT
CAST(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(SLR0.CEO_CVE AS STRING),2,'0'),SLR0.MDA_CVE, LPAD(CAST(SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING),7,'0')) AS VARCHAR(11)) AS ID_SOLICITUD,
CAST(COALESCE(TRIM(SLR0.RCL_NUM),'') AS VARCHAR(15)) AS NUM_RECLAMACION,
CAST('AZUL' AS VARCHAR(4)) AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CAST('RCLA' AS VARCHAR(4)) AS CVE_SISTEMA,
SLR0.CEO_CVE AS CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
SLR0.MDA_CVE AS CVE_MODALIDAD,
CAST(COALESCE(CAST(SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING),'') AS VARCHAR(15)) AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(SLR0.SLR_NUM_TMT, -1) AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
-999 AS NUM_ENTE_INTERVINIENTE,
COALESCE(SLR0.ICD_CVE, '') AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
CMP0.CMP_NUM AS NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
COALESCE(CMP0.CMP_ICD_CVE,'') AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION,
CAST(CASE WHEN CMP0.CMP_ICD_CVE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS VARCHAR(1)) AS BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL,
REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(TRIM(CMP0.CMP_DGN),''), '\\t|\\r|\\n', '') AS DETALLE_DIAGNOSTICO,
CMP0.CMP_IMP_RSV_AUR AS MTO_IMPORTE_RESERVA_AUT,
COALESCE(CMP0.CMP_DIA_AUR,-999) AS TOT_DIAS_AUTORIZADOS,
CMP0.CMP_MOO_IMR_KTA AS MTO_IMPRESO_CARTA,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS FCH_REGISTRO_SOLICITUD,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_ACT AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_ACT AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_ACT AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS FCH_CTRL_ACT_SOLICITUD,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_CTR_TRF AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_CTR_TRF AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(SLR0.SLR_CTR_TRF AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS FCH_CTRL_TRNSF_SOLICITUD,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_ACT AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_ACT AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_ACT AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS FCH_CTRL_ACT_COMPLICACION,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_CTR_TRF AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_CTR_TRF AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_CTR_TRF AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS FCH_CTRL_TRNSF_COMPLICACION,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_FEC_REP AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_FEC_REP AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_FEC_REP AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS FCH_REPORTE_COMPLICACION,
CAST(COALESCE(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_FEC_OCR AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_FEC_OCR AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(CMP0.CMP_FEC_OCR AS STRING),9,2)),'10000101') AS INT) AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_COMPLICACION,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TS_ALTA_HDFS
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTSLR0 AS SLR0
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTCMP0 AS CMP0
ON CMP0.CEO_CVE = SLR0.CEO_CVE
AND CMP0.MDA_CVE = SLR0.MDA_CVE
AND CMP0.SLR_NUM_FOL = SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL
